matomo (4.11.0-1) stable; urgency=high

  * Releasing Matomo 4.11.0
  * Invite new users in Matomo, rather than creating them directly [by
    @diosmosis, @peterhashair] (Closes: #13321)
  * Notify that requests to matomo.org will soon use HTTPS by default
    [by @peterhashair] (Closes: #19081)
  * Goal tracking: New Report "Top Landing Pages URLs/Titles"  for each
    goal (and also "Pages where goals are triggered") [by @bx80]
    (Closes: #2030)
  * Add Goals visualisation for Pages reports in behaviour category [by
    @bx80] (Closes: #14974)
  * Sparklines show correct data in all goals reports [by @sgiehl]
    (Closes: #19206)
  * Show sparkline evolution figures for visits, goals and ecommerce
    overviews [by @bx80] (Closes: #10716)
  * Add refresh / reload keyboard shortcut for visualizations (eg
    tables, pie, bar chart) [by @korve] (Closes: #11047)
  * Fix referrer attribution cookie not set if no tracking request is
    sent, resulting in wrong attribution [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #18809)
  * Fix error in php8.1 running console config:get command [by @sgiehl]
    (Closes: #19225)
  * Show a notification if PHP version is end of life [by @sgiehl]
    (Closes: #19421)
  * Ensure Safari browser shows the information notice [by
    @peterhashair] (Closes: #19244)
  * Fix anchor links issue within Matomo [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #19252)
  * Fix for undefined array index error when rendering sparklines [by
    @bx80] (Closes: #19275)
  * Fixes problem where dashboards can't be copied to users in certain
    circumstances [by @peterhashair, @sgiehl] (Closes: #18692)
  * When a segment is shown, and no data is there, then show accurate
    error message when segment won't be archived  [by @peterhashair]
    (Closes: #19011)
  * Preserve rows to display on Visits overview (with graph) (Closes:
    #11046)
  * Improve memory management in DataTable/CSV [by @sgiehl] (Closes:
    #19158)
  * Take care to always 'return request' in
    appendAvailablePerformanceMetrics [by @danielpunkass, @sgiehl]
    (Closes: #19232)
  * Add utility function for pattern that issues a single AJAX request
    at a time [by @diosmosis, @peterhashair] (Closes: #19239)
  * Add 429 (rate limited) response code [by @JasonMortonNZ,
    @justinvelluppillai] (Closes: #19245)
  * Composer: Revise project type from "application" to "project" [by
    @pixelbrackets, @sgiehl] (Closes: #19268)
  * Use correct async init method to detect when tracker is loaded [by
    @AltamashShaikh] (Closes: #484)
  * Allow dynamic height on Tag manager preview [by @korve,
    @AltamashShaikh] (Closes: #477)
  * "Observe DOM changes" in Visibility Trigger causes JS error on load
    [by @AltamashShaikh] (Closes: #481)
  * Add current PHP versions to Travis CI tests [by @pixelbrackets,
    @sgiehl] (Closes: #70)
  * Fix build badge and remove failing images in Travis CI tests [by
    @pixelbrackets, @sgiehl] (Closes: #71)
  * Import fails when Referrer field is not present using Regex format
    [by @kuzi-moto] (Closes: #335)
  * Set referrer to empty string if it doesn't exist [by @kuzi-moto,
    @sgiehl] (Closes: #336)
  * More virtualization of MatomoTracker class  [by @Demichev] (Closes:
    #103)
  * Add katrd.xyz [by @ericguirbal, @spmedia] (Closes: #1322)
  * Detect new brands: Sylvania, Future Mobile Technology, MBI, OUJIA,
    Qware  and Detect devices for several existing brands  [by
    @sanchezzzhak, @sgiehl] (Closes: #7111)
  * Detect httplib2 [by @sanchezzzhak, @sgiehl] (Closes: #7112)
  * Adds detection for Tesla Browser [by @liviuconcioiu, @sanchezzzhak]
    (Closes: #7117)
  * Adds detection for Patchwatch, WhereGoes [by @liviuconcioiu,
    @sanchezzzhak] (Closes: #7118)
  * Adds detection for various apps and improves version detection for
    Windows [by @liviuconcioiu, @sanchezzzhak] (Closes: #7119)
  * Improves detection for Tesla, Xiaomi devices [by @liviuconcioiu,
    @sanchezzzhak] (Closes: #7120)
  * Improvement of condition for detection the platform when using
    clienthints [by @sanchezzzhak, @sgiehl] (Closes: #7121)
  * Detect devices for existing brands  [by @sanchezzzhak] (Closes:
    #7122)
  * Adds detection for InternetMeasurement, masscan-ng bots [by
    @liviuconcioiu, @sanchezzzhak] (Closes: #7123)
  * Adds detection for Sidekick and Wave Browser [by @liviuconcioiu,
    @sanchezzzhak] (Closes: #7124)
  * Improves version detection for iOS and improves detection for Opera
    GX [by @liviuconcioiu, @sanchezzzhak] (Closes: #7125)
  * Adds detection for various bots [by @liviuconcioiu, @sanchezzzhak]
    (Closes: #7126)
  * Detect new brands: AFFIX, Listo, Aquarius and Detect devices for
    several existing brands  [by @sanchezzzhak] (Closes: #7128)
  * Detect devices for existing brands [by @sanchezzzhak, @sgiehl]
    (Closes: #7130)
  * Detect devices for existing brands and Detect Pi Browser [by
    @sanchezzzhak, @sgiehl] (Closes: #7131)
  * Detect devices for existing brands [by @sanchezzzhak, @sgiehl]
    (Closes: #7133)

 -- Edouard Gaulué <edouard@e-gaulue.com>  Thu, 25 Aug 2022 10:52:46 +0200

matomo (4.10.1-1) stable; urgency=high

  * Releasing Matomo 4.10.1
  * Show spark lines correctly in KPI widget when using segments [by
    @diosmosis] (Closes: #19209)
  * Fix manifest.json sending HTTP-Status 403 [by @sgiehl] (Closes:
    #19251)
  * Set default hasExtraPlugin in campaign builder component to true [by
    @diosmosis] (Closes: #19241)
  * Make CustomDimensions available in Segment Editor [by @diosmosis]
    (Closes: #19237)
  * Set default null/falsey value in FieldNumber to 0 to match previous
    behavior [by @diosmosis] (Closes: #19262)

 -- Edouard Gaulué <edouard@e-gaulue.com>  Thu, 25 Aug 2022 10:48:12 +0200

matomo (4.10.0-1) stable; urgency=high

  * Releasing Matomo 4.10.0
  * Data protection: Hide visitor id in visits log if profile is
    disabled [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #18884)
  * Make Widgetize page translatable [by @korve, @sgiehl] (Closes:
    #19157)
  * Fix console command to disable 2FA for a user [by @sgiehl] (Closes:
    #18947)
  * Fix display issue with z-index for widgets that use tables with
    embedded dashboards [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #19125)
  * Ensure JS tracker unload event is triggered in edge cases to make
    sure tracking requests are sent [by @peterhashair] (Closes: #18810)
  * Make JSON config / package static files unreachable via a GET
    request [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #18128)
  * System check - don't request private directories when disabled [by
    @bx80] (Closes: #18967)
  * Fix error when setting license key from command line [by @bx80,
    @justinvelluppillai] (Closes: #19118)
  * Fix error when adding new goals if no previous goals exist for
    website/measurable [by @MichaelRoosz] (Closes: #19124)
  * PHP8.1 compatibility fixes in referrers plugin [by @MichaelRoosz]
    (Closes: #19127)
  * Create assets folder if it is missing when writing Report [by
    @samjf, @sgiehl] (Closes: #19088)
  * Ensure required translations are loaded for Goal management [by
    @sgiehl, @justinvelluppillai] (Closes: #19102)
  * Add languageName property to PiwikGlobal type [by @diosmosis]
    (Closes: #19113)
  * Rename MenuDropdown component to avoid any case mismatches [by
    @sgiehl, @justinvelluppillai] (Closes: #19156)
  * Tag Manager: Change the location of Preview window [by
    @AltamashShaikh] (Closes: #271)
  * Fix typo in getAvailableContainerVariables [by @comradekingu,
    @AltamashShaikh] (Closes: #473)
  * Updated MatomoTagDescription to remove piwik [by @AltamashShaikh,
    @tsteur] (Closes: #474)
  * Use TemplateParameters instead of raw window in PageHostname var [by
    @ulcuber, @AltamashShaikh] (Closes: #475)
  * Improves detection for generic bots [by @liviuconcioiu,
    @sanchezzzhak] (Closes: #7089)
  * Adds detection for Amazon ELB bot [by @liviuconcioiu, @sanchezzzhak]
    (Closes: #7091)
  * Detect new brands: X-AGE, QLink and devices for several existing
    brands [by @sanchezzzhak, @sgiehl] (Closes: #7093)
  * Detect Open Browser [by @sanchezzzhak, @sgiehl] (Closes: #7095)
  * Detect browsers: BrowseHere, Midori Lite, Pure Lite Browser, Berry
    Browser, Fulldive, Hi Browser,  SuperFast Browser. Amaze Browser,
    Smart Search & Web Browser, Aloha Browser Lite  [by @sanchezzzhak,
    @sgiehl] (Closes: #7097)
  * Detect new brands: Aoro, EBEN, VUCATIMES and Detect devices for
    several existing brands  [by @sanchezzzhak, @sgiehl] (Closes: #7098)
  * Detect new brands: Zonko, Zeeker, TJC, HOTREALS and Detect devices
    for several existing brands [by @sanchezzzhak] (Closes: #7100)
  * Add socialine.net [by @ericguirbal, @spmedia] (Closes: #1313)
  * Add glktfw.net [by @ericguirbal, @spmedia] (Closes: #1314)
  * Add advertisefree.co.uk [by @metmarkosaric, @spmedia] (Closes:
    #1315)
  * Add hilaryblog.top [by @ericguirbal, @spmedia] (Closes: #1316)
  * Add goodcoffeepremium.com [by @ericguirbal, @spmedia] (Closes:
    #1317)
  * Add kimblog.top [by @ericguirbal, @spmedia] (Closes: #1319)

