    detection for Amazon Linux, TencentOS, adds detection for cPanel
    HTTP Client, ALittle Client, PHP cURL Class, SafeIP, NAVER Mail and
    adds detection for various bots [by @liviuconcioiu, @sanchezzzhak]
    (Closes: #7045)
  * Add client hints fixture for Opera GX [by @liviuconcioiu, @sgiehl]
    (Closes: #7046)
  * Detect new brands LOKMAT, Joy, iWaylink and Detect devices for
    several existing brands  [by @sanchezzzhak, @sgiehl] (Closes: #7051)
  * Adds detection for Bittium, EGL, Logic Instrument brands, improves
    detection for AllDocube, Brondi, Hi, Hot Pepper, Energizer, Huawei,
    iPro, Sky, X-View brands, adds detection for Bliss OS [by
    @liviuconcioiu, @sanchezzzhak] (Closes: #7052)
  * Adds detection for GeoIP Update [by @liviuconcioiu, @sanchezzzhak]
    (Closes: #7055)
  * Adds detection for Dolphin Zero, Dolphin, OH Private Browser, Atlas,
    Jelly browsers  [by @sanchezzzhak, @sgiehl] (Closes: #7056)
  * Detect Flow Browser [by @sanchezzzhak, @sgiehl] (Closes: #7057)
  * Detect browsers: UC Browser Mini, Soul Browser, Indian UC Mini
    Browser, Opera, Opera Mini, Fast Explorer, Comfort Browser, CM Mini,
    SilverMob US [by @sanchezzzhak] (Closes: #7061)
