    Browser and adds detection for APUS Browser, Ask.com, Ayoba,
    Savannah Browser, SavySoda, SnapU2B, Surf Browser, Ui Browser Mini
    [by @liviuconcioiu, @sanchezzzhak] (Closes: #7062)
