    (Closes: #7064)
  * TVs detected as smartphone (Closes: #7066)
  * Improves detection for EKO, Kogan, Sharp, Sony, Vodafone devices [by
    @liviuconcioiu, @sanchezzzhak] (Closes: #7067)
