matomo (4.7.1-1) stable; urgency=high

  * Releasing Matomo 4.7.1
  * Rendering performance improvement for reports with many rows [by
    @bx80] (Closes: #18394)
  * Add system check warnings for php-fpm and nginx if config files are
    accessible [by @bx80] (Closes: #13589)
  * Tracking code page: Move JavaScript tracking code right after the
    website [by @peterhashair] (Closes: #18521)
  * Show a summary of what's new in the app [by @bx80] (Closes: #16805)
  * Field conditions eg in Measurable Settings API not working anymore
    [by @diosmosis] (Closes: #18539)
  * Don't archive anything in Goals unless a goal is configured or
    ecommerce is used [by @peterhashair, @sgiehl] (Closes: #18283)
  * Do not create a session if accessing login page with a not supported
    browser  [by @peterhashair] (Closes: #18560)
  * Fix possible error when generating reports for custom dimensions [by
    @sgiehl] (Closes: #18608)
  * Fix possible error when generating PDF reports containing multibyte
    chars [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #18664)
  * Improve average page load time query accuracy (reporting too low in
    some cases) [by @peterhashair] (Closes: #17012)
  * When rearchive_reports_in_past_last_n_months INI setting is used,
    the archiver should not skip processing the report for "Yesterday"
    [by @bx80] (Closes: #18344)
  * Dependent archives never processed for All visits segment causing
    some data to not show [by @peterhashair] (Closes: #18362)
  * Fix possible undefined constant exception when using ssl_no_verify
    [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #18481)
  * Ensure 2FA is not loaded when safemode is triggered [by @sgiehl]
    (Closes: #18501)
  * Ensure updates are always done with super user permission [by
    @sgiehl] (Closes: #18503)
  * remove compareDates with comparePeriods when adding new segment [by
    @diosmosis, @sgiehl] (Closes: #18535)
  * Ignore duplicate entry error when creating a sequence [by @sgiehl]
    (Closes: #18590)
  * Hide commands that don't work on windows [by @sgiehl] (Closes:
    #18603)
  * Force period type to 'range' if date is a range when checking chart
    incomplete periods [by @bx80] (Closes: #18629)
  * API Language updates [by @comradekingu, @justinvelluppillai]
    (Closes: #18506)
  * Filter metadata API response only when the test is executed for
    allowed metadata API [by @AltamashShaikh, @tsteur] (Closes: #18510)
  * Fixes more issues on PHP 8.1 [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #18514)
  * Fixes: Saving plugin settings might not work with certain password
    managers enabled [by @peterhashair, @diosmosis] (Closes: #18515)
  * Fix error where no data is shown on campaign with segments and
    periods [by @peterhashair] (Closes: #18540)
  * Refactor emails about password reset into a Mail sub-class [by
    @samjf, @justinvelluppillai] (Closes: #18616)
  * Updated translation key for fingerprint metric which was not defined
    [by @AltamashShaikh, @sgiehl] (Closes: #18621)
  * Fixed error when importing a container: This variable cannot be
    deleted as it is used in other places [by @AltamashShaikh] (Closes:
    #388)
  * FB pixel changed data type to string from INT [by @AltamashShaikh]
    (Closes: #390)
  * Unable to access MatamoTagManager variable in
    matomoTagManagerAsyncInit [by @FalkHe] (Closes: #400)
  * Make import and publish version faster when there are many
    tags/triggers [by @tsteur] (Closes: #387)
  * Detect new brands: Parrot Mobile, Bubblegum and Detect devices for
    existing brands: Kalley, Multilaser, ZTE, Hyundai, Oukitel, HTC,
    Leagoo, Doogee, Tanix, TCL, Hoozo, Rombica, Polar, GEOFOX, Acer,
