matomo (4.6.1-1) stable; urgency=high

  * Releasing Matomo 4.6.1
  * Dashboard shows proportional evolution comparison for incomplete
    periods (rather than absolute values) [by @peterhashair, @bx80]
    (Closes: #6784)
  * Row Evolution, Support Per-Goals and Ecommerce metrics: conversions,
    conversion rate, revenue and total revenue [by @sgiehl] (Closes:
    #3883)
  * Transitions reports: export full data as XML/JSON [by @bx80]
    (Closes: #6032)
  * Show difference in graphs for data of "unfinished periods" and
    "complete periods" [by @bx80] (Closes: #10291)
  * Remember "Rows to display" user preference for Evolution graphs [by
    @sgiehl] (Closes: #14370)
  * Scheduled tasks should not launch archiving [by @peterhashair]
    (Closes: #17976)
  * Ensure that the archive algorithm cannot be triggered multiple times
    for a same site/period/segment (Closes: #8444)
  * JavaScript Tracker: Add possibility to set URL parameters to ignore
    [by @bx80] (Closes: #11627)
  * Improve in-app feedback mechanism to gain insight from users about
    pain points [by @bx80] (Closes: #18186)
  * Optimise ecommerce life time metric query [by @samjf] (Closes:
    #18036)
  * Make error messages not leak potentially sensitive information when
    tracker db connection fails  [by @peterhashair] (Closes: #18079)
  * Ensure DNS records are only requested for IP allowlist when needed
    [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #18244)
  * Remove "refer us" feature [by @peterhashair] (Closes: #18232)
  * Remove review popup [by @peterhashair] (Closes: #18250)
  * Collect feedback about what features people are using? [by
    @peterhashair] (Closes: #18251)
  * Column names could stick to the top of screen when scrolling down
    report tables [by @peterhashair] (Closes: #3513)
  * More verbose error message when login nonce check fails [by
    @peterhashair] (Closes: #16607)
  * Install routine: Fix text contrast for accessibility [by
    @donovanglover, @sgiehl] (Closes: #18164)
  * Add config option to disable http requests in System Checks to
    prevent server crashes with mod_security [by @geekdenz,
    @justinvelluppillai] (Closes: #17589)
  * [database_tests] section no longer generated when executing php
    tests [by @peterhashair] (Closes: #17856)
  * JSONp API request (with callback) strips first and last character
    from result [by @justinvelluppillai] (Closes: #18133)
  * Fix segment creation fails when enable_create_realtime_segments = 0
    [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #18178)
  * Newsletter Signup in personal settings, mention Matomo privacy
    policy applies [by @bx80] (Closes: #18313)
  * Improve UI of report info icon to show report generation time and
    help message [by @peterhashair] (Closes: #17815)
  * Add system check for 32 bit PHP / OS [by @peterhashair] (Closes:
    #18058)
  * New console command "marketplace:add-license-key" which adds a
    marketplace license key [by @ziegenberg] (Closes: #18070)
  * Add more granular access control for segment creation [by
    @peterhashair] (Closes: #18107)
  * Close Tooltip when redirecting to another page [by @jonathannoel]
    (Closes: #18162)
  * Improve performance of Process::isSupported by caching it [by
    @tsteur, @sgiehl] (Closes: #18152)
  * Make cli archiving faster if only one concurrent request per website
    is configured [by @tsteur] (Closes: #18157)
  * Fix initial export option values so checkbox shows correct value [by
    @sgiehl] (Closes: #18172)
  * Updates davaxi/sparkline to 2.0 to PHP8.1 compatible version [by
    @sgiehl, @tsteur] (Closes: #18211)
  * Fix CSP issue when viewing marketplace plugin details [by @sgiehl,
    @tsteur] (Closes: #18215)
  * Mention guides for Wix, WordPress, SquareSpace, Sharepoint in the
    "No data" email and in the "Tracking code" page [by @bx80] (Closes:
    #15429)
  * Fix 2-lines label overflows the input [by @peterhashair] (Closes:
    #17602)
  * Install routine: language changer line height improvements (Closes:
    #17786)
  * Improve help text on 'Users' report when no data [by @peterhashair]
    (Closes: #11175)
  * When "average generation time" is zero, hide the sparkline and "Avg
    generation time" graphs metric from picker  [by @peterhashair]
    (Closes: #17010)
  * Remove "add new segment" selector in segment editor  [by
    @peterhashair] (Closes: #17890)
  * Manage Users: When user is admin, mention other users might exist
    [by @peterhashair] (Closes: #17996)
  * Remove Provider and CustomVariables plugin from our core release [by
    @peterhashair] (Closes: #17973)
  * Update list of no longer supported browsers (IE11) [by @tsteur]
    (Closes: #18011)
  * Make SecurityPolicy methods a public API and fully enable the CSP
    [by @justinvelluppillai] (Closes: #17923)
  * Tracking request may trigger a warning when providing an invalid
    regex [by @diosmosis, @peterhashair] (Closes: #16153)
  * Special character apostrophe is not getting printed properly in
    visits log (campaign url) [by @diosmosis, @bx80] (Closes: #14695)
  * Fix dashboard showing incorrect percentage on increases bigger than
    1000% (Closes: #16067)
  * Include lox/xhprof in the Matomo build release so Profiling works
    [by @tsteur] (Closes: #17939)
  * Make the opt out work when a PHP 32 bit is used [by @peterhashair]
    (Closes: #18019)
  * Fixed in place sorting order bug for PHP8+ (Closes: #18130)
  * Fix annotations for "Behaviour > Performance" StackedBarEvolution
    charts [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #18231)
  * Decode goal top dimension values [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #18267)
  * Add field lastSeen in the API for the UsersManager [by
    @peterhashair] (Closes: #10550)
  * Introduce new config setting to set a contact email address [by
    @sgiehl] (Closes: #17916)
  * [Vue] Introduce Vue + Workflow commands [by @diosmosis, @sgiehl]
    (Closes: #17940)
  * Provide console command for adding a marketplace license key
    (#18070) [by @ziegenberg, @tsteur] (Closes: #18071)
  * Update container factory to allow for sorting plugins [by
    @JasonMortonNZ, @tsteur] (Closes: #18074)
  * Use detachEvent when removeEventListener isn't available [by
    @peterhashair, @justinvelluppillai] (Closes: #18110)
  * Don't browser archive when segment is set to be pre-processed [by
    @tsteur] (Closes: #18123)
  * Make the Twig cache template path more configurable with a DI entry
    [by @samjf, @tsteur] (Closes: #18137)
  * Fix error cannot read property "replace" of undefined in quick
    search [by @tsteur, @justinvelluppillai] (Closes: #18149)
  * Small optimisations to Archiving performance [by @samjf, @tsteur]
    (Closes: #18156)
  * [Vue] Migrate content-block, enriched-headline, rate-feature +
    related [by @diosmosis, @sgiehl] (Closes: #18166)
  * Fix possible problem with CSP in overlay feature [by @sgiehl]
    (Closes: #18187)
  * [Vue] migrate comparisons service + component [by @diosmosis]
    (Closes: #18193)
  * Always remove hash part from URL when detecting the script name [by
    @sgiehl] (Closes: #18204)
  * [Vue] migrate date-picker and other period-selector related
    components [by @diosmosis] (Closes: #18213)
  * [Vue] migrate dropdown and related directives [by @diosmosis,
    @sgiehl] (Closes: #18214)
  * [Vue] migrate notifications directive & service + UI.Notifications
    [by @diosmosis, @sgiehl] (Closes: #18225)
  * Changes to keep sorting order consistent across all PHP versions for
    Live.getLastVisitsDetails API [by @AltamashShaikh,
    @justinvelluppillai] (Closes: #18235)
  * Take archive TTL time into consideration for today when browser
    archiving is enabled [by @tsteur, @sgiehl] (Closes: #18241)
  * Fix archiving too many segments that aren't needed and showing 0
    conversions for new visits/returning visitors [by @tsteur] (Closes:
    #18255)
  * Support downloading system tests from plugins [by @tsteur] (Closes:
    #18263)
  * Remove cache clearing from forget invalidations loop. [by @samjf,
    @tsteur] (Closes: #18278)
  * Corrected paths mentioning "piwik/" to "/path/to/matomo/". [by
    @cherouvim, @sgiehl] (Closes: #18300)
  * Couple of fixes in QuickForm2 for PHP8.1 compatibility [by @sgiehl,
    @tsteur] (Closes: #18309)
  * Enable Debugging mode without URL parameter [by @AltamashShaikh]
    (Closes: #217)
  * Right clicks trigger twice for "All Links Click" and "All Elements
    Click" in Firefox (Closes: #375)
  * Fix deprecation warning on PHP 8.1 [by @sgiehl, @tsteur] (Closes:
    #378)
  * Add detection for Google Podcasts (Closes: #5773)
  * Improvements for the OS parser a second level of regular expressions
    has been added [by @sanchezzzhak] (Closes: #6793)
  * Detect devices for existing brands: Xiaomi, Samsung, Realme, Tecno
    Mobile, Mobicel, Vivo, Lenovo, ZTE, OPPO, Oukitel, CUBOT, UMIDIGI,
    OnePlus, Ulefone, Doogee, TCL, Vivo, Vertex, Infinix, Kr"uger&Matz,
    Wiko, DEXP, BQ [by @sanchezzzhak, @sgiehl] (Closes: #6870)
  * Detect new brand Nubia [by @sanchezzzhak, @sgiehl] (Closes: #6872)
  * Detect new brands: Bluebird, Mara and Detect devices for existing
    brands: Kr"uger&Matz, iHunt, Sony, Teclast, Tanix, Logicom, Nubia,
    Xiaomi, QMobile, DIXON, Zuum, Vodacom, Mobicel, Oukitel, Motorola,
    Stylo, Tecno Mobile, Chuwi, OnePlus, Vivo, iTel, Doogee, Cat,
    Homtom, CUBOT, MLS, Blu, Casper, Unonu [by @sanchezzzhak, @sgiehl]
    (Closes: #6873)
  * Detect new brands: BMAX, Geotex and Detect devices for existing
    brands: Telefunken, Asus, Huawei, Lenovo, Tecno Mobile, Nomi,
    Coolpad, Blu, Navitel, Winnovo, Digiland, DEXP, Sony, Inoi, OPPO,
    Samsung, Xiaomi, LG, Vivo, UMIDIGI, Mobicel, Teclast, Zuum [by
    @sanchezzzhak, @sgiehl] (Closes: #6874)
  * Detect new brand: Rakuten and Detect devices for existing brands:
    Beelink, Sony, Blackview, Samsung, NUU Mobile, Oukitel, Coolpad, LG,
    DEXP, Acer, ZTE, TCL, Mobicel, Contixo, BQ, ONYX BOOX, Mecer, Digma,
    Lenovo, RCA Tablets, Intex, Huawei, Santin, Vivo, NOA, iTel, Sharp,
    Prestigio, HTC, OnePlus, Wiko, Fly, Meizu, Lava, Gionee  [by
    @sanchezzzhak, @sgiehl] (Closes: #6877)
  * detect the device type for other browsers (Huawei, Quark,
    MQQBrowser) (Closes: #6878)
  * Detect devices for existing brands: Vivo, Huawei, ZTE, Smartisan,
    Samsung, OPPO, HTC, Xiaolajiao, POCO, Xiaomi, Blu [by @sanchezzzhak,
    @sgiehl] (Closes: #6879)
  * Adds detection for Apple iPhone 13 models [by @liviuconcioiu,
    @sanchezzzhak] (Closes: #6880)
  * Detect device type for chrome forks [by @sanchezzzhak, @sgiehl]
    (Closes: #6881)
  * Detect devices for existing brands: Vivo, HTC, Hisense, Gionee,
    Huawei, Samsung, Realme, Blu, NOA [by @sanchezzzhak, @sgiehl]
    (Closes: #6883)
  * Detect oss: Java ME, REX [by @sanchezzzhak, @sgiehl] (Closes: #6885)
  * Detect new brand: DING DING and Detect devices for existing brands:
    Zopo, F2 Mobile, iBall, Kr"uger&Matz, Hotwav, Orange, Tecno Mobile,
    Runbo, Vonino, M4tel, Kempler & Strauss, Rokit, Stylo, DEXP,
    Prestigio, Mobicel, Santin [by @sanchezzzhak, @sgiehl] (Closes:
    #6886)
  * Detect devices for existing brands: X-TIGI, Prestigio, Micromax, LG,
    DEXP, Oukitel, Hurricane, Alcatel, M4tel, Blackview, S-TELL,
    Coolpad, HTC, Teclast, Mecer, Huawei, Reeder, Orange, Mobicel,
    Realme, NUU Mobile, Xiaomi, Huawei, Hisense, Zuum, Kr"uger&Matz,
    Motorola [by @sanchezzzhak, @sgiehl] (Closes: #6888)
  * Adds detection for GitHub Desktop and Logi Options+ apps [by
    @liviuconcioiu, @sanchezzzhak] (Closes: #6889)
  * Adds detection for Bonsai, Peeps dBrowser, Flash, Harman, Lagatos,
    LT, PSI, Spectre and Sushi Browsers [by @liviuconcioiu,
    @sanchezzzhak] (Closes: #6890)
  * Adds detection for Roku OS [by @liviuconcioiu, @sgiehl] (Closes:
    #6891)
  * Adds detection for OpenWrt OS and uclient-fetch library [by
    @liviuconcioiu, @sgiehl] (Closes: #6892)
  * Adds detection for multiples apps and improves iOS, Windows, iPhone,
    iPod detection [by @liviuconcioiu, @sanchezzzhak] (Closes: #6894)
  * Detect devices for existing brands: Nubia, F150, Vivo, Huawei,
    Realme, Google, Oukitel, TCL, Packard Bell, Xiaomi, Cube, Lenovo,
    OnePlus, iHunt, Proline, Reeder, Stylo, Hurricane, OPPO, Mobicel,
    Ugoos, Beeline, 4Good, Teclast, K-Touch, Prestigio, Tecno Mobile,
    AllDocube, Ravoz, T-Mobile, DIXON, Motorola, Asus [by @sanchezzzhak,
    @sgiehl] (Closes: #6895)
  * Detect new brands: Trident, SUNWIND, OKSI, Taiga System and Detect
    devices for existing brands: TechPad, Santin, Realme, Meizu,
    Alcatel, Xiaomi, ONN, UMIDIGI, DEXP, Premio, Oukitel, Coolpad, Sky,
    Huawei, Stylo, Mobicel, Casper, Infinix, TCL, Qumo [by
    @sanchezzzhak, @sgiehl] (Closes: #6897)
  * Adds detection for Apple Watch Series 7 [by @liviuconcioiu, @sgiehl]
    (Closes: #6899)
  * Improves detection for Apple devices [by @liviuconcioiu,
    @sanchezzzhak] (Closes: #6900)
  * Improves detection for Hisense, Samsung and TCL devices [by
    @liviuconcioiu, @sanchezzzhak] (Closes: #6901)
  * Improves Android, iPadOS, iOS, macOS version detection [by
    @liviuconcioiu, @sanchezzzhak] (Closes: #6902)
  * Improves detection for iOS, iPadOS, macOS, Android, Windows, Apple,
    Motorola, Samsung and Sony brands, and adds detection for Telco
    brand and various apps [by @liviuconcioiu, @sanchezzzhak] (Closes:
    #6903)
  * Adds detection for Cellution, Juniper Systems, Kazuna, Oculus,
    STRONG, Topelotek brands and improves detection for Alcatel, Amazon,
    ANS, Kocaso, LG, Motorola, Sony, UMIDIGI brands [by @liviuconcioiu,
    @sanchezzzhak] (Closes: #6904)
  * Adds detection for various apps [by @liviuconcioiu, @sanchezzzhak]
    (Closes: #6905)
  * Detect new brands: Glofiish, Polar, MyGica and Detect devices for
    existing brands: Cavion, Stylo, Mobicel, Hurricane, Proline, bq,
    Hisense, Archos, NOA, GOCLEVER, Blackview, Blu [by @sanchezzzhak,
