  * Adds detection for KRIP brand, improves detection for Alcatel, Blu,
    BMobile, Epik One, Gateway, Huawei, Hyundai, IKU Mobile, MobiWire,
    MicroMax, Positivo, Safaricom, TCL, UMIDIGI, Vivo brands and
    improves detection for Opera GX, Windows, x86, x64 platforms [by
    @liviuconcioiu, @sanchezzzhak] (Closes: #6907)
  * Fix for double newline issue when a redirect is used [by
    @JasonMortonNZ, @tsteur] (Closes: #97)
  * Couple of fixes for PHP 8.1 [by @sgiehl, @tsteur] (Closes: #98)

