    @diosmosis] (Closes: #17838)
  * make sure summary rows are serialized with their in-db subtable ID
    and not in memory one [by @diosmosis, @tsteur] (Closes: #17831)
  * Add command to generate a system check [by @tsteur, @diosmosis]
    (Closes: #17832)
