 -- Edouard Gaulué <edouard@e-gaulue.com>  Thu, 17 Feb 2022 10:19:54 +0100

matomo (4.4.0-1) stable; urgency=high

  * Releasing Matomo 4.4.0
  * Send email notifications to a user whenever their settings are
    changed (2FA, token_auth, user is updated or deleted), and to super
    users when security settings are changed (brute force logic, 2FA,
    cors changes) [by @flamisz, @diosmosis] (Closes: #17531)
  * widget: minimize and reload icon [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #17626)
  * setting the cookie domain even when cookies are disabled for
    compatibility with "Require Cookie Consent" feature [by
    @justinvelluppillai] (Closes: #17417)
  * Show more clearly the freshness of reports when looking at Today or
    This week [by @flamisz] (Closes: #14977)
  * Insights widget shows only "Others" page titles [by @flamisz]
    (Closes: #17615)
  * Uncaught exception in API:
    Piwik\Exception\UnexpectedWebsiteFoundException: An unexpected
    website was found in the request: website id was set to '-1' . in
    core/Site.php [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #17759)
  * Allow web cron via POST [by @justinvelluppillai] (Closes: #14190)
  * Ensure redirects from logme method are only done to trusted hosts
    [by @sgiehl, @diosmosis] (Closes: #17661)
  * Disable logme functionality by default [by @sgiehl, @diosmosis]
    (Closes: #17665)
  * Ensure login is correctly detected for brute force detection when
    using logme feature [by @sgiehl, @diosmosis] (Closes: #17677)
  * Make error messages not leak potentially sensitive information when
    db connection fails [by @justinvelluppillai, @diosmosis] (Closes:
    #17789)
  * JS Tracking code should validate with the W3C validator [by
    @justinvelluppillai] (Closes: #17281)
  * System Check showing warning when max_execution_time is set to -1 in
    PHP.ini [by @justinvelluppillai] (Closes: #17585)
  * Sticky "Maximize" tooltip  [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #17625)
  * Support for Tracker INI settings to be set for each website [by
    @diosmosis] (Closes: #17636)
  * <wbr> can be displayed in tooltip in "Row Evolution" [by @sgiehl]
    (Closes: #17679)
  * New console command "core:version" outputs the Matomo version
    information [by @ziegenberg] (Closes: #17755)
  * "Rows to display" cannot be changed if a row is expanded [by
    @justinvelluppillai] (Closes: #17628)
  * Improve purge log data logic to improve speed, and avoid locks in
    some cases [by @tsteur, @diosmosis] (Closes: #17632)
  * for AWS Aurora users and when using a DB Reader: new INI setting to
    enable aurora read replica read committed for fixing purge lag
    performance issue [by @justinvelluppillai, @diosmosis] (Closes:
    #17718)
  * Fix redirect link not working after plugin activation [by @Findus23,
    @diosmosis] (Closes: #17654)
  * Fix parameters of UsersManager.addUser.end event [by @sgiehl,
    @diosmosis] (Closes: #17678)
  * Warning - session_regenerate_id(): Cannot regenerate session id -
    session is not active [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #17737)
  * UI: Disabling browser archiving is not clear it does not disable
    browser archiving for segment [by @justinvelluppillai] (Closes:
    #17479)
  * Publish new Cloudflare App for Matomo (Closes: #17068)
  * PHP 8.1 compatibility: fix "Deprecated - glob(): Passing null to
    parameter #2 ($flags) of type int is deprecated" [by @Findus23,
    @diosmosis] (Closes: #17687)
  * PHP 8.1 compatibility, fix "Warning - foreach() argument must be of
    type" [by @Findus23, @diosmosis] (Closes: #17688)
  * PHP 8.1 compatibility, fix "Deprecated - explode(): Passing null to
    parameter" [by @Findus23, @diosmosis] (Closes: #17693)
  * Add link to new FAQ how to make the diagnostic "Managing processes
    via CLI" show Ok [by @mattab, @diosmosis] (Closes: #17527)
  * Allow plugins to abort sending emails via 'Mail.send' event [by
    @diosmosis] (Closes: #17635)
  * JS Tracker: new setPageViewId function to override the pageviewid
    and not have it auto generated  [by @JE4GLE, @diosmosis] (Closes:
    #17655)
  * Add possiblity to open sites manager and directly edit a specific
    site using URL parameter [by @tsteur, @diosmosis] (Closes: #17726)
  * Make anchor links on Admin General Settings page work [by @tsteur]
    (Closes: #17727)
  * Fix preselection in site selector form fields [by @sgiehl,
    @diosmosis] (Closes: #17742)
  * Matomo application logs can now be written in syslog and errorlog
    [by @mwithheld, @diosmosis] (Closes: #17764)
  * Bad filesystem detection (NFS) (Closes: #12217)
  * Outlink and download tracking not working for links added after DOM
    ready (which many are these days eg angular, vue.js, react, ...
    SPA). [by @flamisz] (Closes: #15780)
  * In Tag Manager, Manage Containers page is blank [by @tsteur]
    (Closes: #16672)
  * When embedding a widget with the "Multisites" report (All websites),
    the links are not working [by @justinvelluppillai] (Closes: #17001)
  * Exporting main metrics with a period of "week" as CSV produces
    broken exports [by @ziegenberg] (Closes: #17441)
  * JS Tracking code may generate "The operation is insecure" warnings
    with specific Firefox settings [by @justinvelluppillai] (Closes:
    #17454)
  * Make sure that all segment archives are invalidated when
    invalidating all visits archives [by @diosmosis] (Closes: #17617)
  * ComparisonRowGenerator::compareTables() must implement interface
    Piwik\\DataTable\\DataTableInterface or be null, (Closes: #17641)
  * In Diagnostics, fix edge case "Warning - trim() expects parameter 1
    to be string, array given" [by @diosmosis, @sgiehl] (Closes: #17653)
  * When using PDO to connect to the database, a failed connection might
    trigger a PDOException [by @sgiehl, @diosmosis] (Closes: #17670)
  * Make sure overlay API requests send force_api_session as POST param
    [by @diosmosis] (Closes: #17675)
  * Fix issue "Call to a member function getMainUrl() on null" in
    permission checks in siteWithoutData method [by @sgiehl] (Closes:
    #17694)
  * Fix few bugs in sparklines visualisation when there is no row [by
    @tsteur, @diosmosis] (Closes: #17728)
  * activating non-existing plugin via console plugin:activate results
    in uncaught exception and plugin is listed as installed afterwards
    [by @diosmosis] (Closes: #17770)
  * If table prefix is not specified, the database abilities diagnostic
    can fail [by @diosmosis, @sgiehl] (Closes: #17771)
  * Call to a member function getSubtableDimension() on null in
    core/DataTable/Filter/PivotByDimension.php [by @sgiehl] (Closes:
    #17775)
  * Call to undefined method Piwik\\DataTable\\Map::getRowFromLabel() in
    plugins/UserCountry/API.php [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #17776)
  * in PHP 8.0, when enabling MySQL SSL, got a HTTP 500  (Closes:
    #17782)
  * Update PHP extension requirements & deprecate Common::mb_* methods
    [by @sgiehl, @diosmosis] (Closes: #16754)
  * more private Referrer-Policy: use strict-origin-when-cross-origin
    [by @Findus23, @diosmosis] (Closes: #17382)
  * Add query string to error logs [by @diosmosis] (Closes: #17472)
  * Use CLI archiving in more places for more reliable archiving (by not
    using the 'which' tool) [by @diosmosis] (Closes: #17576)
  * invalidate-report-data console to show a timestamp in the output [by
    @diosmosis] (Closes: #17633)
  * Remove archive status locking since it is not needed anymore [by
    @diosmosis] (Closes: #17657)
  * Ignore invalid capabilities instead of throwing an exception [by
    @sgiehl, @diosmosis] (Closes: #17660)
  * Add extra info when two non-summable columns are added together for
    easier debugging  [by @diosmosis] (Closes: #17664)
  * Move tests documentation to developer website [by @tsteur,
    @diosmosis] (Closes: #17668)
  * Link to Drupal or WebFlow Matomo FAQ when the website is detected to
    use it [by @sgiehl, @diosmosis] (Closes: #17671)
  * Improves detection of local hostnames [by @sgiehl, @diosmosis]
    (Closes: #17681)
  * add config to read the last IP address in the list of proxies rather
    than the first [by @diosmosis] (Closes: #17765)
  * When reading IP address, do not ignore remote_addr if reading the
    last ip in proxy header lists [by @tsteur] (Closes: #17790)
  * Add "AllowOverride" to faq/troubleshooting/how-do-i-fix-the-error-
    private-directories-are-accessible [by @tsteur] (Closes: #17819)
  * Archiving may fail when also using roll up reporting [by @tsteur,
    @mattab] (Closes: #17822)
  * Make sure bot categories are consistent in bots.yml  (Closes: #5727)
  * Adds detection for iPadOS operating system [by @liviuconcioiu,
    @sanchezzzhak] (Closes: #6624)
  * Adds detection for Maelstrom browser [by @liviuconcioiu, @sgiehl]
    (Closes: #6626)
  * Adds detection for Arvin browser [by @liviuconcioiu, @sgiehl]
    (Closes: #6647)
  * Adds detection for Mandarin browser [by @liviuconcioiu, @sgiehl]
    (Closes: #6686)
  * Ensure the useragent is a string, to avoid php error (Closes: #6697)
  * Detect new brands: Spectralink, Vega, Bleck, TurboPad and Detect
    devices for existing brands: DEXP, ZTE, MiXzo, Lava, VGO TEL, AT&T,
    CUBOT, Oysters, NEXON, Alfawise, CHIA, Mobicel, Casper, Wiko,
    Beeline, BIHEE, AllDocube, Xiaomi, Blu, Blackview, OPPO, Vivo,
    Realme, Motorola, Allwinner, MyPhone, TurboKids, Kivi, Vernee,
    Teclast [by @sanchezzzhak] (Closes: #6742)
  * Adds detection for Odnoklassniki mobile app  [by @sanchezzzhak,
    @sgiehl] (Closes: #6743)
  * Adds detection for My World mobile app  [by @sanchezzzhak, @sgiehl]
    (Closes: #6744)
  * Detect new brand: STG Telecom and Detect devices for existing
    brands: Lava, Telenor, Mito, LT, IconBIT, Cloudfone, Bitmore, Tecno
    Mobile, Danew, LG, Mpman, EXO, Digma, Walton, EvroMedia, LG, Celkon,
    Huawei, Phicomm, Wiko [by @sanchezzzhak] (Closes: #6748)
  * Detect devices for existing brands: Coolpad, Samsung, Sharp, Sony,
    Xiaomi, Kyocera [by @sanchezzzhak, @sgiehl] (Closes: #6752)
  * Detect new brand: Revo, RoyQueen, Axioo and Detect devices for
    existing brands: Runbo, EE, E-Boda, Navon, Ramos, Invens, Karbonn,
    RoverPad, Q.Bell, GFive, Quantum. Sky, Vivax, SWISSMOBILITY, Oysters
    [by @sanchezzzhak] (Closes: #6753)
  * Detect new brand: Rivo, Four Mobile and Detect devices for existing
    brands: Mito, Melrose, Medion, Manta Multimedia, Multilaser, M-Tech
    [by @sanchezzzhak, @sgiehl] (Closes: #6754)
  * Detect new brand: New Balance, Astro, Cobalt, FMT, mPhone, WIWA and
    Detect devices for existing brands: Asus, Maxwest, Intex, Celkon,
    Woxter, LG, Zuum [by @sanchezzzhak] (Closes: #6755)
  * Adds detection for Tecno Mobile devices [by @liviuconcioiu,
    @sanchezzzhak] (Closes: #6756)
  * Detect new brand: Inch, Jeka, KREZ, Kurio, UZ Mobile, L-Max, UTime
    and Detect devices for existing brands: Vsmart, Unihertz, Huawei,
    Jinga, DNS, BB Mobile, Inco, Verico, ZTE, Highscreen, MyPhone,
    Oukitel, OnePlus, Alcatel, Xiaomi, Irbis, Zopo [by @sanchezzzhak]
    (Closes: #6758)
