matomo (4.3.1-1) stable; urgency=high

  * Releasing Matomo 4.3.1
  * Banner to ask to refer users can be annoying [by @flamisz] (Closes:
    #17571)
  * Uploading logo logs out users [by @flamisz] (Closes: #17586)
  * Creating/updating segments w/ values w/ encoded chars does not auto
    schedule rearchiving (Closes: #17583)
  * Rename dimension called "Measurable" to "Website name"  [by
    @flamisz] (Closes: #17107)
  * report information: "Report generated" without time unit (seconds?)
    [by @flamisz] (Closes: #17567)
  * Alexa.php(40): Warning - DOMDocument::loadHTML(): Unexpected end tag
    [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #17578)
  * Visitor Map shows no visits for all regions of Greece (matomo
    4.2.1/geoip2 lite) [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #17590)
  * Improves Geolocation diagnostics [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #17573)
  * Ignore performance metrics that are obviously too high [by @sgiehl,
    @tsteur] (Closes: #17574)
  * HeatmapSessionRecording.addHeatmap failed (Closes: #17580)
  * Improve required private directories check [by @tsteur] (Closes:
    #17606)
  * Licence Mismatch (Closes: #93)
  * Improves detection for LinkedIn app  [by @sanchezzzhak, @sgiehl]
    (Closes: #6749)
