 -- Edouard Gaulué <edouard@e-gaulue.com>  Thu, 17 Feb 2022 01:07:16 +0100

matomo (4.3.0-1) stable; urgency=high

  * Releasing Matomo 4.3.0
  * Display Inline help icon linking to User Guide, for all features
    with a user guide [by @diosmosis] (Closes: #4481)
  * When accessing UI with unsupported browser throw error and suggest
    to use other browser [by @flamisz] (Closes: #16776)
  * Remove the "Visitor ID" segment when the "Visitor profile" feature
    has been disabled [by @flamisz] (Closes: #17488)
  * Setting process_new_segments_from not respected when archiving
    bigger periods [by @flamisz] (Closes: #17336)
  * Performance report table not displayed properly [by @flamisz]
    (Closes: #17242)
  * Show periods labels in the evolution graphs to make it easier to
    change period [by @flamisz] (Closes: #15021)
  * Store the segment hash in the DB table [by @flamisz] (Closes:
    #17301)
  * Invalidate segment data on update only if the definition changes [by
    @sgiehl] (Closes: #17444)
  * Display the "oops" red error message, only when there was an error,
    do not show it when user clicks away to load another menu or page
    (Closes: #10578)
  * Allow selecting password_hash algorithm [by @Findus23, @diosmosis]
    (Closes: #17199)
  * Performance metrics issues after 4.2 update [by @flamisz] (Closes:
    #17259)
  * Row evolution on subtables can cause errors randomly [by @sgiehl]
    (Closes: #17374)
  * Marketplace: "more" link does not work [by @flamisz] (Closes:
    #17561)
  * Ask for password confirmation before installing all plugins [by
    @sgiehl, @diosmosis] (Closes: #17285)
  * vendor/composer/installed.json is exposed publicly [by @sgiehl]
    (Closes: #17378)
  * Escape URL in geolocation admin error message [by @sgiehl,
    @diosmosis] (Closes: #17436)
  * detect brute force login attempts from different ip addresses [by
    @diosmosis] (Closes: #17503)
  * Ensure redirects in HTTP class are only done to allowed protocols
    (for cURL) [by @sgiehl, @diosmosis] (Closes: #17524)
  * Use Common::safe_unserialize for session data [by @sgiehl,
    @diosmosis] (Closes: #17539)
  * Add plugin name as comment to SQL query (Closes: #17327)
  * Email export as TSV format [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #17463)
  * Error Message notification is not hidden when navigating to a new
    page [by @flamisz] (Closes: #17104)
  * JS Error tracking should record the same error only once per page
    view [by @flamisz] (Closes: #17163)
  * Improve tracker performance when using custom dimensions (one less
    update query per tracking request) (Closes: #17173)
  * Don't load review logos if they are not shown (Closes: #17422)
  * Unwanted date filter automatically added to
    Live.getLastVisitsDetails [by @flamisz] (Closes: #17237)
  * Initiate range archiving if an archive is invalidated, the request
    is from the browser, and browser archiving is authorized [by
    @diosmosis] (Closes: #17379)
  * Exporting "Visitor Profile" data results in "Your session has
    expired due to inactivity. Please log in to continue." [by @sgiehl]
    (Closes: #17407)
  * Re-allow tracking bots (Closes: #17497)
  * Allow invalidating empty site [by @diosmosis] (Closes: #17519)
  * Improve no data tracked yet please set up tracking code screen [by
    @flamisz] (Closes: #16787)
  * When a period has no data, but raw data, show a message [by
    @flamisz] (Closes: #16790)
  * In "Help" screen, show first the section "How can we help?" [by
    @flamisz] (Closes: #17108)
  * the "Compare to" button design has slightly regressed on firefox
    only [by @flamisz] (Closes: #17162)
  * icon for informational system check [by @Findus23, @diosmosis]
    (Closes: #17389)
  * better systemcheck error boxes [by @Findus23, @diosmosis] (Closes:
    #17416)
  * replace generate:plugin warning with pointer to guide [by @flamisz]
    (Closes: #16922)
  * When showing the Export URL, clarify that users must use their app
    token (instead of displaying a token_auth that only works in their
    session) (Closes: #16990)
  * rename testcookie to make it clear it is created by Matomo [by
    @Findus23, @diosmosis] (Closes: #17243)
  * Don't allow enforcing 2FA unless the superuser has set it up already
    (Closes: #17352)
  * French Guiana shows up as France in maps and reports [by @sgiehl]
    (Closes: #5056)
  * France regions are not up-to-date (Closes: #15203)
  * Ask users to refer us to other friends [by @flamisz] (Closes:
    #16803)
  * Translation missed on "Create a new user" [by @flamisz] (Closes:
    #17086)
  * Improve configuration of rearchive_reports_in_past_last_n_months
    setting [by @diosmosis] (Closes: #17366)
  * more markdown friendly system checks [by @Findus23, @diosmosis]
    (Closes: #17421)
  * Run Javascript tests with node/puppeteer as well as Phantomjs [by
    @sgiehl] (Closes: #17424)
  * Add date period to segment archive queries [by @flamisz] (Closes:
    #17330)
  * Avoid double HTML entities / special characters encoding [by
    @flamisz] (Closes: #14065)
  * Hide Unique Visitors from email reports when the metric is not
    activated for this period [by @diosmosis] (Closes: #16222)
  * Site Search hover help bug [by @TheCrowned] (Closes: #16374)
  * core/Cookie.php:Cookie->delete() don't set secure and SameSite.
    (Closes: #16637)
  * Prevent new username from using existing user email address [by
    @flamisz] (Closes: #17070)
  * Matomo comparing month report with same month when clicking on the
    last day of the month [by @flamisz] (Closes: #17080)
  * fatal error: Modulo by zero: method=imageGraph while widht = 0
    (Closes: #17092)
  * CSV reports can fail because HTTP Content-Disposition header has
    invalid characters in the filename field [by @flamisz] (Closes:
    #17209)
  * trackPageView still sends page performance report after
    disablePerformanceTracking [by @tsteur] (Closes: #17267)
  * archiving: look for all usable done flag types when checking for
    existing child periods [by @diosmosis] (Closes: #17304)
  * Widgetize request with token_auth param fails if superuser session
    exists [by @flamisz] (Closes: #17335)
  * Installer starts over after asking super user details (Closes:
    #17362)
  * Ensure correct no access message is shown [by @sgiehl] (Closes:
    #17445)
  * work around group_concat max len being too small in
    ArchiveSelector.getArchiveIds [by @diosmosis] (Closes: #17496)
  * Our work process when changing or removing a public API from the
    Matomo platform [by @mattab] (Closes: #8126)
  * Making it easier to know when a code review is required [by @tsteur]
    (Closes: #17317)
  * Developer Changelog and documenting changes in the Matomo Platform
    [by @mattab] (Closes: #8127)
  * In core:invalidate-report-data match segments by ID, name or
    definition ... [by @diosmosis] (Closes: #16994)
  * Add informational diagnostic for archive invalidations table. [by
    @diosmosis] (Closes: #17110)
  * Use https for urls in visitor details if host is defined with https
    in site [by @sgiehl, @diosmosis] (Closes: #17151)
  * Do not append performance metrics to page view log if performance
    tracking disabled [by @ufoproger, @diosmosis] (Closes: #17268)
  * Fix Marketplace falsely thinks a plugin is installed when it is not
    [by @tsteur, @diosmosis] (Closes: #17278)
  * remove dangling invalidation check (no longer needed) [by
    @diosmosis] (Closes: #17289)
  * Prevent possible warning during GeoIP2 update if providers aren't
    initialised [by @tsteur, @sgiehl] (Closes: #17295)
  * remove deletion of old archives in CronArchive since we do this in
    ArchiveWriter, and it is buggy here [by @diosmosis] (Closes: #17314)
  * Make sure not to clear the tracker cache so often when invalidating
    in core:archive [by @diosmosis] (Closes: #17321)
  * Allow configuring segments to not be rearchived when rearchiving
    reports in the past. [by @diosmosis] (Closes: #17325)
  * Add -skip-cache-clear option to core:update command  ... [by
    @diosmosis] (Closes: #17326)
  * allow forcing Archive to not initiate archiving for child archives
    [by @diosmosis] (Closes: #17331)
  * Add extra core:archive log for initiation of logging [by @diosmosis]
    (Closes: #17332)
  * Add event tags to top and bottom of body [by @MHarmony, @diosmosis]
    (Closes: #17333)
  * Require password confirmation for more plugin operations. [by
    @diosmosis] (Closes: #17345)
  * Ensure login allow list is not checked for authenticated tracking
    requests [by @sgiehl, @diosmosis] (Closes: #17357)
  * check for openssl extension [by @Findus23, @diosmosis] (Closes:
    #17364)
  * Warning in 2fa setting: gmdate() expects parameter 2 to be int [by
    @tsteur, @diosmosis] (Closes: #17365)
  * Apache 2.4+ compatibility for misc/cron/.htaccess [by @jorisdrenth,
    @diosmosis] (Closes: #17387)
  * Use ranking query in custom dimensions archiver [by @diosmosis]
    (Closes: #17396)
  * Disallow enable 2FA requirement when user doesn't have 2FA enabled
    [by @andyjdavis, @diosmosis] (Closes: #17400)
  * fix ScheduledReports.sendReport API [by @Findus23, @diosmosis]
    (Closes: #17402)
  * Do not allow setting partial archives to DONE_INVALIDATED [by
    @diosmosis] (Closes: #17437)
  * [automatic submodule updates] [by @github-actions[bot], @sgiehl]
    (Closes: #17438)
  * INI process_new_segments_from: allow processing segments X days
    before last edit day [by @sgiehl, @diosmosis] (Closes: #17447)
  * Workaround error in Overlay when site has no URLs [by @diosmosis]
    (Closes: #17457)
  * Add get-segment-sql development command for debugging [by
    @diosmosis] (Closes: #17461)
  * Add comment about using shop@innocraft.com for premium features [by
    @diosmosis] (Closes: #17477)
  * Add diagnostic that checks if server directories that should be
    private are accessible [by @diosmosis] (Closes: #17490)
  * no links in copy-paste system check [by @Findus23, @tsteur] (Closes:
    #17515)
  * Do not confuse normal rows with the label "-1" w/ the summary row
    [by @diosmosis] (Closes: #17517)
  * require password confirmation when resetting 2fa [by @diosmosis]
    (Closes: #17528)
  * add new ini config to enable/disable the php profiler feature [by
    @diosmosis] (Closes: #17537)
  * Add option to skip log purging check when invalidating archives in
    the rare cases it is needed. [by @diosmosis] (Closes: #17538)
  * more neutral wording and other style improvements [by @Findus23,
    @sgiehl] (Closes: #17540)
  * If no archives names are requested when querying archive data, do
    not initiate archiving. [by @diosmosis] (Closes: #17547)
  * Make sure summary row subtables are included in the serialized
    representaion of a datatable tree. [by @diosmosis, @tsteur] (Closes:
    #17569)
  * iOS/macOS apps not detected correctly (Closes: #6604)
  * Adds detection for Lumin OS and Helio browser [by @liviuconcioiu,
    @sanchezzzhak] (Closes: #6656)
  * Adds detection for DVKBuntu operating system [by @liviuconcioiu,
    @sgiehl] (Closes: #6671)
  * Detect new brands: Seatel, 3GNET, IT, Jiake, Malata, Ditecma,
    Datamini, Newsday and Detect devices for existing brands: Leotec,
    Navon, Evolveo, Cherry Mobile, iPro, Odys, Iris, Maxwest, iTel [by
    @sanchezzzhak] (Closes: #6694)
  * Detect new brands: iQ&T, Pixela, Datalogic, Navitel, Naomi Phone,
    Mantra, Maximus, Navcity, Linnex and Detect devices for existing
    brands: Inco, MicroMax, IMO Mobile, Blu, Kzen, Cherry Mobile,
    Altron, Evercoss, Leagoo, Leader Phone, Lava [by @sanchezzzhak]
    (Closes: #6695)
  * Fixes detection for Aloha browser [by @zudwalex, @sanchezzzhak]
    (Closes: #6698)
  * Detect library: Embarcadero URI Client and app: Rucket Chat and
    bots: Ryowl, Sputnik Favicon Bot, Sputnik Image Bot, Hatena Favicon
    [by @sanchezzzhak] (Closes: #6699)
  * Detect new brands: Suzuki, Nabi, Gresso, G-Touch, FaRao Pro,
    StrawBerry, Smartab, Subor, SuperTab, Pendoo, Engel and Detect
    devices for existing brands: Sugar, TrekStor, Ghia, Lenovo, Freetel,
    Lark, Zidoo, Sony, Siragon, SPC, Karbonn, Bitel, Cloudfone, Navon,
    Ritmix, Starlight, Zuum, Blu, Dune HD, Philco [by @sanchezzzhak,
