matomo (4.2.1-1) stable; urgency=high

  * Releasing Matomo 4.2.1
  * Make all cookies httpOnly [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #17270)
  * Segments are not deleted when User is deleted [by @flamisz] (Closes:
    #13976)
  * possibly avoid infinite looping if group_concat cuts off result [by
    @diosmosis] (Closes: #17244)
  * Only force single plugin archiving for root archive requests. [by
    @diosmosis] (Closes: #17250)
  * Critical error during database upgrade "The date '-0001-11-30' is a
    date before first website was online" when updating to 4.2.0
    (Closes: #17253)
  * [automatic translation update] Updated 295 strings in 8 languages
    (de el bg it sk tr sq sv) [by @github-actions[bot], @sgiehl]
