 -- Edouard Gaulué <edouard@e-gaulue.com>  Thu, 17 Feb 2022 00:51:04 +0100

matomo (4.2.0-1) stable; urgency=high

  * Releasing Matomo 4.2.0
  * Show a message in each most valuable pages in Matomo to explain why
    it's important [by @diosmosis] (Closes: #13716)
  * Tracking requests might not be loaded because of CORB [by @sgiehl]
    (Closes: #17159)
  * PerformanceTiming API used by Matomo is deprecated, use
    PerformanceNavigationTiming if available [by @sgiehl] (Closes:
    #17102)
  * Editing Users screen is partially broken [by @diosmosis] (Closes:
    #17079)
  * Open Row Evolution icon invisible on mobile screens < 617 px
    (Closes: #9947)
  * What happens when a user denies consent and grants it later in the
    same session? (Closes: #17183)
  * Create new Dashboard popup does not show radio button to select
    options (empty, default) [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #17223)
  * Limit GeoIP downloads to certain hosts only [by @sgiehl, @diosmosis]
    (Closes: #17097)
  * Don't deactivate a core plugin during update [by @tsteur,
    @diosmosis] (Closes: #17213)
  * properly encode segment definitions from table so the hash will be
    the same as from query params [by @diosmosis] (Closes: #17029)
  * Anonymous user settings not working after v4 upgrade [by @sgiehl]
    (Closes: #17077)
  * Widget is showing wrong data from yesterday instead of today [by
    @sgiehl] (Closes: #17095)
  * Real-Time Map description switches to "There is no data for this
    report." [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #17099)
  * Graph of returning visitors doesn't show returning visitors [by
    @diosmosis] (Closes: #17123)
  * use Rules method instead of getting stored segments directly to pre-
    archive extra segments [by @diosmosis] (Closes: #17148)
  * Fix jquery location in page overlay [by @sgiehl, @diosmosis]
    (Closes: #17217)
  * Fix force-report parameter for core:archive [by @sgiehl, @diosmosis]
    (Closes: #17236)
  * If only one website exists, remove the site selector from reporting
    page [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #16789)
  * Error page served with HTTP 200 status (Closes: #10881)
  * Call to a member function getDateStart() on boolean
    DataTable/Renderer/Rss.php [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #16918)
  * Starting with php 7.3 on windows OS the geoip2php Update procedure
    is not working anymore.  [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #17023)
  * enable_auto_update=0 doesn't remove update check in the UI (Closes:
    #17106)
  * Custom tracking timestamp should return an integer to prevent HTTP
    500 tracking error [by @tsteur, @diosmosis] (Closes: #17127)
  * Error in console when trying to communicate with service worker in
    Firefox with persistant cookies disabled [by @tsteur] (Closes:
    #17136)
  * SMS evolution metrics might be formatted incorrectly on PHP 8 [by
    @sgiehl, @diosmosis] (Closes: #17152)
  * Tracking requests on PHP 8 might fail if an invalid encoding is sent
    [by @sgiehl, @diosmosis] (Closes: #17153)
  * Issues on map naming (Closes: #17171)
  * Include report column in duplicate check when inserting archive
    invalidations. [by @diosmosis] (Closes: #17192)
  * CustomLogo upload not working with PHP8 [by @gecon, @sgiehl]
    (Closes: #17205)
  * Error when using comparison feature: Argument 4 passed to
    Piwik\\Plugins\\API\\Filter\\DataComparisonFilter\\ComparisonRowGene
    rator::compareTable() must be an instance of Piwik\\DataTable or
    null, bool given [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #17212)
  * Archiver: do not create done flags like "done." [by @diosmosis]
    (Closes: #17215)
  * fix a couple bugs in archive querying when browser archiving is
    disabled [by @diosmosis] (Closes: #17216)
  * Fix warning when memory_limit = -1 [by @okom3pom, @sgiehl] (Closes:
    #17218)
  * [automatic translation update] Updated 440 strings in 48 languages
    (ru de eu et es da ka pt-br el ro ko bg be zh-cn pt cs vi id is ca
    pl ja it ar uk nn nl nb hr es-ar hu hi he am fr sk sl zh-tw tr tl lt
    lv fa th sq sr fi sv) [by @github-actions[bot], @sgiehl] (Closes:
    #17103)
  * [automatic translation update] Updated 433 strings in 10 languages
    (de es zh-cn cs it nl fr zh-tw tr sq) [by @github-actions[bot],
    @sgiehl] (Closes: #17137)
  * [automatic translation update] Updated 2 strings in 1 languages (de)
    [by @github-actions[bot], @sgiehl] (Closes: #17166)
  * [automatic translation update] Updated 33 strings in 2 languages (zh-
    cn sv) [by @github-actions[bot], @sgiehl] (Closes: #17197)
  * [automatic translation update] Updated 406 strings in 48 languages
    (ru de et es da eo pt-br el ro ko cy bg be zh-cn pt cs vi id bs ca
    pl ja it ar uk nn nl nb hr es-ar hu hi he fr sk sl zh-tw tr tl lt lv
    fa th sq sr fi ta sv) [by @github-actions[bot], @sgiehl] (Closes:
    #17220)
  * [automatic translation update] Updated 509 strings in 8 languages
    (el zh-cn it uk nl tr sq sv) [by @github-actions[bot], @sgiehl]
    (Closes: #17239)
  * Creates issue templates [by @sgiehl, @tsteur] (Closes: #17187)
  * Introduce PHP CS to improve code quality [by @sgiehl] (Closes:
    #16755)
  * core:archive command new parameter -force-report to only process
    invalidations for a specific report in a specific plugin. [by
    @diosmosis] (Closes: #16991)
