  * Add this commit to override spelling errors in changelog

 -- Edouard Gaulué <edouard@e-gaulue.com>  Wed, 16 Feb 2022 23:25:24 +0100

matomo (4.0.5-1) stable; urgency=high

  * Releasing Matomo 4.0.5
  * Unable to log in to matomo after 4.0.3 upgrade - Nginx/Ubuntu
    (Closes: #16866)
  * Support date format last week, last month, last year  [by @sgiehl]
    (Closes: #13818)
  * Displaying widgets in iframes logs bruteforce attacks [by @sgiehl]
    (Closes: #16867)
  * AbstractDeviceParser::getShortCode() must be of the type string, int
    returned [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #16889)
  * Check only invalidations created for correct sites [by @diosmosis]
    (Closes: #16892)
  * Comparison feature on All Websites dashboard not working (Showing
    through Site Selector/Not showing comparison data) [by @sgiehl]
    (Closes: #16879)
  * named parameters in mysqli_stmt->bind_param (Closes: #16885)
  * [automatic translation update] Updated 14 strings in 2 languages (de
    zh-tw) [by @github-actions[bot], @sgiehl] (Closes: #16887)
  * Use wikimedia/less.php instead of leafo/lessphp [by @sgiehl,
    @diosmosis] (Closes: #16813)
  * Avoid inserting duplicates in invalidation table to reduce IO. [by
    @diosmosis] (Closes: #16843)
  * Remove invalidations for segments that are not pre-processed if
    found. [by @diosmosis] (Closes: #16895)
  * Host detection: use HTTP_HOST as default, but provide a setting to
    use SERVER_NAME instead [by @sgiehl, @tsteur] (Closes: #16899)
  * SEO Plugin broken [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #16778)
  * CLI Archive might not stop [by @diosmosis] (Closes: #16788)
  * No custom dimensions in Matomo 4.0.0 (Closes: #16786)
  * Error upgrading db while upgrading to 4.0.0-b1 (session update
    fails) [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #16798)
  * Matomo 4.0.0 warns about "ExampleTheme requires Piwik <4.0.0-b1" [by
    @tsteur] (Closes: #16804)
  * Matomo 4 migration: Index column size too large [by @sgiehl]
    (Closes: #16811)
  * Improve token auth migration [by @tsteur] (Closes: #16822)
  * Change referrer url size to 1500 (#16835)
  * Trim referrer url if needed (#16836)
  * Create robots.txt to prevent bots from indexing Matomo app (#16795)
  * Improve php8 compatibility (#16838)
  * re-add missing condition for -skip-segments-today (#16777)
  * never specify optional parameter before required one [by @tsteur]
    (Closes: #16828)
  * Missing setGenerationTimeMs after upgrade to 4.x [by @tsteur]
    (Closes: #16853)
  * Matomo 4.0.2 warns about "ExampleLogTables requires Piwik <4.0.0-b1"
    [by @tsteur] (Closes: #16857)
  * -skip-segments-today no longer working in Matomo 4? [by @diosmosis]
    (Closes: #16775)
  * Create robots.txt to prevent bots from indexing Matomo app [by
    @mattab, @tsteur] (Closes: #16795)
  * More rigorous checks for non-existant site so archiving wont fail if
    ... [by @diosmosis, @tsteur] (Closes: #16837)
  * Segments not working on preprocessed files since Matomo 4.0.0 [by
    @diosmosis] (Closes: #16842)
  * only select invalidations that were added before a sites archiving
    began [by @diosmosis, @tsteur] (Closes: #16844)
  * Fix ttl not being respected on existing invalidations [by
    @diosmosis] (Closes: #16851)
  * Widget access always only works with view access not respecting new
    config setting [by @diosmosis] (Closes: #16869)
  * When forcing GET request method in JS tracker then disable send
    beacon [by @tsteur] (Closes: #16870)
  * Detect browsers: Slimjet, 7Star, MxNitro [by @sanchezzzhak, @sgiehl]
    (Closes: #6443)
  * Detect new brands: Starlight, GEOFOX, Verico, Tinmo, Matrix and
    Detect devices for existing brands: Asus, Sharp, Coolpad, Sony,
    OPPO, Lenovo, Philips, Vivo, Xiaomi, Manta Multimedia, NEC, Vernee,
    Karbonn, Kr"uger&Matz, RugGear, DEXP, Digma, MiXzo, Atom, Yu, Acer,
    Irbis, teXet, Telefunken, Onda, IconBIT, Polaroid, Doogee, Allview,
    BB Mobile, Touchmate, ArmPhone, Memup, Kazam, ZTE, Odys, Jinga,
    Ginzzu, iLife, Mobicel, Blu, Blaupunkt [by @sanchezzzhak] (Closes:
    #6444)
  * Detect Crazy Browser [by @sanchezzzhak, @sgiehl] (Closes: #6448)

 -- Edouard Gaulué <edouard@e-gaulue.com>  Wed, 16 Feb 2022 23:15:22 +0100

matomo (4.0.0-2) stable; urgency=high

   * deal with new files in 4.x (focus on Buster and Bullseye due to min 
     php version) 
   * fix lintian overrides (add/delete libraries/licenses/fonts...)
   * change Makefile to reflect lintian request (import_logs.py use 
     python3, fix permissions)
   * postinstall now execute: 
     /usr/share/matomo/console core:create-security-files
   * review /etc/matomo/apache.conf to reflect the previous line
   * fix debian packages dependencies
   * fix package compatibility level to 13
   * update copyright
   * update Debian.md

 -- Edouard Gaulué <edouard@e-gaulue.com>  Wed, 16 Feb 2022 23:05:55 +0100

matomo (4.0.0-1) stable; urgency=high

  * Releasing Matomo 4.0.0
  * Add support for app specific passwords (create and revoke
    token_auth)  [by @tsteur] (Closes: #6559)
  * Detect when stats load slowly and explain to user to disable Browser
    trigger archiving in Admin [by @andrzejewsky, @diosmosis] (Closes:
    #6210)
  * Offline tracking in JavaScript API [by @tsteur] (Closes: #9939)
  * Offer feature to anonymise or shorten the referrer [by @diosmosis,
    @tsteur] (Closes: #15426)
  * Allow force disable cookies [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #16258)
  * Allow disabling Visitor Profile feature and visits log feature [by
    @sgiehl] (Closes: #16259)
  * Offer possibility to not store IP address at all [by @sgiehl]
    (Closes: #16377)
  * Support PHP 8 (Closes: #16183)
  * Drop support for PHP 5.x, Require PHP 7.2  (Closes: #13611)
  * Activate DB-Ip support by default for all users [by @sgiehl]
    (Closes: #12811)
  * Tracking API: track Emoji correctly in page URLs and others [by
    @sgiehl] (Closes: #8790)
  * Allow plugins to generate their reports using historical data (eg.
    Custom Reports) [by @diosmosis] (Closes: #11974)
  * Provide more insights into page performance metrics  [by @sgiehl]
    (Closes: #12653)
  * Show "browser" report in goal by dimension report, view conversion
    rates by browser [by @tsteur] (Closes: #13202)
  * Add "Movers and shakers" widget to the default dashboard [by
    @tsteur] (Closes: #13153)
  * JS Tracker: enable alwaysUseSendBeacon by default [by @tsteur]
    (Closes: #13681)
  * Heartbeat / ping requests should only update visit_total_time
    (Closes: #9626)
  * Make Matomo JS Tracker work in strict mode (Closes: #14791)
  * New visitor ID generated per action in iframes (SameSite cookie
    issue) (Closes: #16161)
  * SameSite cookie attribute can now be configured in JS tracker [by
    @fealXX, @tsteur] (Closes: #16724)
  * Offer possibility to sync JavaScript tracker with any CDN (new
    community plugin TrackerJsCdnSync) (Closes: #13462)
  * log_visit.referer_url and log_action.name as TEXT instead of VARCHAR
    cause a lot of tmp table on disk [by @tsteur] (Closes: #14535)
  * Add new dimension and segment whether cookies were used or not:
    "Profilable" [by @tsteur] (Closes: #16192)
  * Reporting API: remove the PHP serialization response format [by
    @sgiehl] (Closes: #8100)
  * Reporting API: Make json2 format the default json format (potential
    BC break) [by @diosmosis] (Closes: #8566)
  * ISP detection should support the DB-IP ASN database [by @sgiehl]
    (Closes: #16499)
  * Drop-Down appears on top of lower level [by @sgiehl] (Closes:
    #16557)
  * New diagnotic warning when both auto archiving and browser archiving
    are enabled [by @tsteur, @diosmosis] (Closes: #16738)
  * Use name "segmented visits log" (plural) to be consistent with
    "Visits log" naming [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #16521)
  * Cloudron installation method (Closes: #16168)
  * Outlinks icons are not aligned in all reports [by @sgiehl] (Closes:
    #16436)
  * Disable Custom Variables feature by default [by @sgiehl] (Closes:
    #11524)
  * Drop support for IE 10 (Closes: #13613)
  * When DB user doesn't have the 'CREATE TEMPORARY TABLE' grant,
    display a clear error message [by @katebutler, @sgiehl] (Closes:
    #15237)
  * allow invalidating plugin archives only and archiving past data for
    plugins [by @diosmosis] (Closes: #15889)
  * Minimise token_auth exposure, hide token_auth from html responses
    (Closes: #4171)
  * update frontend libraries like jquery [by @diosmosis] (Closes:
    #12961)
  * Translate the "Asking for consent" page [by @maxpereira, @sgiehl]
    (Closes: #14954)
  * Content-tracking: I want to be able to disable piwik.php redirect
    and instead use the link tracking 500ms solution. [by @tsteur]
    (Closes: #6265)
  * Custom opt out screen should not imply tracking consent given
    (Closes: #16362)
  * Check that all Matomo cookies are set with the secure flag [by
    @tsteur] (Closes: #15681)
  * Referrer name should allow more than 70 characters (up to 255
    characters) [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #13582)
  * Remove LoginHttpAuth submodule [by @tsteur, @sgiehl] (Closes:
    #15396)
  * New page performance reports [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #15736)
  * Track seconds instead of days for "days since" dimensions [by
    @diosmosis] (Closes: #15774)
  * New log importer (log analytics) now only supports python3 [by
    @diosmosis] (Closes: #16095)
  * Custom Dimensions available and activated by default (Closes:
    #16265)
  * in Visitors>User IDs, opening a Profile for a given User ID
    shouldn't show other visits from User IDs who shared the same
    computer (Closes: #15440)
  * Prevent server gone away error in CronArchive [by @tsteur, @sgiehl]
    (Closes: #15619)
  * When looking at Yesterday's data, and there is data for today,
    notify users to try to look at Today [by @tsteur] (Closes: #13754)
  * When a user opts-out, do not send any tracking requests to the
    Tracking API (Closes: #12767)
  * Set higher expiry time for the "Ignore tracking" cookie [by @tsteur]
    (Closes: #13042)
  * JS Tracker: Add possibility to turn cookies back on,  enableCookies
    [by @tsteur] (Closes: #13056)
  * When signing up for the Matomo newsletter, clarify In the privacy
    notice that emails are processed by Madmimi  [by @sgiehl] (Closes:
    #15182)
  * Do not generate crossdomain link when cookies are disabled [by
    @tsteur] (Closes: #16017)
  * Make Matomo database use utf8mb4 collation by default [by @sgiehl]
    (Closes: #9785)
  * Use random_bytes() instead of uniqid/md5 in Common::generateUniqId()
    for improved security [by @katebutler] (Closes: #13357)
  * JS Tracker: set secure flag for _pk_testcookies (Closes: #15313)
  * Store session ID hashed in the DB [by @tsteur] (Closes: #15390)
  * Improve host validation: now using the SERVER_NAME and no longer the
    HOST header [by @tsteur, @diosmosis] (Closes: #16169)
  * Only allow widgetize and token usage for view users [by @tsteur]
    (Closes: #16263)
  * When embedding reports (widgets) into a site, it is no longer
    possible to use authentication tokens of users with at least write
    access  [by @tsteur, @diosmosis] (Closes: #16264)
  * Make sure the same 2FA token cannot be used twice [by @tsteur,
    @diosmosis] (Closes: #16389)
  * Reporting API: apply `hideColumns` recursively to nested values by
    setting `hideColumnsRecursively=1` [by @mattab, @tsteur] (Closes:
    #11115)
  * SQL type FLOAT should not be used for economical data [by @tsteur]
    (Closes: #12575)
  * "Back to content" link overlaps with the logo, fix skip-to-content
    offset [by @Findus23, @tsteur] (Closes: #16429)
  * Mobile: Icons not fully shown and shown not correctly (Closes:
    #13256)
  * JS Tracker: add rtf to list of downloads (Closes: #14579)
  * Adds INI setting to disable referrer spam blocklist  [by
    @john357smith, @sgiehl] (Closes: #15744)
  * Tracking of visitors without JavaScript (image beacon) does not work
    with strict referrer-policy [by @tsteur] (Closes: #15845)
  * Add more information to system check and be able to copy/paste for
    debugging purposes [by @tsteur] (Closes: #15931)
  * Track ecommerce views as new dimensions instead of custom variables
    [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #15999)
  * Make it possible to detect other clients than Browsers [by @sgiehl]
    (Closes: #16197)
  * prevent vacation messages in response to Email reports [by
    @Findus23] (Closes: #16288)
  * New feature to exclude tracking requests via config file: INI
    setting exclude_requests [by @tsteur] (Closes: #16302)
  * System check: Add Matomo Version History and download feature [by
    @tsteur, @diosmosis] (Closes: #16386)
  * Do not index the opt out iframe in search engines [by @tsteur]
    (Closes: #16446)
  * Visitor map shows info icon but no tooltip when there is no data [by
    @sgiehl] (Closes: #8505)
  * Don't lock log_visit table to check if privilege is granted [by
    @tsteur] (Closes: #15247)
  * New INI setting delete_logs_unused_actions_max_rows_per_query useful
    for speeding up deletion process for very large sites [by @toredash,
    @tsteur] (Closes: #15492)
  * Row Evolution PopUp opens after Visitors Log Popup Closed [by
    @sgiehl] (Closes: #15875)
  * Improve performance/memory of archive selection [by @tsteur,
    @diosmosis] (Closes: #15887)
  * Tracker API speed: avoid DB query when recording historical data or
    other authenticated tracking requests [by @tsteur] (Closes: #15986)
  * Allow configuration of a shorter lock wait time in tracker mode (new
    INI setting innodb_lock_wait_timeout) [by @tsteur, @diosmosis]
    (Closes: #16092)
  * Manage Dimensions: Sorting by ID is not numeric [by @nina-py,
    @tsteur] (Closes: #16473)
  * Move Provider plugin to the Marketplace [by @tsteur] (Closes: #5341)
  * Fix VisitorFrequency.get API for idsites=all [by @sgiehl] (Closes:
    #15601)
  * update php-di to latest version 6.x [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #15974)
  * JS Tracker: require category and action in trackEvent [by @Findus23,
    @tsteur] (Closes: #15980)
  * Get all our plugins and premium plugins to pass w/ updated frontend
    libs [by @diosmosis, @tsteur, @sgiehl] (Closes: #16031)
  * wrong escaping of cookie path [by @MichaelHeerklotz, @diosmosis,
    @tsteur] (Closes: #16087)
  * no cut-off icons in DataTables [by @Findus23, @sgiehl] (Closes:
    #15979)
  * Segmented Visitor profile: Layout breaks when zooming out (Closes:
    #16238)
  * properly align pre code [by @Findus23, @sgiehl] (Closes: #16354)
  * split disabled PHP functions to not break table layout [by
    @Findus23, @tsteur] (Closes: #16428)
  * Document adding Custom JS to tracker via tracker.js / tracker.min.js
    on https://developer.matomo.org/guides/enrich-js-tracker [by
    @tsteur] (Closes: #11572)
  * Sort Custom dimensions in reporting page alphabetically [by @sgiehl]
    (Closes: #16148)
  * doTrackGoal() in the PHP API should return success or failure
    response, not tracking GIF [by @tsteur] (Closes: #12739)
  * Make segment title clickable and add segment definition to tooltip.
    [by @diosmosis, @tsteur] (Closes: #15269)
  * When closing a popover, leave opened any previously opened popover
    [by @sgiehl, @tsteur] (Closes: #15444)
