    @john357smith, @sgiehl] (Closes: #15805)
  * The display problem of piwik-siteselector in asia language
    environment [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #16072)
  * Fix behaviour for segments using "not equals" or "not contains" on
    an action dimension [by @sgiehl, @tsteur] (Closes: #16172)
  * SQL error: Data too long for column 'user_id' (Closes: #16249)
  * Bug: Copying a dashboard to another user - special characters are
    being urlencoded [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #16270)
  * Make sure confirmPassword uses the currently active login plugin,
    not always "Login". [by @diosmosis, @tsteur] (Closes: #16281)
  * Warning in sparklines: Argument 1 passed to
    Piwik\\Plugins\\CoreVisualizations\\Visualizations\\Sparkline::ensur
    eValuesEvenIfEmpty() must be of the type array, boolean given [by
    @sgiehl] (Closes: #16294)
  * Use relative URLs for svgBasePath so proxy url doesn't need to be
    configured to make real time map work [by @tsteur, @sgiehl] (Closes:
    #16341)
  * Marketplace search broken in Reports (Closes: #16358)
  * Do not cache core updater oneClickUpdate page in browser [by
    @tsteur] (Closes: #16466)
  * Replaced 'Piwik' with 'Matomo' in console output when creating extra
    Custom Dimensions [by @nina-py, @tsteur] (Closes: #16475)
  * Update our Develop guides for Matomo 4.0.0  [by @tsteur] (Closes:
    #8415)
  * Document how plugins can extend Visitor Log and Visitor Profile [by
    @sgiehl] (Closes: #12073)
  * Make all GDPR pages translatable [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #15574)
  * add missing link to consent help page [by @Findus23, @tsteur]
    (Closes: #15973)
  * Tracking API: fail with an error when wrong authentication provided
    when sending custom ip address (instead of using the sender's ip
    address) [by @tsteur, @sgiehl] (Closes: #13471)
  * UI tests on Travis do not execute UI tests of submodules [by
    @diosmosis, @sgiehl] (Closes: #9253)
