  * Roblox Android App with unusual User Agent Format (Closes: #6372)
  * Added Roblox and GOG Galaxy App detection [by @nickperkins, @sgiehl]
    (Closes: #6373)
  * Makes it possible to fully anonymize a IPv6 address [by @sgiehl]
    (Closes: #15)
  * Proposal to rename this referrer-spam-list (Closes: #1224)
  * Add prizesk.com [by @JayVii, @spmedia] (Closes: #1238)
  * Add eecz.org [by @ericguirbal, @spmedia] (Closes: #1241)
  * Add darcysassoon.top [by @ericguirbal, @spmedia] (Closes: #1242)
  * Add aimiot.net [by @ericguirbal, @spmedia] (Closes: #1243)
  * Add meroyharte.top [by @ericguirbal, @spmedia] (Closes: #1244)
  * Added own-ahrefs.com (same spammer as semalt.com) [by @Steltek,
    @spmedia] (Closes: #1245)

 -- Edouard Gaulué <edouard@e-gaulue.com>  Sun, 13 Feb 2022 13:12:13 +0100

