matomo (3.7.0-1) stable; urgency=high

  * Releasing Matomo 3.7.0
  * Add Matomo Tag Manager to core [by @tsteur] (Closes: #13402)
  * HTML in report documentation is shown plain text (Closes: #13668)
  * Limit password length (at a reasonable length) [by @tsteur] (Closes:
    #13491)
  * Bad position of the date in the title [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #13649)
  * Some translation in maps contains an unnecessary %s [by @sgiehl]
    (Closes: #13695)
  * Real-time widget border is slightly misplaced [by @tsteur] (Closes:
    #13322)
  * Device Type and Browser plugins reports: hide rows without visits
    [by @tsteur] (Closes: #12266)
  * Actions performed at the same time register as different visits
    (Closes: #5966)
  * "Remember me" doesn't, very much (Closes: #13327)
  * After 3.6.1 update, error in e-commerce widget and overview "please
    specify a value for date" [by @tsteur] (Closes: #13644)
  * Show the CORS settings in the UI when
    enable_general_settings_admin=0 [by @mattab, @tsteur] (Closes:
    #13660)
  * [automatic translation update] Updated 222 strings in 9 languages
    (ja, fi, uk, de, es, pt, it, cs, tr) [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #13663)
  * [automatic translation update] Updated 272 strings in 13 languages
    (da, et, pl, pt-br, ru, sq, es, de, el, it, pt, tr, cs) [by @sgiehl]
    (Closes: #13708)
  * Page title in Tag Manager, Help page, Admin pages show the date but
    there is no calendar in the page [by @tsteur] (Closes: #13353)
  * Ability to change periods over which evolution graphs display in
    scheduled reports [by @diosmosis] (Closes: #13501)
  * Fix possible error in visitor profile when no visit found [by
    @tsteur, @sgiehl] (Closes: #13549)
  * Regenerate OmniFixture dump w/ more xss payloads [by @diosmosis]
    (Closes: #13556)
  * fix domain age from archive.org [by @Findus23, @sgiehl] (Closes:
    #13574)
  * Add more tests for format=original. [by @diosmosis, @sgiehl]
    (Closes: #13584)
  * Regenerate htaccess files after update [by @tsteur, @sgiehl]
    (Closes: #13591)
  * Different `delete_logs_older_than` value for log tables (Closes:
    #13610)
  * Update theme to reflect the new logo and brand color changes [by
    @tsteur, @mattab] (Closes: #13629)
  * fix switch continue in CreatePull [by @Findus23, @sgiehl] (Closes:
    #13635)
  * Tracking unavailable when data rotation happens (Closes: #13636)
  * Undefined index: never [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #13638)
  * Added API endpoint to return the php version info [by @Toflar,
    @tsteur] (Closes: #13646)
  * Fix punctuation, spelling, and grammar [by @imronras, @mattab]
    (Closes: #13650)
  * Let plugins change content of JS Tracking Code Missing Email [by
    @tsteur] (Closes: #13658)
  * Fix wrong Site class is used which may not be available in build [by
    @tsteur, @diosmosis] (Closes: #13693)
  * Fix link to linkedin to point directly to the group [by @tsteur,
    @mattab] (Closes: #13699)
  * In API requests made by Insights, make sure existing query params do
    not affect requests. [by @diosmosis] (Closes: #13700)
  * Add request parameters to API.Request.intercept event. [by
    @diosmosis] (Closes: #13720)
  * Matomo analytics tag option for setting secure cookies [by @tsteur]
    (Closes: #119)
  * Make sure that if JS tracker doesnt get bundled the tracking still
    works [by @tsteur] (Closes: #121)
  * Added VWO tag [by @MichaelHeerklotz, @tsteur] (Closes: #64)
  * Added Emarsys tag [by @MichaelHeerklotz, @tsteur] (Closes: #65)
  * add Bing Conversion Tracking [by @Findus23, @tsteur] (Closes: #76)
  * Add new tag: Drift chat [by @Findus23] (Closes: #91)
  * Add new tag: Change android address bar color [by @Findus23]
    (Closes: #92)
  * Add LiveZilla Tag [by @scysys, @tsteur] (Closes: #95)
