 -- Matomo Autonomous Build System <nobody@matomo.org>  Sun, 25 Nov 2018 04:13:23 +0000

matomo (3.6.1-1) stable; urgency=high

  * Releasing Matomo 3.6.1
  * Generate changelog using our Github Changelog Generator.
  * Add possibility to manage and view Intranet websites [by @tsteur]
    (Closes: #7724)
  * Replace our github service "Piwik Plugins" with an app "Matomo
    Plugins" or webhook [by @tsteur] (Closes: #13050)
  * Send email if no tracked data within N days. [by @diosmosis]
    (Closes: #13363)
  * Implements wrapper method for a more secure unserialize with PHP 7
    [by @sgiehl, @diosmosis] (Closes: #13285)
  * Ensure report title is escaped in export overlay [by @sgiehl,
    @diosmosis] (Closes: #13502)
  * When requesting a password reset, the email content is out of date
    [by @diosmosis] (Closes: #13520)
  * Ensure sensitive data is sent as POST parameters in user management
    [by @sgiehl, @diosmosis] (Closes: #13621)
  * When a Goal is created as "Matching event", allow to set Goal value
    as the event value (Closes: #13476)
  * 3.6.0 period=day&date=today no longer highlights current date [by
    @sgiehl] (Closes: #13369)
  * Make sure user is not logged out when settings saved w/ no password
    change. [by @diosmosis, @sgiehl] (Closes: #13391)
  * HTML E-Mail report - Report list incorrect color [by @diosmosis]
    (Closes: #13401)
  * Fixes Ecommerce overview [by @sgiehl, @diosmosis] (Closes: #13405)
  * Replace row action image icon with font icon in User ID report [by
    @sgiehl] (Closes: #13303)
  * Make email report unsubscribe link look consistent with other report
    footer links [by @diosmosis] (Closes: #13330)
  * Remove the user "alias" feature [by @diosmosis] (Closes: #10165)
  * Please change wording of "You are currently opted in." [by @tsteur]
    (Closes: #12954)
  * Updates submodules [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #13564)
  * New events + some other misc changes [by @diosmosis] (Closes:
    #13388)
  * Campaign name with capitals will create duplicate visits (Closes:
    #12250)
  * Pivoting by custom dimension results in an error [by @diosmosis]
    (Closes: #13317)
  * Fix capabilities weren't detected correctly [by @tsteur, @diosmosis]
    (Closes: #13368)
  * WARNING: /var/www/html/plugins/API/API.php(401): Notice - compact():
    Undefined variable: idGoal [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #13375)
  * Manage Users: SQL Error for role write [by @diosmosis] (Closes:
    #13384)
  * Error: You can't access this resource as it requires 'view' access
    for the website id = 60. [by @diosmosis] (Closes: #13406)
  * Work around mysql client segfault in update. [by @diosmosis,
    @sgiehl] (Closes: #13407)
  * It should not be possible to edit anonymous user or set certain
    permissions [by @diosmosis] (Closes: #13412)
  * When displaying unprocessed segment message, check for urlencoded
    segment. [by @diosmosis, @tsteur] (Closes: #13415)
  * Anonymous user settings results in an error when site no longer
    exists [by @tsteur] (Closes: #13423)
  * Fatal error in referrers report [by @tsteur] (Closes: #13438)
  * Create periods with timezones in a couple places that are missing
    it. [by @diosmosis] (Closes: #13445)
  * Referrer name comparison should be case insensitive ... [by
    @diosmosis] (Closes: #13469)
  * Fix incorrect sort order when scheduled report uses custom report
    [by @diosmosis] (Closes: #13487)
  * Live.getSimpleLastVisitCount widget loses segment upon refresh
    (Closes: #13499)
  * Error message CpChart triggered with specific payload [by @sgiehl]
    (Closes: #13505)
  * Error message Variable "topMenu" does not exist [by @sgiehl]
    (Closes: #13506)
  * Error message in various places when invalid parameters are used [by
    @sgiehl] (Closes: #13507)
  * Better check for valid URLs [by @mattab, @diosmosis] (Closes:
    #13572)
  * Fix single day archive check in ArchiveProcessor/Parameters. [by
    @diosmosis] (Closes: #13580)
  * Adds new language Spanish (Argentina) [by @sgiehl, @diosmosis]
    (Closes: #13350)
  * [automatic translation update] Updated 303 strings in 8 languages
    (el, fa, fi, fr, sv, it, pt, tr) [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #13436)
  * [automatic translation update] Updated 699 strings in 15 languages
    (es, fa, ja, nl, nn, sq, sv, uk, fr, el, it, pt-br, tr, cs, de) [by
    @sgiehl] (Closes: #13560)
  * [automatic translation update] Updated 73 strings in 6 languages
    (it, sq, tr, el, es, pt-br) [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #13612)
  * Run our automated tests suite also on PHP7 (Closes: #10586)
  * Exception on visitor profile popup [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #12215)
  * Multiple conditions for goal with AND/OR seperation (Closes: #12346)
  * Auto-detect timezone and currency in installer [by @c960657,
    @tsteur] (Closes: #13092)
  * Couple changes to aid debugging [by @diosmosis] (Closes: #13269)
  * Use Python 2.7 for travis tests [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #13282)
  * Stable sort for most frequent segment values [by @sgiehl,
    @diosmosis] (Closes: #13286)
  * Make sure simple datatable metadata is serialized + some test case
    changes [by @diosmosis] (Closes: #13296)
  * Updates all Guides and FAQs to reference the new "Write" permission
    (Closes: #13297)
  * Remove COLUMN_AGGREGATION_OPS_METADATA_NAME metadata before
    serializi... [by @diosmosis] (Closes: #13304)
  * Adds UI tests for Custom Logos [by @sgiehl, @diosmosis] (Closes:
    #13311)
  * If serialize=1 in Original renderer, return serialized array w/
    exception info instead of throwing. [by @diosmosis, @tsteur]
    (Closes: #13340)
  * Show confirm before changing a users password and show notification
    on save complete. [by @diosmosis, @mattab] (Closes: #13342)
  * Add site type as attribute to site card in sitesmanager UI so they
    can be selected by type. [by @diosmosis] (Closes: #13343)
  * Remember user who created a site. [by @diosmosis] (Closes: #13362)
  * Override string trim only if needed to fix performance issue [by
    @tsteur, @diosmosis] (Closes: #13371)
  * Always set hours to 0 for periods.getToday [by @sgiehl, @diosmosis]
    (Closes: #13373)
  * Manage Users: Can't filter by access write [by @diosmosis] (Closes:
    #13385)
  * Fix "not empty" condition in SegmentExpression [by @splinter89,
    @tsteur] (Closes: #13386)
  * Ensure action details are sorted stable across PHP versions [by
    @sgiehl, @diosmosis] (Closes: #13404)
  * Prevent error related report may not be defined [by @tsteur,
    @sgiehl] (Closes: #13425)
  * Use Request::processRequest() so API events are triggered. [by
    @diosmosis] (Closes: #13428)
  * Allow session to be writable in CLI mode so tests can write values.
    [by @diosmosis] (Closes: #13430)
  * Replace unsupported characters in all tracking request params [by
    @sgiehl, @diosmosis] (Closes: #13437)
  * Use postMessage instead of directly making API calls in the overlay
    iframe. [by @diosmosis] (Closes: #13446)
  * do not automatically download lfs files when cloning/checking out
    [by @diosmosis] (Closes: #13449)
  * Remove user-agent checking code in SessionAuth. [by @diosmosis]
    (Closes: #13470)
  * Stable sort for additional pivoted columns [by @sgiehl, @diosmosis]
    (Closes: #13477)
  * don't send referrer to plugin authors website [by @Findus23,
    @diosmosis] (Closes: #13479)
  * Escape feature name for rate feature tooltips [by @sgiehl,
    @diosmosis] (Closes: #13503)
  * Avoid creating any archive tables for future dates [by @sgiehl,
    @diosmosis] (Closes: #13504)
  * Warning message in a UI notification after requesting a password
    reset [by @diosmosis] (Closes: #13519)
  * Put our current mission statement (as of Sept 2018) in the Readme
    [by @mattab, @tsteur] (Closes: #13522)
