    @diosmosis] (Closes: #13523)
  * Quote db name in certain queries. [by @diosmosis] (Closes: #13529)
  * Manage users: when clicking "edit" button, scroll back to top [by
    @oswdr, @tsteur] (Closes: #13551)
  * don't consider .swf files safe [by @Findus23, @sgiehl] (Closes:
    #13558)
