 -- Matomo Autonomous Build System <nobody@matomo.org>  Tue, 26 Jun 2018 07:35:50 +0000

matomo (3.5.1-1) stable; urgency=high

  * Releasing Matomo 3.5.1
  * See IP addresses in Real-time visitor widget [by @sgiehl] (Closes:
    #12876)
  * Show privacy notice when signing up for a newsletter during
    installation [by @diosmosis] (Closes: #12921)
  * Row evolution broken [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #12862)
  * Tooltip for limit selector appears even when limit selector is open
    [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #12937)
  * Rename Actions and Referrers in reporting menu [by @diosmosis]
    (Closes: #12750)
  * Check configured variables for availability in GeoIP2 server module
    [by @sgiehl, @diosmosis] (Closes: #12892)
  * Slightly faster location provider instance creation [by @tsteur,
    @diosmosis] (Closes: #12967)
  * Rename "Users" report to "User IDs" and move it down the list [by
    @sgiehl] (Closes: #12806)
  * Leave the help text always displayed once the Help icon was clicked
    [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #12895)
  * Add possibility to trigger the archiving only for a specific plugin
    [by @tsteur, @diosmosis] (Closes: #12945)
  * GeoIPAutoUpdater fails updating geoip2 database with .mmdb file
    ending [by @mattab] (Closes: #11049)
  * Super users are not anonymous [by @letharion, @diosmosis] (Closes:
    #12766)
  * The Visitor Map does not show unique visitors at city level [by
    @sgiehl] (Closes: #12860)
  * Prevent possible fatal when showing deleted goals in visitor profile
    [by @sgiehl, @diosmosis] (Closes: #12910)
  * Invalid MySQL Version [by @tsteur] (Closes: #12927)
  * Fix DI is not used in tracker updater command [by @tsteur,
    @diosmosis] (Closes: #12944)
  * Fixed undefined APIRequest in Visualization.php [by @bagbag,
    @sgiehl] (Closes: #12947)
  * Update Intl translations to CLDR 33 [by @c960657, @sgiehl] (Closes:
    #12890)
  * [automatic translation update] Updated 273 strings in 13 languages
    (ar, da, de, fa, fr, hu, pl, pt-br, pt, sq, tr, zh-tw, el) [by
    @sgiehl] (Closes: #12912)
  * [automatic translation update] Updated 427 strings in 47 languages
    (am, ar, be, bg, ca, cs, da, de, el, es, et, eu, fa, fi, fr, gl, he,
    hi, hu, id, is, it, ja, ka, ko, lt, lv, nb, nl, nn, pl, pt-br, pt,
    ro, ru, sk, sl, sq, sr, sv, th, tl, tr, uk, vi, zh-cn, zh-tw) [by
    @sgiehl] (Closes: #12982)
  * EU is called "Unknown" in the country overview (Closes: #11588)
  * Improve and split tests [by @sgiehl, @diosmosis] (Closes: #12822)
  * Move the "Locations" menu just above the "Real-time Map" [by
    @sgiehl] (Closes: #12852)
