    @diosmosis] (Closes: #12953)
  * Geoip1 should still be available even when Geoip2 is available [by
    @mattab] (Closes: #12959)
  * Added a few mobile user-agents (mostly top Android devices) [by
    @GregOriol, @sgiehl] (Closes: #5735)
