    @GregOriol, @sgiehl] (Closes: #5736)
  * Google bots not detected [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #5738)
  * Syntax regular browser.yml errror (JS) [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #5739)
  * Added a few more mobile device variants [by @GregOriol, @sgiehl]
    (Closes: #5740)
