 -- Matomo Autonomous Build System <nobody@matomo.org>  Sun, 24 Jun 2018 03:30:46 +0000

matomo (3.4.0-1) stable; urgency=high

  * Releasing Matomo 3.4.0
  * JS Tracker, New method `resetUserId` to de-assign a user id after a
    logout [by @znerol, @mattab] (Closes: #12141)
  * Let user select how many records / rows to export when clicking for
    example CSV export (Closes: #8314)
  * Let me customise the opt-out iframe: fonts, color, sizes (Closes:
    #12455)
  * Email reports sent via the cron core:archive task do not contain
    reports that depend on idsite (Closes: #12560)
  * Shows icon to disable/enable Zen Mode (full screen view) [by
    @ryyee99, @mattab] (Closes: #12459)
  * Added custom URL parameters to style the optOut iframe [by @Jouveer,
    @mattab] (Closes: #12472)
  * New Dashboard API methods: `copyDashboardToUser`,
    `createNewDashboardForUser`, `removeDashboard` and
    `resetDashboardLayout` [by @sgiehl, @mattab] (Closes: #12587)
  * Give developers the possibility to compare translation keys in
    different languages [by @tsteur] (Closes: #12495)
  * Add more date segments: visitEndServerDate visitEndServerDayOfMonth
    visitEndServerDayOfWeek visitEndServerDayOfYear, etc. [by @tsteur]
    (Closes: #12521)
  * scrollTo feature not working anymore, notifications not visible etc
    (Closes: #12625)
  * Chrome: Selecting the tracking code with one click does not work
    anymore (Closes: #12637)
  * Small performance improvement in custom tracker [by @tsteur,
    @mattab] (Closes: #12443)
  * Fix a possible issue when there are more than 2 billion visits
    tracked and system is 32 bits [by @mattab] (Closes: #12469)
  * Format sparklines better (Closes: #12451)
  * Popover: position the minimise and reload icons correctly [by
    @Jouveer, @mattab] (Closes: #12458)
  * Align icon in Row Evolution popover [by @danikachhour, @mattab]
    (Closes: #12464)
  * Page Overlay: Replace images with font icons [by @sgiehl] (Closes:
    #12465)
  * Improvements to Annotations listing design [by @carmenliao, @mattab]
    (Closes: #12476)
  * Move site selector loading indicator to the left [by @Findus23,
    @sgiehl] (Closes: #12485)
  * improve styling of shortcut help [by @Findus23, @sgiehl] (Closes:
    #12486)
  * update checker display issues [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #12487)
  * Adds new icons to UI demo page [by @sgiehl, @mattab] (Closes:
    #12490)
  * Fixes position of activity indicator [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #12530)
  * DeviceDetection, display themed "refresh" button [by @alcalyn,
    @sgiehl] (Closes: #12570)
  * Remove word "website" from website selector [by @tsteur] (Closes:
    #9063)
  * Better adblock detection during setup (Closes: #11660)
  * Allow to login by Email as well as Username (Closes: #11959)
  * Hide widgets not working without internet connection if disabled in
    config [by @sgiehl, @mattab] (Closes: #12279)
  * Add new keyboard shortcuts for Top/Bottom of page (Closes: #12456)
  * Embed Widgets page: added link to the Embed reports user guide [by
    @ryyee99, @mattab] (Closes: #12475)
  * Improvement maintenance mode message to show a message based on
    record_statistics value [by @ryyee99, @mattab] (Closes: #12479)
  * Add possibility to toggle (show/hide) left menu [by @tsteur]
    (Closes: #9263)
  * Login and Reset password: improved fields [by @Jouveer, @mattab]
    (Closes: #12448)
  * Renames piwik font to matomo [by @sgiehl, @mattab] (Closes: #12489)
  * updates piwik/* and matomo/* composer packages [by @sgiehl] (Closes:
    #12645)
  * UserID "Signing out use-case" - actions still attributed to the same
    Visitor [by @znerol, @mattab] (Closes: #7556)
  * E-Mail Report: Page URL Links shifted after "Others" [by @sgiehl]
    (Closes: #11825)
  * Page Overlay Information boxes are displayed under menus and divs
    [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #12168)
  * Twig Filesystem: Warning - realpath(): open_basedir restriction in
    effect [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #12280)
  * Browser widget bug with pagination [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #12369)
  * Visitor Profile "First visit" does not always show the very first
    visit [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #12373)
  * Do not use segment to fetch additional visits for visitor profile
    [by @sgiehl, @mattab] (Closes: #12374)
  * Move public static functions out of Live controller [by @sgiehl]
    (Closes: #12394)
  * Show error message if visitor in visitor profile could not be found
    instead of fatal error [by @tsteur, @mattab] (Closes: #12396)
  * GeoIP re-attribution: debug output now shows changes to visits geo-
    location [by @lwille, @mattab] (Closes: #12478)
  * When generating URLs, only strip PATH_INFO when it is not empty [by
    @mattab] (Closes: #12500)
  * JS Tracker: expected no warning in the console when addTracker
    multiple times [by @mattab, @tsteur] (Closes: #12545)
  * Cloud visualisation may display error "Key 1 for array with keys 0
    does not exist" [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #12578)
  * Ensure to also install plugins when there is a POST request [by
    @tsteur, @sgiehl] (Closes: #12619)
  * Trigger DB failed exception also for POST API requests [by @tsteur]
    (Closes: #12621)
  * [automatic translation update] Updated 2074 strings in 49 languages
    (hr, de, bn, bs, cy, ta, am, be, bg, ca, eu, gl, he, hu, is, ka, ar,
    cs, da, el, es, et, fa, fi, fr, hi, id, it, ja, lt, nl, pl, pt-br,
    ru, sq, sr, sv, tr, uk, zh-cn, zh-tw, ko, nb, nn, pt, ro, th, vi,
    lv) [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #12514)
  * [automatic translation update] Updated 1628 strings in 49 languages
    (bs, ca, el, et, eu, fi, fr, ja, ka, ko, nb, nl, pl, pt-br, sk, sl,
    sq, sv, tl, tr, vi, zh-cn, zh-tw, it, ar, be, bg, cs, da, de, es,
    fa, he, hi, hu, id, is, nn, pt, ro, ru, sr, th, uk, lt, lv, ta, gl,
    bn) [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #12629)
  * Export overlay for Datatables [by @sgiehl, @mattab] (Closes: #11958)
