    @sgiehl] (Closes: #12501)
  * During installation, trim inputs in the database setup page to avoid
    whitespaces issues [by @mattab] (Closes: #12502)
  * Use renamed composer packages [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #12518)
  * Adds audio icon to matomo font [by @sgiehl, @mattab] (Closes:
    #12520)
  * Use more font icons instead of images [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #12532)
  * Better handling of POST tracking requests when page is unloaded
    (using sendBeacon) [by @tsteur, @mattab] (Closes: #12538)
  * Fix others row might not be replaced in subtables of others row [by
    @tsteur] (Closes: #12541)
  * Update reports cache at least once every hour [by @tsteur, @mattab]
    (Closes: #12542)
  * Allow plugins to define custom action types [by @sgiehl] (Closes:
    #12556)
  * Update error message in API/UI if date is before 1992 (#12559) [by
    @simivar, @sgiehl] (Closes: #12561)
  * Add new Filesystem.allCachesCleared event after all caches cleared.
    [by @diosmosis, @tsteur] (Closes: #12568)
  * Key visitsAggregated does not exist as the array is empty in
    _profileSummaryVisits.twig (Closes: #12579)
  * Developer documentation: the list of all segments is missing the
    "Metrics" segments [by @diosmosis] (Closes: #12590)
  * Update component-cache version to 1.0.2. [by @diosmosis, @tsteur]
    (Closes: #12591)
  * JS Tracker, cross domain tracking: new method to get the URL
    parameters to forward the Visitor id value (&pk_vid=xyz) [by
    @diosmosis] (Closes: #12602)
