 -- Matomo Autonomous Build System <nobody@matomo.org>  Sun, 24 Jun 2018 03:22:28 +0000

matomo (3.3.0-1) stable; urgency=high

  * Releasing Matomo 3.3.0
  * Piwik is now Matomo [by @tsteur] (Closes: #12410)
  * All Websites view does not truncate website title when title is very
    long [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #12386)
  * API: when an invalid format is specified, keep the error message
    shorter [by @mattab, @sgiehl] (Closes: #12401)
  * Multi-Channel attribution modelling (Closes: #6064)
  * Hide duplicate actions in visitor log by default [by @sgiehl]
    (Closes: #12160)
  * Consider matomo-org as official github owner [by @tsteur] (Closes:
    #12414)
  * Fixes memory leak in piwikApiService. [by @jvilk, @tsteur] (Closes:
    #12249)
  * Piwik 3.2.1 Right Sidebar Menu issue [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #12334)
  * in the console command diagnostics:run, display a success message
    when all checks are green [by @mattab] (Closes: #12342)
  * Email server settings: disable fields auto completion [by @mattab,
    @tsteur] (Closes: #12404)
  * use SPDX license specifier for plugins (Closes: #12429)
  * visitor log: grouping hides information [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #9586)
  * [automatic translation update] Updated 1069 strings in 13 languages
    (fi, cs, fr, ru, sq, tr, ro, de, ja, zh-tw, sv, el, pl) [by @sgiehl]
    (Closes: #12419)
  * Upgrade to latest Travis CI infrastructure [by @mneudert] (Closes:
    #11986)
  * Ability to customise the piwik/tmp directory path in
    config/config.ini.php file [by @iMarkus, @mattab] (Closes: #12189)
  * Usort Warning ReportsProvider.php line 166 [by @sgiehl] (Closes:
    #12281)
  * Extends TestRunner options for Travis trusty distribution selection
    [by @mneudert, @sgiehl] (Closes: #12295)
  * Adds segment for device model [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #12298)
  * Adds segmented visitor log for provider report [by @sgiehl, @mattab]
    (Closes: #12299)
  * Release Piwik 3.2.1 [by @mattab] (Closes: #12333)
  * Respect maintenance mode when archiving [by @tsteur] (Closes:
    #12339)
  * When general settings admin is disabled, do not show archive
    settings [by @tsteur] (Closes: #12343)
  * Integrity check in Piwik-3.2.1 shows essential core
    directories/files as 'deletable'... [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #12344)
  * Improves truncate twig filter [by @sgiehl, @mattab] (Closes: #12347)
  * Log Analytics: use latest submodule [by @mattab] (Closes: #12350)
  * JS Tracker: make setSecureCookie work [by @mattab] (Closes: #12355)
  * Show trace in log message only if enabled. [by @tsteur, @mattab,
    @sgiehl] (Closes: #12357)
  * Files integrity system check messages (Closes: #12362)
  * Truncate multisites label if too long [by @sgiehl, @tsteur] (Closes:
    #12387)
  * Prevent fatal error message when accessing visitor log without
    access [by @tsteur] (Closes: #12393)
  * Prevent possible error languageTranslateWithCode is not defined [by
    @tsteur] (Closes: #12398)
  * UI test improvements [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #12405)
  * Fix theme color regression [by @sgiehl, @tsteur] (Closes: #12407)
  * Delete PULL_REQUEST_TEMPLATE [by @Findus23, @tsteur] (Closes:
    #12412)
  * Further Piwik.org => Matomo.org replacements [by @tsteur] (Closes:
    #12415)
  * Update default DB table prefix [by @tsteur, @mattab] (Closes:
    #12416)
  * Show Matomo instead of Piwik in the user interface in more places
    [by @mattab] (Closes: #12421)
  * Mention name change in the developer changelog [by @tsteur] (Closes:
    #12424)
  * Matomo 3.3.0-b2 [by @mattab] (Closes: #12427)
  * Show the 'Piwik is Matomo' banner after the successful upgade [by
    @mattab] (Closes: #12434)
  * Log Analytics: Track the HTTP request method used for each request
    (GET or POST) [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #25)
  * Piwik & self signed certificates : urlopen error [SSL:
    CERTIFICATE_VERIFY_FAILED] certificate verify failed. Add new -
    accept-invalid-ssl-certificate [by @ntd] (Closes: #138)
  * Adds option to enable tracking of HTTP-method as page custom
    variable [by @sgiehl, @mattab] (Closes: #183)
  * Abort with warning when using Python 3 [by @mneudert, @mattab]
    (Closes: #195)
  * Invalid log lines with common_complete log format (Closes: #197)
  * Only issue an invalid line status, when the line was really invalid
    and skipped [by @mattab] (Closes: #198)
  * Add -accept-invalid-ssl-certificate option. [by @smarsching,
    @mattab] (Closes: #199)
  * Make code compatible with Python <=2.7.8. [by @smarsching, @mattab]
    (Closes: #200)
  * Run _get_token_auth after config object is initialized. [by
    @smarsching, @mattab] (Closes: #201)

 -- Matomo Autonomous Build System <nobody@matomo.org>  Sat, 23 Jun 2018 09:48:06 +0000

piwik (3.2.1-1) stable; urgency=high

  * Releasing Piwik 3.2.1
  * New plugin: provide simple UI to invalidate old reports [by @sgiehl]
    (Closes: #8942)
  * Ability to restrict user login to specific IP addresses (Closes:
    #4577)
  * Use consistent HTML email body for all scheduled reports (HTML, PDF
    & CSV) [by @diosmosis, @mattab] (Closes: #12233)
  * Show shortcut help screen when pressing `?` [by @sgiehl, @mattab]
    (Closes: #12283)
  * Various bugs when using SSL and/or a reverse proxy (Closes: #6880)
  * Piwik setup in a sub path URL behind a proxy (Closes: #7898)
  * When embedding dashboard in an iframe, some widgets don't apply the
    selected Segment [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #12172)
  * Actions tracked without a URL but with action_name should be
    displayed in the Visitor log [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #12182)
  * Formats numbers in the real time widget [by @AMcNeice, @mattab]
    (Closes: #12171)
  * UI: Backspace eats extra characters [by @Morerice, @sgiehl] (Closes:
    #12143)
  * issue with Widgetized dashboards: only [object Object] displayed [by
    @sgiehl] (Closes: #12113)
  * Customizable LESS var for header/menu links color [by @tsteur,
    @mattab] (Closes: #12201)
  * Issue the CORS header (Access-Control-Allow-Origin) also on Tracking
    API requests [by @mattab] (Closes: #12207)
  * Add visitor details events [by @tsteur] (Closes: #12262)
  * Sometimes the datatable footer controls can be hidden [by @sgiehl]
    (Closes: #10605)
  * Document how to view our UI demo page in developer guides (Closes:
    #11710)
  * Convert period selector to angular & allow plugins to add periods to
    the frontend [by @diosmosis, @mattab] (Closes: #11873)
  * Integrity Check wants to delete whole piwik directory [by @sgiehl]
    (Closes: #12290)
  * SEO Report average keyword position for google keywords (Closes:
    #2466)
  * New Report: the Top IP Addresses (Closes: #3613)
  * Include segment codes, where applicable, in all API results (Closes:
    #4381)
  * Widget - Table content disappears when "Display a table with more
    metrics" icon is clicked (Closes: #6330)
  * Action URL segment could filter both (Page URLs OR Event URLs) [by
    @mattab, @sgiehl] (Closes: #11131)
  * Keyboard shortcuts for Piwik app [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #5230)
  * Make it possible to configure max visits for visitor profile
    (Closes: #12045)
  * New "Event URL" segment `eventUrl` to segment on any Segment URL [by
    @mattab] (Closes: #12236)
  * Add possibility to restrict piwik access by ip [by @tsteur, @mattab]
    (Closes: #12242)
  * In log importer, allow filtering logs by host & datetime (new
    submodule commit + tests). [by @diosmosis, @mattab] (Closes: #12267)
  * Add possibility to ignore certain files in File integrity check [by
    @sgiehl] (Closes: #12268)
  * Show message if visitor log shows no data because the data was
    purged [by @tsteur, @mattab] (Closes: #12294)
  * Fixes seriespicker regression (changes to dashboard weren't saved
    anymore) [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #12223)
  * Small performance improvements in ArchiveProcessor [by @tsteur,
    @mattab] (Closes: #12288)
  * Improve serialize dataTable performance [by @tsteur, @mattab]
    (Closes: #12289)
  * use same padding for all widget content [by @fdellwing, @mattab]
    (Closes: #12220)
  * In Tracking code page, clarify that at least two domains need to be
    set in the Websites before one can enable "Enable cross domain
    tracking" feature (Closes: #11866)
  * Make all new segments "Pre-processed" when
    browser_archiving_disabled_enforce=1 [by @mattab] (Closes: #12254)
  * Mention that old report data can be invalidated using the new
    InvalidateReports plugin [by @mattab] (Closes: #12286)
  * make HTML in safemode-page valid [by @Findus23, @sgiehl] (Closes:
    #12270)
  * Updates device detector to 3.9.1 [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #12329)
  * Moved UI tests from core to custom alerts plugin [by @sgiehl]
    (Closes: #12330)
  * Log on DEBUG level all SQL archiving queries [by @mattab] (Closes:
    #12257)
  * Fix addTracker does not return the tracker instance [by @tsteur]
    (Closes: #12203)
  * Prevent error Key "url" for array with keys XXX does not exist [by
    @mattab, @sgiehl] (Closes: #12272)
  * Create a FAQ about tracking Internal newsletters (Closes: #11566)
  * [automatic translation update] Updated 615 strings in 7 languages
    (de, el, fi, ja, nl, pl, tr) [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #12180)
  * [automatic translation update] Updated 495 strings in 11 languages
    (pl, el, fa, it, ja, ko, nl, sv, tr, zh-cn, zh-tw) [by @sgiehl]
    (Closes: #12241)
  * [automatic translation update] Updated 887 strings in 13 languages
    (cs, de, es, fr, it, ja, nb, sq, sv, tr, el, pl, zh-tw) [by @sgiehl]
    (Closes: #12328)
  * added $_COOKIE to RequestSet environment [by @MichaelHeerklotz,
    @tsteur] (Closes: #11771)
  * Configuration for Piwik behind nginx reverse proxy with path rewrite
    [by @user121216, @mattab] (Closes: #12011)
  * Upgrade travis to trusty environment [by @mneudert, @sgiehl]
    (Closes: #12087)
  * Even more HTTPS links [by @Findus23, @sgiehl] (Closes: #12161)
  * Do not show bundles in premium feature widgets [by @tsteur, @mattab]
    (Closes: #12179)
  * Date:getUtcOffset() returns in seconds, not in minutes [by @sgiehl]
    (Closes: #12205)
  * Ignore Java detection on Edge as it doesn't work [by @sgiehl,
    @mattab] (Closes: #12214)
  * Command in update screen should include piwik-domain [by @sgiehl]
    (Closes: #12219)
  * New setting `show_update_notification_to_superusers_only` makes it
    possible to hide update notifications for users except for super
    users [by @peterbo, @sgiehl] (Closes: #12224)
  * When tracking, ignore user abort first [by @tsteur, @sgiehl]
    (Closes: #12226)
  * Add cross domain linking helper text [by @spacenate, @mattab]
    (Closes: #12235)
  * Check XML files in tests for validity [by @sgiehl, @mattab] (Closes:
    #12247)
  * Disallow indexing for pages doing a redirect [by @sgiehl, @mattab]
    (Closes: #12263)
  * Update Piwik PHP SDK to latest version (piwik/piwik-php-tracker) [by
    @mattab] (Closes: #12287)
