piwik (3.1.1-1) stable; urgency=high

  * Releasing Piwik 3.1.1
  * Fatal on real time widget, icon not defined [by @sgiehl] (Closes:
    #12037)
  * Range period should use existing archives of week/month/year periods
    if possible [by @tsteur, @mattab] (Closes: #12003)
  * 3.1.0 - Error 500 when getVisitorProfilePopup [by @sgiehl] (Closes:
    #12028)
  * The visit counter displays incorrect values after more than 100
    visits [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #12034)
  * Error "SQLSTATE[42S22]: Column not found: 1054 Unknown column
    'log_action_event_category.type' in 'field list'" [by @sgiehl]
    (Closes: #12036)
  * vendor/twig/twig/lib/Twig/Extension/Core.php(1560): Warning -
    constant(): Couldn't find constant
    Piwik::LABEL_ID_GOAL_IS_ECOMMERCE_ORDER [by @mattab] (Closes:
    #12070)
  * Remove commit 4e47c8 (Remove Tibet from the map) [by @sgiehl]
    (Closes: #6006)
  * Windows: rename(C:misc/GeoIPCity.dat.new,C:misc/GeoIPCity.dat): The
    process cannot access the file because it is being used by another
    process. (code: 32) [by @RMastop, @mattab] (Closes: #5050)
  * Raw html-output of error-message instead of rendered html [by
    @sgiehl] (Closes: #11172)
  * action_title_category_delimiter not respected for transitions view
    [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #11754)
  * Running the system check in the console may not show all of the
    information [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #11789)
  * Changes to support custom periods [by @diosmosis, @mattab] (Closes:
    #11837)
  * Updating Angular to version 1.6 [by @diosmosis, @mattab] (Closes:
    #11857)
  * regression for Plugins extending EventAction class [by @sgiehl,
    @Yiivgeny] (Closes: #12041)
  * Hide file integrity warnings from SEO site verification processes
    [by @mattab] (Closes: #12060)
