 -- Aurélien Requiem <aurelien@requiem.fr>  Sat, 16 Sep 2017 09:01:57 +1000

piwik (3.1.0-1) stable; urgency=high

  * Releasing Piwik 3.1.0
  * Ask for confirmation before granting Anonymous user a "view"
    permission on any website [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #11703)
  * New Piwik Certification program (Closes: #6172)
  * Measure how far users scroll down the page (Closes: #6069)
  * Customizeable / Extendable Visitor Profile & Visitor Log [by
    @sgiehl, @mattab] (Closes: #11579)
  * Make it easier to select websites in Zen Mode [by @tsteur] (Closes:
    #5367)
  * Improve switching between sites in reporting area when viewing an
    entity [by @tsteur, @sgiehl] (Closes: #11721)
  * error piwik_plugin_setting' doesn't exist after upgrade to v3 [by
    @sgiehl] (Closes: #11067)
  * Fix icon size for multi row evolution [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #11762)
  * Added new events for scheduled tasks [by @tsteur] (Closes: #11718)
  * Make TrackerUpdater a public API [by @tsteur] (Closes: #11724)
  * Allow setting custom headers for requests sent by
    Http::sendHttpRequestBy() [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #11738)
  * Create and Schedule a report: "Send report to" "Send to me" gets
    selected while editing [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #11622)
  * The wrong segment may be selected in the Segment editor [by @sgiehl]
    (Closes: #11787)
  * New INI setting "enable_internet_features" to disable outgoing
    network communications [by @ThaDafinser, @sgiehl] (Closes: #11465)
  * Add possibility to specify multiple plugins in activate / deactivate
    command [by @tsteur, @sgiehl] (Closes: #11733)
  * site-select shows ... , when the length of site name is longer than
    210px on Firefox 55.0b2. [by @Findus23, @sgiehl] (Closes: #11815)
  * Aggregate data for multiple (groups) of websites (Closes: #2541)
  * Import Google keywords from Webmaster tools in Piwik? (Closes:
    #4185)
  * Allow any plugin to extend and display data in the Visitor Log and
    Visitor Profile [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #6111)
  * Content-tracking: display content views and interactions in the
    Visitor log [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #6416)
  * Create Piwik <> CloudFlare integration [by @mattab] (Closes: #6797)
  * Add WebGL detection (available in new plugin DeviceFeatureWebGL) [by
    @sgiehl] (Closes: #10841)
  * display Device Type/Model in Visitor Profile pop-up [by @sgiehl]
    (Closes: #11520)
  * Piwik: Visitor Log and browser language [by @sgiehl] (Closes:
    #11707)
  * New method `setSecureCookie` that sets the cookie secure parameter
    [by @dudu84, @mattab] (Closes: #11891)
  * always return full Referrer URL in Live.getLastVisitDetails API [by
    @sgiehl] (Closes: #11976)
  * Allow different reports pre-archiving frequency for each period [by
    @tsteur] (Closes: #11965)
  * Fix metric selection in multi row evolution [by @sgiehl, @mattab]
    (Closes: #11953)
  * System Check says to delete vendor/szymach/c-pchart/app; doing so
    breaks Piwik [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #11978)
  * A long goal name will overflow the submenu [by @sgiehl] (Closes:
    #10614)
  * text displayed on top of each other on visitor profile window [by
    @sgiehl] (Closes: #11589)
  * Hide dashboard selection box if no dashboards available for
    selection [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #11757)
  * File Integrity Checks show only commands for Linux [by @sgiehl]
    (Closes: #11895)
  * Visitor Profile: order of visit numeration is confusing [by @sgiehl]
    (Closes: #8491)
  * Always show the link to "Visitor Profile" in the Visitor log
    (Closes: #10272)
  * "Visits by Server Time" graph should state 2pm 4pm 6pm instead of 2h
    4h 6h [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #10983)
  * Console config:set not working properly with string values and
    'section.key=value' syntax [by @mattab] (Closes: #11774)
  * write timezone (in our case: always "UTC") in log messages [by
    @patrickbr, @mattab] (Closes: #11893)
  * Add a link to Campaign tracking docs + URL Builder + Marketing
    Campaigns Reporting plugin [by @mattab] (Closes: #11997)
  * Use DI so plugins can change Custom Piwik JS [by @tsteur, @mattab]
    (Closes: #11717)
  * Improve handling of DevicePlugins to make it extendable [by @sgiehl]
    (Closes: #11748)
  * More generic raw log access [by @tsteur, @sgiehl] (Closes: #11775)
  * Uncomment a line to log on DEBUG level all archiving SQL queries [by
    @mattab] (Closes: #11812)
  * removes usage of deprecated jQuery.size() (#11874) [by @mneudert,
    @sgiehl] (Closes: #11883)
  * Custom logo is not shown in Update screen (Closes: #9291)
  * Action table for type '12' was not found during Actions archiving
    [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #11623)
  * Segment settings lost while updating segment [by @sgiehl] (Closes:
    #11624)
  * Separating read-only from read-write files: PIWIK_USER_PATH does not
    work [by @florianjacob, @mattab] (Closes: #11654)
  * Error when trying to check for updates and marketplace is disabled
    [by @tsteur] (Closes: #11714)
  * "Send an email when a plugin update is available" is default since
    Piwik 3.0.0-b1 [by @mattab, @sgiehl] (Closes: #11770)
  * Ecommerce Log always show segment "visitEcommerceStatus!=none" but
    should also apply the current selected segment [by @sgiehl] (Closes:
    #11788)
  * core:update command needs to be executed twice to find update [by
    @tsteur, @sgiehl] (Closes: #11831)
