piwik (3.0.3-1) stable; urgency=high

  * Releasing Piwik 3.0.3
  * Add option to disable plugin upload [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #11329)
  * New flag icons [by @Findus23, @mattab] (Closes: #11553)
  * Page Overlay may show the Piwik top bar behind the Website page
    overlay report [by @phoob, @mattab] (Closes: #11510)
  * Custom logo with white text and transparency is not visible on error
    pages [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #11419)
  * More secure / more random integer generation [by @tsteur] (Closes:
    #11473)
  * Fix multiple memory leaks in UserCountryMap [by @jvilk, @sgiehl]
    (Closes: #11350)
  * Fix memory leaks in data table / jqplot [by @jvilk, @sgiehl]
    (Closes: #11354)
  * Package "mass icons" via composer or submodule (Closes: #11370)
  * On "No data has been recorded yet" show links to guides, faq and
    features [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #11277)
  * Default value for a plugin setting should be the human readable
    value [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #11408)
  * "No data has been recorded yet" page should mention alternative SDKs
    [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #11436)
  * Pressing ALT+d keyboard combination should not open calendar [by
    @sgiehl] (Closes: #11498)
  * always use window.jQuery instead of $ in ui tests [by @tsteur]
    (Closes: #11505)
  * Replace pChart library with CpChart [by @sgiehl, @mattab] (Closes:
    #11559)
  * Marketplace Plugins ZIP file cannot be decompressed on some systems
    (eg. Windows) [by @sgiehl, @mattab] (Closes: #6538)
  * NumberFormatting problems, avg. page generation time is displayed
    with two decimal points in German language (Closes: #10596)
  * Running the archive via cron will result often in errors "Illegal
    string offset 'XAxisDisplay' 'XAxisFormat' " [by @sgiehl] (Closes:
    #11116)
  * Scheduled reports with images can generate error "Call to undefined
    method PiwikDataTableSimple::getDataTables() in
    plugins/ImageGraph/API.php on line 423 [by @mattab, @sgiehl]
    (Closes: #11276)
  * Scheduled PDF Reports: Report Referrer Type shows only keywords but
    not detailed titles [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #11323)
  * Integrity Check (whitelist misc/*.bin) + notice message [by @sgiehl]
    (Closes: #11389)
  * "Export as Image" exported image graph does not fit in the popover
    on displays > 2k [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #11464)
  * showColumns in Multisites API by pageviews does not work (Closes:
    #11471)
  * Fix Overlay bubbles on Firefox (and Opera Mini) [by @phoob, @mattab]
    (Closes: #11485)
  * Unable to find report 'Insights.getInsights'. [by @sgiehl] (Closes:
    #11489)
  * Error with mover and shaker widget after updating to Marketing
    Campaigns Reporting [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #11493)
  * Page Overlay: for links to the left of the screen, bubbles are
    partially hidden [by @phoob, @mattab] (Closes: #11511)
  * Premium Plugin Installer shows false error message after install [by
    @tsteur, @mattab] (Closes: #11512)
  * Undefined index warning in archive log (plugin: DevicesDetection)
    [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #11567)
  * Intl LC_NUMERIC use fallback if locale en_US not installed [by
    @peterbo, @sgiehl] (Closes: #11571)
  * [automatic translation update] Updated 244 strings in 9 languages
    (de, es, fi, fr, pl, it, el, sq, zh-tw) [by @sgiehl] (Closes:
    #11504)
  * Plugin Filter "third party" shows several plugins with author
    "piwik" [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #11145)
  * System tests: enable images generation in scheduled reports [by
    @mattab] (Closes: #11278)
  * Fix UIControl memory leak [by @jvilk, @sgiehl] (Closes: #11362)
  * Add system check for the hash() function [by @okay19, @sgiehl]
    (Closes: #11455)
  * Add unifont.ttf to file integrity whitelist [by @okay19, @sgiehl]
    (Closes: #11456)
  * Post JavaScript events when performing an action [by @tsteur]
    (Closes: #11463)
  * File integrity checker creates too long command lines. [by @sgiehl]
    (Closes: #11468)
  * Method description confusing in broadcast.js [by @sgiehl] (Closes:
    #11469)
  * Post current action in Template.beforeContent event [by @tsteur]
    (Closes: #11481)
  * Add new option to ignore ssl errors when running U tests via
    PhantomJS [by @tsteur] (Closes: #11482)
  * New event that lets plugins trigger notifications in the admin area
    [by @tsteur] (Closes: #11483)
  * Add possibility to select a specific frame within a page [by
    @tsteur] (Closes: #11484)
  * Improve URI check when showing external pages for Overlays [by
    @sgiehl, @mattab] (Closes: #11497)
  * Prepend only valid urls to api example links [by @sgiehl, @mattab]
    (Closes: #11502)
  * Make it possible to disable Flatten feature for a given report [by
    @sgiehl, @mattab] (Closes: #11529)
  * Drop temporary table when no longer needed [by @tsteur, @mattab]
    (Closes: #11544)
  * All icons in own repo and included as a submodule [by @mattab,
    @Findus23] (Closes: #11548)
  * Release Piwik 3.0.3-b1 [by @mattab] (Closes: #11533)
  * Release Piwik 3.0.3-b2 [by @mattab] (Closes: #11551)
  * fixed detect Asus zen 2 & go; + add zen 3 model + new brands [by
    @sanchezzzhak, @sgiehl] (Closes: #5593)
