    and reddit domains [by @spmedia, @sgiehl] (Closes: #32)
  * Fix nginx acess_log directive [by @paskal, @mattab] (Closes: #159)
  * Fix NGINX related documentation [by @easybe, @mattab] (Closes: #168)

