piwik (3.0.2-1) stable; urgency=high

  * Releasing Piwik 3.0.2
  * segment not valid-errors when filtering for operating system [by
    @sgiehl] (Closes: #11321)
  * Email reports in HTML: Updated styling to be consistent with new
    Custom Alerts emails design [by @afroboya, @mattab] (Closes: #11251)
  * Zen in Visitor Log, Visitor Profile: hide http:// and https:// from
    URLs [by @mattab] (Closes: #5317)
  * When there is no data for a website, as soon as a visit was detected
    reload the report for Today [by @mattab] (Closes: #11275)
  * Visitor log: "Close" button of visitor profile stays visible [by
    @sgiehl] (Closes: #11302)
  * piwik.js: Cross domain tracking [by @tsteur, @mattab] (Closes:
    #2211)
  * piwik.js: cross domain POST and automatically
    setRequestMethod('POST') when request > 2K [by @tsteur, @mattab]
    (Closes: #2321)
  * LTV analytics - Ecommerce Life Time Value metric in Piwik Visitor
    Profile and Live APIs [by @mattab] (Closes: #2750)
  * New Reporting API: return the mapping from two letter country code
    to the country name [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #11109)
  * SMS Provider: new integration for ASP SMS [by @sgiehl] (Closes:
    #11213)
  * When printing Piwik reports, make the print version useful and
    beautiful [by @niks799, @mattab] (Closes: #11242)
  * Cross Domain linking in JavaScript tracking client piwik.js [by
    @tsteur, @mattab] (Closes: #11243)
  * Added new keyboard shortcuts, "s" for selector, "d" for calendar,
    "w" for site selector [by @mattab] (Closes: #11252)
  * Ecommerce Life Time Value metrics + New Ecommerce section in Visitor
    Profile [by @mattab] (Closes: #11294)
  * New "Enable cross domain linking" checkbox in Javascript Tracker
    Code generator (Advanced section) [by @tsteur, @mattab] (Closes:
    #11295)
  * Improvements for tracking of single page applications [by @tsteur,
    @mattab] (Closes: #11344)
  * Garbled text of translation [by @mattab] (Closes: #11130)
  * Small performance improvement [by @tsteur] (Closes: #11273)
  * Visitors in real time data gone after 4PM Piwik 3.0 (Closes: #11165)
  * Fix typo in example report [by @tsteur, @mattab] (Closes: #11164)
  * Improved old icons [by @Findus23, @mattab] (Closes: #11190)
  * Improved the design of Visitor Profile for more clarity [by @mattab]
    (Closes: #11218)
  * Tag cloud visualisation more readable: Colour and Size changes [by
    @sonika-k, @mattab] (Closes: #11203)
  * Visitor profile: use consistent close icon [by @niks799, @mattab]
    (Closes: #11231)
  * Better icons for SEO widget [by @Findus23, @sgiehl] (Closes: #11245)
  * Define icon size for plugin icon in popup in visitor log [by
    @Findus23, @mattab] (Closes: #11271)
  * Fix Piwik UI becomes very slow when having many rows [by @tsteur]
    (Closes: #11308)
  * Dev documentation for getAsyncTracker function signatures not
    correct (Closes: #11207)
  * Update button should be more easily clickable in dashboard [by
    @CheweyZ, @mattab] (Closes: #11211)
  * Show links as underlined in reports help texts [by @niks799,
    @mattab] (Closes: #11217)
  * Replace prefilled values in Name & SiteUrl with placeholders. [by
    @NickWilde1990, @mattab] (Closes: #11279)
  * Added a new method that allows plugins to define metrics we expect
    to see percentage values [by @tsteur] (Closes: #11274)
  * X-Frame-Options header set to empty value [by @mattab] (Closes:
    #10167)
  * Downloading some HTML reports shows a "Success:ok" after the HTML
    (Closes: #11014)
  * "File integrity" modal is unusable as content is displayed as HTML
    entities [by @mattab] (Closes: #11167)
  * Personal settings - language selection overlapped by other dropdown
    (Closes: #11180)
  * Optional item "GD > 2.x + Freetype" in system check are Required [by
    @mattab] (Closes: #11316)
  * WARNING: /plugins/CorePluginsAdmin/Controller.php(272) ob_clean():
    failed to delete buffer. No buffer to delete [by @mattab] (Closes:
    #11320)
  * Duplicating data using multiple Piwik trackers doesn't work
    (documentation) [by @mattab] (Closes: #11340)
  * Fix dataTable label suffix is directly shown after prefix but not
    after the value itself [by @tsteur, @mattab] (Closes: #11378)
  * SEO widget: Image Size too large (Closes: #11192)
  * Clicking on the "Dashboard" top link hides all dashboard content [by
    @sgiehl, @tsteur, @mattab] (Closes: #11386)
