piwik (3.0.1-1) stable; urgency=high

  * Releasing Piwik 3.0.1
  * More beautiful (and vectorised?) icons for browsers, operating
    systems, device types, device plugins [by @Findus23, @sgiehl]
    (Closes: #10587)
  * When safe mode is displayed, and Super User was not logged in
    already, let Super User display the full safe mode to troubleshoot
    further [by @mattab] (Closes: #11082)
  * Unique visitors are displayed/processed wrongly when amount is
    bigger than 1000 [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #11090)
  * File integrity checker now reports files found in the filesystem but
    not expected to be there [by @mattab] (Closes: #11096)
  * Number of pageviews missing in realtime map tooltip [by @sgiehl]
    (Closes: #11119)
  * Widgetized Dashboard accessed with token is no longer working after
    updating to 3.0 (Closes: #11055)
  * updated browser and os icons [by @Findus23, @sgiehl] (Closes:
    #11063)
  * Layout issue in installation process (Closes: #11122)
  * Display safe mode when a third party plugin triggers error such as
    "Call to undefined method PiwikMenuMenuTop::add()" [by @tsteur]
    (Closes: #10876)
  * Safe mode: Display plugin versions next to plugin names [by @mattab]
    (Closes: #11043)
  * On Apache server: Internal Server Error due to .htaccess [by
    @mattab] (Closes: #11040)
  * Non Well Formed Numeric Value in Live Plugin in 3.0 [by @mattab]
    (Closes: #11066)
  * fix WARNING:
    /home/piwik/htdocs/plugins/Referrers/Controller.php(422) Warning -
    Invalid argument supplied for foreach() [by @mattab] (Closes:
    #11098)
  * Update FAQ: How do I change the Super User's password when password
    recovery emails are not sent? (Closes: #10941)
  * [automatic translation update] Updated 1042 strings in 51 languages
    (ja, zh-tw, da, ar, be, bg, bs, ca, cs, cy, de, el, es, et, eu, fa,
    fi, fr, gl, he, hi, hr, hu, id, is, it, ka, ko, lt, lv, nb, nl, nn,
    pl, pt-br, pt, ro, ru, sk, sl, sq, sr, sv, ta, te, th, tr, uk, vi,
    zh-cn, tl) [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #11080)
  * [automatic translation update] Updated 1201 strings in 14 languages
    (zh-tw, ar, da, el, es, fa, fr, hu, it, pl, ru, sq, sv, tl) [by
    @sgiehl] (Closes: #11134)
  * [automatic translation update] Updated 352 strings in 1 languages
    (zh-tw) [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #11142)
  * Allow plugin to decide about archiving without visits: new method
    PiwikPluginArchiver::shouldRunEvenWhenNoVisits() [by @sgiehl,
    @mattab] (Closes: #10719)
  * Use gender-neutral wording where possible [by @x3ro, @mattab]
    (Closes: #10982)
  * Remove on pixel overlapping boxshadow on the corners [by
    @michelgotta, @mattab] (Closes: #11052)
  * when there's an error during Twig template processing, or during
    LESS css compiling, or a generic PHP error, display the safe mode
    [by @mattab] (Closes: #11083)
  * Enabling WOFF files under Windows IIS [by @ksubileau, @mattab]
    (Closes: #11091)
  * updated searchEngine and social icons [by @Findus23, @sgiehl]
    (Closes: #11093)
  * Clarify FAQ instructions for logme mechanism (automatically logging
    in users when they click from my app to Piwik) (Closes: #11094)
  * Live API: New 'generationTimeMilliseconds' field used to process
    Average generation time in Visitor Profile [by @mattab] (Closes:
    #11095)
  * Do not add Options -Indexes to .htaccess [by @mattab] (Closes:
    #11097)
  * Fix Numeric value out of range: 1264 Out of range value for column
    'interaction_position' [by @mattab] (Closes: #11101)
  * updated plugin icons [by @Findus23, @sgiehl] (Closes: #11121)
  * System check, File integrity: Report directories to delete
    separately + display command to delete directories and files [by
    @mattab] (Closes: #11123)
  * Release Piwik 3.0.1-b1 [by @mattab] (Closes: #11103)
  * Release Piwik 3.0.1-b2 [by @mattab] (Closes: #11124)
  * Release Piwik 3.0.1-b3 [by @mattab] (Closes: #11154)
  * Added new event for totals calculation [by @tsteur, @mattab]
    (Closes: #11139)
  * Updating piwik/referrer-spam-blacklist (1.0.11) and piwik/piwik-php-
    tracker (1.1.0) [by @mattab] (Closes: #11158)
  * Release Piwik 3.0.1 (Closes: #11156)
  * Device models are not recognized for various devices [by @sgiehl]
    (Closes: #5548)
  * recognize PritTorrent as bot [by @eteubert, @sgiehl] (Closes: #5564)
  * isTouchEnabled - array instead of boolean [by @sgiehl] (Closes:
    #5568)
  * Fixes fixtures for some YAML parsers [by @mneudert, @sgiehl]
    (Closes: #5569)
  * timer4web.com (Closes: #532)
  * Add stocktwits.com (Closes: #533)
  * add adsensecustomsearchads.com (Closes: #547)
  * New spammer meduza-consult.ru [by @mattb77, @spmedia] (Closes: #548)
  * New spammer azbukafree.com [by @mattb77, @spmedia] (Closes: #550)
  * Add mockupui.com [by @ericguirbal, @spmedia] (Closes: #554)
  * Issue with file_get_contents and PHP 5.5 [by @braekling] (Closes:
    #6)
  * Add support for fetching the content with CURL when fopen is
    disabled in PHP configuration [by @mattab] (Closes: #21)
  * Output the image/gif HTTP header only when needed [by @mattab]
    (Closes: #22)
  * Add possibility to add custom tracking parameter (Closes: #6)
  * New const for number of max categories [by @tsteur, @mattab]
    (Closes: #22)

