  * Drop support for PHP 5.4, require PHP 5.5 [by @mattab] (Closes:
    #8156)
  * Half of the dashboard manager dropdown is cut off now due to it's
    placement in top controls [by @tsteur] (Closes: #9100)
  * Add support for "issues" link to plugin.json and display in
    Marketplace / Core (Closes: #4570)
