 -- Aurélien Requiem <aurelien@requiem.fr>  Tue, 04 Oct 2016 17:24:20 +1100

piwik (2.16.3-1) stable; urgency=high

  * Releasing Piwik 2.16.3
  * Mark 2.16.3 DB upgrade as Major as it updates a field on the
    log_visit table: visit_entry_idaction_url [by @mattab] (Closes:
    #10631)
  * Create index.htm files in all tmp/ sub-folder as an additional
    safety net [by @mattab, @tsteur] (Closes: #10414)
  * Add support for "issues" link to plugin.json and display in
    Marketplace / Core (Closes: #4570)
  * Moved UI screenshots inside the repository using git-lfs [by
    @mnapoli, @sgiehl] (Closes: #8392)
  * When updating the config file failed (or when any other file is not
    writable...), the Updater (for core or plugins) will now
    automatically throw an error and cancel the update [by @mattab]
    (Closes: #10423)
  * Automatically update all marketplace plugins when updating Piwik [by
    @tsteur, @mattab] (Closes: #10527)
  * Warn users (in all admin pages) when the PHP version is not recent
    enough to upgrade Piwik to latest major version [by @mattab]
    (Closes: #10633)
  * PHP 7: when there is a fatal error in API request processing,
    display the original error in the api response [by @mattab, @tsteur]
    (Closes: #10406)
  * When the core:update command is executed with a user:group different
    from the user:group that owns the Piwik files, display a message to
    indicate how to fix file permissions [by @mattab, @tsteur] (Closes:
    #10424)
  * Show a better selection of data, in the default dashboard layout [by
    @mattab] (Closes: #10598)
  * Display warning in console command when the DB upgrade is major [by
    @mattab] (Closes: #10630)
  * issue tracker: remove the LTS milestone on Github (Closes: #10425)
  * As a Piwik plugin user, I want to leave a feedback to the plugin
    developer (Closes: #5395)
  * Remove tests from plugin when packaging on the Marketplace (Closes:
    #6386)
  * Move UI screenshots to git-lfs [by @mnapoli, @sgiehl] (Closes:
    #7726)
  * Split piwik.js into multiple files and provide a merged one [by
    @tsteur, @mattab] (Closes: #10441)
  * Daily Scheduled Reports sent one hour late, if daylight saving time
    is active [by @sgiehl] - Sponsored by Piwik PRO] (Closes: #7658)
  * When opening the visitor profile, the Segment is applied, which can
    cause the Visitor Profile to be incomplete [by @tsteur] - Sponsored
    by Piwik PRO] (Closes: #9893)
  * .htaccess file ownership in 2.16.1 [by @mattab, @tsteur] (Closes:
    #10143)
  * Correct wording: Donation widget only displayed to superusers [by
    @johnrackles, @mattab, @tsteur] (Closes: #10357)
  * Plugins: Generating a new visualisation via
    'generate:visualizationplugin' fails with InvalidArgumentException
    [by @tsteur] (Closes: #10374)
  * Fatal error when requesting RSS format: Call to a member function
    getTimezone() on boolean [by @mattab, @tsteur] (Closes: #10399)
  * DoNotTrack: Tk response header value wrong (Closes: #10427)
  * Deprecated - Non-static method
    PiwikDbAdapter::isRecommendedAdapter() should not be called
    statically, [by @tsteur] (Closes: #10463)
  * Fix possible twig error in updater if support is defined but no
    email [by @tsteur] (Closes: #10501)
  * Cannot Generate Tests using Piwik Console [by @tsteur] (Closes:
    #10368)
  * Update documentation how to install Piwik from git on Windows for
    developers (Closes: #10370)
  * Update Docs: Tracking Events with Custom Dimension (Closes: #10389)
  * Implement ordering by "last updated", "new" at
    http://plugins.piwik.org/ (Closes: #9105)
  * Update to Device detector 3.7.1 [by @mattab, @tsteur] (Closes:
    #10362)
  * Added new event Archiving.makeNewArchiverObject to allow customising
    plugin archiving [by @mgazdzik, @mattab] (Closes: #10366)
  * Add tests for piwik/searchengine-and-social-list#14 for Japanese
    search engines and keywords [by @piwikjapan, @sgiehl] (Closes:
    #10440)
  * Define changelog, faq and documentation in separate files in plugins
    [by @tsteur] (Closes: #10481)
  * Exposing some DOM methods for Piwik.js [by @tsteur, @mattab]
    (Closes: #10522)
  * Additional information passed in the hook "isExcludedVisit" (issue
    #10415) [by @Thomas-F, @mattab] (Closes: #10564)
  * If Piwik is not installed yet, it's possible the tmp/ folder is not
    writable, display a useful error message [by @mattab] (Closes:
    #10634)
  * [automatic translation update] Updated 103 strings in 36 languages
    (fa, fr, sv, tr, ar, cs, da, de, el, es, fi, it, ja, ko, nb, nl, pl,
    pt-br, ro, ru, sk, sr, tl, uk, zh-cn, be, bg, ca, id, lt, lv, pt,
    sl, sq, vi, zh-tw) [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #10384)
  * [automatic translation update] Updated 118 strings in 4 languages
    (cs, it, nb, de) [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #10442)
  * [automatic translation update] Updated 201 strings in 8 languages
    (cs, de, el, es, fr, nb, tr, it) [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #10585)
  * Release 2.16.2 [by @mattab, @sgiehl, @tsteur] (Closes: #10058)
  * Possibly broken encoding & rule in tablet.yml [by @sgiehl] (Closes:
    #5355)
  * Add some bots found in logs [by @HostedDinner, @sgiehl] (Closes:
    #5518)
  * Detection of dbbrowser and Streamy browsers [by @Wazelin, @sgiehl]
    (Closes: #5521)
