    @sgiehl] (Closes: #5536)
  * Optimized Catchpoint lookup [by @sckoop, @sgiehl] (Closes: #5537)
  * ViewSonic V500 is recognized as "smart display" instead of
    smartphone [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #5538)
