 -- Aurélien Requiem <aurelien@requiem.fr>  Mon, 03 Oct 2016 15:46:10 +1100

piwik (2.16.2-1) stable; urgency=high

  * Releasing Piwik 2.16.2
  * New report listing all User ID, in Visitors > Users [by @alexkuk,
    @tsteur] (Closes: #9883)
  * Full PHP 7 compatibility [by @tsteur, @mattab] (Closes: #8689)
  * Piwik.js: Support for sending data to multiple idSites (Closes:
    #7257)
  * The string to escape is not a valid UTF-8 string in
    "@CoreHome/getDefaultIndexView.twig". [by @mattab, @tsteur] (Closes:
    #4410)
  * Piwik JS Tracker: Easier way for using multiple trackers [by
    @mattab] (Closes: #9525)
  * Manage websites: Links to website [by @Peteys93, @tsteur] (Closes:
    #10066)
  * Add a web app manifest so you can add Piwik icon to the launcher in
    Mobile devices [by @tsteur] (Closes: #10214)
  * piwik.js: Access is denied in Internet Explorer 8 within IFrame [by
    @Kijewski, @mattab] (Closes: #10105)
  * Let users exclude IPv6 address ranges using archives debian Makefile
    piwik README.md scripts tmp wildcard exclusion rules for IPv6 such
    as 2001:DB8:*:*:*:*:*:* [by @mattab] (Closes: #9411)
  * Document new way to easily send tracking requests to multiple Piwik
    servers and/or multiple websites ID [by @mattab] (Closes: #10174)
  * Manage goals: Help text is misplaced [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #9995)
  * Unlimited paging in lists when selecting all [by @sgiehl] (Closes:
    #10044)
  * 7 days in Evolution over the period when Period is Day [by @tsteur]
    (Closes: #10130)
  * Improve detection for empty keywords for referring search engines
    [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #10163)
  * Piwik.js: add callback ability to trackPageView [by @er314, @tsteur]
    (Closes: #10172)
  * New Goals.getGoal(idSite, idGoal) API method to get a single goal
    [by @tsteur] (Closes: #10305)
  * Embed Piwik Report - columnDescription-bubbles are out of view [by
    @sgiehl - Sponsored by Piwik PRO] (Closes: #9838)
  * Update country flags for Tokelau, Myanmar, Lesotho, Libya and French
    Guiana to their modern versions. [by @polyfloyd, @sgiehl] (Closes:
    #10242)
  * When changing segment definition, inform the user that past data
    will be cleared [by @sgiehl - Sponsored by Piwik PRO] (Closes:
    #9984)
  * on Mobile Device, let users drag and drop items such as segments,
    using touchpunch library [by @wronan, @mattab] (Closes: #10045)
  * Tweak core:archive output logging to better explain where to find
    error log depending on server configuration [by @mattab, @sgiehl]
    (Closes: #10189)
  * piwik.js: Prepend a slash to all paths such as when users don't
    specify leading slash for URL path [by @mattab] (Closes: #10302)
  * Accessibility: set a title attribute on Main menu item for better
    experience on screen readers [by @tyrylu, @sgiehl] (Closes: #10160)
  * Don't try to display a custom logo or favicon if they don't exist
    [by @ksubileau, @tsteur] (Closes: #9966)
  * Updates device detector to latest version [by @sgiehl] (Closes:
    #10204)
  * Professional Services for Piwik, neutral branding within Piwik app
    [by @mattab] (Closes: #10339)
  * Creating visitor segment in mobile phone fails [by @tsteur, @mattab]
    (Closes: #9196)
  * Bing, Yahoo, etc. may be shown as "Websites" instead of "Search
    engines" (Closes: #9438)
  * Some periods may not be archived at all [by @tsteur] (Closes: #9468)
  * Outlinks and downloads may not be tracked if users don't specify a
    leading slash in paths (eg. setDomains) (Closes: #9872)
  * Goal conversion sometimes not tracked when a Goal matches event
    names/categories/actions [by @mattab] (Closes: #9923)
  * Don't try to display a custom logo or favicon if they don't exist
    [by @ksubileau, @tsteur] (Closes: #10000)
  * PHP 7, API: actual error messages not shown when a PHP Error occurs
    [by @mattab] (Closes: #10115)
  * Error: Invalid dimension 'null'. [by @mattab] (Closes: #10117)
  * When a custom search engine is added and it has the same domain as
    the website tracked, referrer is not detected as expected [by
    @sgiehl - Sponsored by Piwik PRO] (Closes: #10121)
  * trackLink does not invoke callback if request is done via GET ? [by
    @er314] (Closes: #10153)
  * Overlay bubbles are not displayed if custom port in
    http://hostname:port/ [by @tsteur] (Closes: #10169)
  * JavaScript SDK: Calling an undefined JS API method should trigger a
    useful error message to help users locate the issue quickly [by
    @mattab] (Closes: #10175)
  * Error in visit details when UserCountry plugin is disabled (Closes:
    #10206)
  * addEcommerceItem not added to subsequent order [by @mattab] (Closes:
    #10252)
  * API: CSV exports compatibility with &date=previousX, &date=lastX and
    more [by @tsteur, @mattab] (Closes: #10273)
  * Archiving output showing always "0" visits for period = day summary
    [by @mattab] (Closes: #10276)
  * New install of Piwik 2.16.1 incorrectly reports Tracker Status 500
    "GET request to piwik.php failed." [by @mattab] (Closes: #10283)
  * Tracked resolution of Mac Retina displays is wrong (Closes: #10289)
  * Searching recursively in sub-tables should work as expected [by
    @mattab] (Closes: #10303)
  * Piwik.js: setting custom dimensions fails on IE8 with
    customDimensionIdsAlreadyHandled is a array,has no indexOf() in line
    3932 [by @sgiehl, @mattab] (Closes: #10310)
  * [automatic translation update] Updated 42 strings in 5 languages
    (ru, de, sv, pt-br, fr) [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #10092)
  * [automatic translation update] Updated 491 strings in 48 languages
    (am, ar, be, bg, ca, cs, da, de, el, es, et, eu, fa, fi, fr, gl, he,
