piwik (2.16.1-2) stable; urgency=high

  * Added support for PHP7

 -- Aurélien Requiem <aurelien@requiem.fr>  Fri, 08 Jul 2016 19:45:52 +1000

piwik (2.16.1-1) stable; urgency=high

  * Releasing Piwik 2.16.1
  * Improve all websites dashboard performance (Closes: #9662)
  * Some periods may not be archived at all [by @tsteur] (Closes: #9468)
  * When a user changes a password (or resets password), inform user
    that token_auth will change [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #9833)
  * Apply offset and limit correctly to the Visitor Log SQL queries [by
    @mattab] (Closes: #9774)
  * Better document how to measure Domains, Sub-domains, or a mix of
    both, and how to correctly configure the JavaScript tracker with
    setDomains, setCookieDomain and setCookiePath [by @mattab] (Closes:
    #9932)
  * Day names not displayed in some languages [by @sgiehl] (Closes:
    #9717)
  * Migrating Piwik forums to use Discourse (Closes: #8747)
  * Error when running console command 'usercountry:attribute' to
    attribute past geo location data [by @tsteur] (Closes: #9912)
  * use consistent wording "processed" to make it clear the segment will
    be processed across all websites [by @mattab] (Closes: #9801)
  * Create/Remove a new dashboard is not working as expected (Closes:
    #9750)
  * Visitor log: remove "google keyword ranking" extra linebreak [by
    @sgiehl] (Closes: #9930)
  * URL query string parameters to remove from URL are now stored in
    config file [by @mattab] (Closes: #9986)
  * Piwik.js 'setDomains' method supports page wildcards matching:
    example.com/index* [by @mattab] (Closes: #9979)
  * Set returning visitor flag when user first visited the website at
    least 1 day ago [by @mattab] (Closes: #9942)
  * Fix behaviour of reset password form on error [by @sgiehl, @tsteur]
    (Closes: #9880)
  * Add possibility to use piwik.js via browserify [by @alexbeletsky,
    @tsteur] (Closes: #9876)
  * Piwik.js: handle clickable phone number 'tel:' (Closes: #9865)
  * .htaccess files should be generated also for non-apache servers [by
    @mattab] (Closes: #9810)
  * Better archive logging message 'tracking data found for website id
    since... ' [by @mattab] (Closes: #9809)
  * Add 'sid' to the list of query params excluded by default (Closes:
    #9789)
  * Show an error message in case we deactivate a plugin because of
    missing dependencies [by @tsteur] (Closes: #9676)
  * Some elements may appear over the popover - z-index issue on profile
    settings page [by @mattab] (Closes: #9868)
  * Consistent design when hovering in segment selection [by @sgiehl,
    @tsteur] (Closes: #9740)
  * Display a useful message when there is no goal conversion (Closes:
    #9909)
  * Improve usage of placeholder in translations [by @sgiehl] (Closes:
    #9546)
  * Remove unused variable from piwik.js [by @BBosman, @tsteur] (Closes:
    #9831)
  * Simplified console output and removed stars archives debian Makefile
    piwik README.md scripts tmp [by @mattab, @tsteur] (Closes: #9824)
  * Measure which Mysql versions is currently used [by @tsteur] (Closes:
    #9734)
  * Open source plugins now upload their builds artifacts to a public
    space [by @mattab] (Closes: #7761)
  * Add possibility to set a system setting is writable/not writable [by
    @tsteur] (Closes: #9794)
  * 403 error on icon font file plugins/Morpheus/fonts/piwik.eot [by
    @ksubileau] (Closes: #9967)
  * Can't add a goal based on page title (Closes: #9955)
  * Visitor log: remove link when provider is "Unknown" [by @mattab]
    (Closes: #9945)
  * Outlinks and downloads not being tracked in Firefox [by @tsteur]
    (Closes: #9924)
  * LoginHttpAuth is in .gitmodules but not listed in plugins/ directory
    on Github [by @mattab] (Closes: #9908)
  * "Keep Page URL fragments when tracking Page URLs" not persistent [by
    @tsteur] (Closes: #9896)
  * Warning - array_udiff_assoc(): Argument #2 is not an array - Piwik
    2.16.0 (Closes: #9892)
  * Disabling overlay plugin causes dashboard not to load (Closes:
    #9870)
  * The site search HTML chars are not displayed correctly in visitor
    log [by @andrzejewsky] (Closes: #9862)
  * When Marketplace is disabled, it is not possible to access Manage
    Themes page [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #9857)
  * SQLSTATE[23000]: Integrity constraint violation when trying to open
    transition [by @mattab] (Closes: #9822)
  * Undefined index in plugins/Live/Visitor.php(161) (using Piwik
    2.16.0) (Closes: #9820)
  * Transitions: %s is not replaced by a value (Closes: #9799)
  * Clicking on the 'Goal metrics' icon in 'All Referrers' report, the
    column headers are missing the goal names (Closes: #9773)
  * Changing password using an HTML entity may result in an error
    (Closes: #9763)
  * Warning - is_dir(): open_basedir restriction in effect.
    File(/var/tmp/) is not within the allowed path (Closes: #9722)
  * Error in Events report: Unsupported pivot: the subtable dimension
    for 'Events.Event Actions' does not match the requested pivotBy
    dimension (Closes: #9716)
  * Website chooser may not work because of a whitespace problem [by
    @tsteur, @sgiehl, @mattab] (Closes: #9712)
  * ReferenceError: DataTable_RowActions_Transitions is not defined
    (Closes: #9704)
  * Pivot is not correctly remembered (Closes: #9667)
  * Function getPiwikUrlForOverlay returns wrong URL when it receives
    different URL than suffixed with piwik.php (Closes: #9467)
  * Reloading a report whose saved ViewDataTable params includes pivotBy
    results in incorrect report rendering (Closes: #7505)
  * usernames should allow German umlauts characters (Closes: #7114)
  * piwik.js: remove the feature of `setDomains` that sets cookie path
    [by @mattab] (Closes: #9933)
  * New automated test to detect when piwik.js minified file is out of
    sync with original piwik.js (Closes: #8195)
  * Fix metadata problem for goal reports [by @sgiehl, @mattab] (Closes:
    #9993)
  * When Github is down some scheduled tasks trigger warnings [by
    @tsteur] (Closes: #10010)
  * When forcing archiving on multiple sites, it silently fails if one
    site doesn't exist any more [by @tsteur] (Closes: #10005)
  * When URLs contains: /0/ it shows in the report UI as: /-/ [by
    @sgiehl, @mattab] (Closes: #9628)
  * Live API when a Segment is used: Select 10 times more rows so that
    resultset after grouping is more likely to contain enough rows [by
    @mattab] (Closes: #10024)
  * Update Omnifixture and add test fixture [by @andrzejewsky, @mattab]
    (Closes: #10020)
  * Display labels correctly in Excel / LibreOffice [by @mattab]
    (Closes: #10015)
  * [automatic translation update] Updated 77 strings in 4 languages
    (nb, ru, pl, sr) [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #9994)
  * [automatic translation update] Updated 219 strings in 9 languages
    (fi, el, ko, nb, ru, sq, sv, tr, lt) [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #9964)
  * [automatic translation update] Updated 93 strings in 26 languages
    (ro, vi, cs, de, el, fi, fr, ko, pt-br, sk, tr, da, it, ca, es, hi,
    hu, id, ja, nb, nl, ru, sl, sr, sv, zh-cn) [by @sgiehl] (Closes:
    #9888)
  * [automatic translation update] Updated 176 strings in 34 languages
    (zh-cn, am, be, bg, da, el, fa, fi, fr, he, hi, id, ko, pl, ro, ru,
    sl, sv, tl, tr, uk, zh-tw, de, sq, cs, es, et, it, ja, nb, nl, pt-
    br, sr, vi) [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #9860)
  * [automatic translation update] Updated 44 strings in 2 languages
    (sq, sv) [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #9811)
  * [automatic translation update] Updated 415 strings in 8 languages
    (sq, tr, de, th, zh-cn, es, cs, el) [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #9805)
  * [automatic translation update] Updated 2284 strings in 49 languages
    (ar, fr, be, bg, bn, bs, ca, cs, da, de, el, es, et, eu, fa, fi, gl,
    he, hi, hr, hu, id, it, ja, ko, lt, lv, nb, nl, nn, pl, pt-br, pt,
    ro, ru, sk, sl, sq, sr, sv, ta, te, th, tl, tr, uk, vi, zh-cn, zh-
    tw) [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #9721)
  * [automatic translation update] Updated 45 strings in 4 languages
    (nl, hu, de, ru) [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #10027)
  * Update documentation: Placement of JavaScript tracker code (Closes:
    #9802)
  * enable https on forum.piwik.org (Closes: #9443)
  * Name for our new Piwik 2 and 3 develop branches (feedback needed
    quickly) (Closes: #9891)
  * We are hiring engineers to build an awesome product and platform
    used by millions of people [by @mattab] (Closes: #9814)
  * Detect Web TV as model instead of brand [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #5479)
