 -- Aurélien Requiem <aurelien@requiem.fr>  Tue, 12 Apr 2016 11:31:20 +1000

piwik (2.16.0-1) stable; urgency=high

  * Releasing Piwik 2.16.0
  * Let me view all visitors who reached a specific goal via a link in
    all Goal reports (Closes: #7411)
  * Allow any plugin system setting to be overwritten in the config file
    [by @tsteur] (Closes: #9521)
  * Don't let "admin" users see all other users in Piwik [by @tsteur,
    @mattab] (Closes: #4314)
  * Multiple visits with each pageview when "/?pk_campaign" is used [by
    @tsteur] (Closes: #9299)
  * No data in segmented visitor log for urls with ampersand [by
    @tsteur] (Closes: #9192)
  * Publicise the LogViewer plugin [by @mattab] (Closes: #8834)
  * Administration > Diagnostics > Config file lets Super User view all
    config values in the UI [by @tsteur, @mattab] (Closes: #9526)
  * New segment DeviceBrand [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #9501)
  * New segment: ActionType [by @tsteur, @mattab] (Closes: #9314)
  * Add new segment ActionUrl [by @tsteur] (Closes: #9224)
  * Custom Dimensions: making Custom Variables more powerful and easier
    to use [by @tsteur, @danmichaelo] (Closes: #9129)
  * Adding new command config:set command to set INI config [by
    @diosmosis, @mattab] (Closes: #9124)
  * Add Ability to Export ALL Records (new 'all' option in the Row limit
    selector) (Closes: #9068)
  * New segment operators: "Starts with" and "Ends with" [by @tsteur]
    (Closes: #8076)
  * Display the "Segmented Visitor Log" icon in sub-tables reports [by
    @diosmosis, @sgiehl] (Closes: #7213)
  * Let Super User view and edit segments created by other users [by
    @mattab] (Closes: #6766)
  * Piwik compatible with old Mysql 4.1 (cannot connect to DB since
    2.15.0) [by @Joey3000] (Closes: #9088)
  * Allow switching to 24h format for languages with AM/PM formatted
    timestamps as default [by @mattab] (Closes: #9082)
  * when "Only track visits and actions when the action URL starts with
    one of the above URLs" is enabled for a website, action URLs on an
    Alias URL subdomain will not be tracked anymore (Closes: #9428)
  * Running core:delete-logs-data with option -no-interaction doesn't do
    anything (Closes: #9316)
  * Improvements to search engine and social network detection [by
    @sgiehl, @mattab] (Closes: #9174)
  * ./console customvariables:set-max-custom-variables should run in no
    interaction mode [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #8469)
  * Events reports: option to view all columns: min, max and avg values
    [by @tsteur] (Closes: #6761)
