    #4789)
  * The pragma "disableCookies" does not work in some browsers [by
    @tsteur] (Closes: #7494)
  * Very slow SQL queries when archiving a segment for an unknown action
    (Closes: #8102)
  * Details cut-off on Visitor Log modal pop-up (screenshot included)
    [by @mattab] (Closes: #7812)
  * Make sure to escape error messages [by @tsteur] (Closes: #8197)
  * While loading Piwik, the top menu displays all language names in a
    row for 1 second [by @tsteur] (Closes: #7736)
  * Disallow api content to be loaded within Piwik [by @mattab] (Closes:
    #8182)
  * Create a page that lists all available tracker SDKs for "universal"
    properties (Closes: #8039)
