piwik (2.13.0-1) stable; urgency=high

  * Releasing Piwik 2.13.0
  * New design for Maintenance mode [by @mnapoli] (Closes: #7620)
  * New design for Updater screen [by @mnapoli, @mattab] (Closes: #7450)
  * Add Help link to top menu [by @mnapoli, @mattab] (Closes: #7642)
  * Refreshed the copy of "Help" page [by @mattab] (Closes: #7637)
  * Make it easier to see how to edit a Goal [by @mnapoli] (Closes:
    #7345)
  * "Manage goals" page in the reporting menu [by @mnapoli, @mattab]
    (Closes: #7704)
  * very tiny: visitor profile: not enough room for "g" [by @sgiehl]
    (Closes: #7609)
  * Responsive reports: 2 columns layouts now use Bootstrap CSS classes
    [by @mnapoli, @mattab] (Closes: #7504)
  * Improve device model & brand reports [by @mnapoli] (Closes: #6933)
  * Visitor Log: hide the plugin icons, and show instead the geo located
    city and region (Closes: #6176)
  * Visitor Log - view profile link and number of views overlaps [by
    @sgiehl, @mattab] (Closes: #7089)
  * UI/UX issue in narrow screens (Closes: #5878)
  * UI: improve Calendar interactions [by @diosmosis, @mattab] (Closes:
    #7728)
  * Marketplace UI tweaks: "Search 47 plugins..." in search input [by
    @mattab, @diosmosis] (Closes: #7721)
  * Show paging in the screen 'Manage websites' to easily manage
    thousands of websites [by @mattab, @tsteur] (Closes: #3838)
  * Performance: Monthly archiving should use the smaller amount of
    weeks and days inside the month [ by @tsteur] (Closes: #3611)
  * Performance: Faster access, Make dashboard etc faster when having
    thousands of sites [by @tsteur, @diosmosis] (Closes: #7641)
  * Performance: Store blob archives more efficient [ by @tsteur]
    (Closes: #7373)
  * Do not pre-process custom segments when pre-processing date ranges
    to load by default [ by @mattab] (Closes: #7611)
  * Performance: Faster archiving of aggregated reports [by @tsteur,
    @mattab] (Closes: #7577)
  * DataTable performance improvements [by @tsteur] (Closes: #7502)
  * Performance: Sort filters are sometimes applied multiple times [ by
    @tsteur] (Closes: #7388)
  * Run archiving through CLI sub-processes on OS X [by @mnapoli,
    @diosmosis] (Closes: #7681)
  * Performance: All websites dashboard - improve speed when thousands
    of websites [by @tsteur] (Closes: #6809)
  * Performance: Memory error in API Live.getLastVisitsDetails when
    filter_offset is large [by @tsteur] (Closes: #7458)
  * -force-all-websites share the list of websites across multiple
    threads of `core:archive` [by @mnapoli] (Closes: #7614)
  * Performance: Do not log SQL statements by default [by @diosmosis]
    (Closes: #7640)
  * Performance: Cache result of "isIpInRanges" for faster tracking in
    Bulk / Queue [by @tsteur, @mattab] (Closes: #7757)
  * Improve performance of BulkTracking and QueuedTracking [by @tsteur,
    @mattab] (Closes: #7688)
  * In API requests if the current user is already authenticated, do not
    authenticate the user again [by @tsteur, @mattab] (Closes: #7643)
  * Make Piwik opt-out feature work on safari and internet explorer [by
    @diosmosis] (Closes: #3135)
  * Reorganize reports in Devices and Softwares [by @sgiehl] (Closes:
    #7227)
  * Improve the "Device model" report by prefixing the model with the
    brand name [by @mnapoli, @mattab] (Closes: #7410)
  * Add a Search field to the 'Manage websites' tables (use case
    thousands of websites) [by @tsteur] (Closes: #4476)
  * JavaScript tracking: automatically consider HTML5 download
    attributes as file downloads [by @sgiehl, @mattab] (Closes: #7663)
  * Ability to use Redis to store sessions (Closes: #6800)
  * Provide extended core:archive logger output messages for easier
    monitoring (Closes: #6764)
  * Log which segments are currently being archived [by @mnapoli]
    (Closes: #7536)
  * Better logging in archiver and Task scheduler [by @diosmosis,
    @mnapoli] (Closes: #7602)
  * Piwik.js Exclude extensions as downloads via new function:
    `removeDownloadExtensions` [by @sgiehl, @mattab] (Closes: #7444)
  * Include certificates for update over HTTPS [by @mnapoli] (Closes:
    #7580)
  * Update to device detector 3.1.1 [by @sgiehl, @diosmosis] (Closes:
    #7627)
  * Developer.piwik.org - New blog post to announce it to the community
    (Closes: #7154)
  * Extend list of known Referrer Spammers (Closes: #5099)
  * Agree on naming for data access objects Dao Vs Models in core
    platform and plugins (Closes: #7540)
  * Improve translator experience/efficiency [by @sgiehl] (Closes:
    #7567)
  * Check if plugin uses Piwik methods that are Deprecated or not API
    [by @diosmosis] (Closes: #6539)
  * Short term backlog is too full -> how to keep number of issues lower
    eg. 100 issues [by @mattab] (Closes: #6430)
  * Inclusion of Bootstrap's base and grid system [by @mnapoli, @mattab]
    (Closes: #7481)
  * Refactored the system check to allow plugins to add new diagnostics
    [by @mnapoli, @diosmosis] (Closes: #7646)
  * -replay-tracking should ignore HTTP status errors/redirects (in case
    Piwik server was unreachable) [by @diosmosis] (Closes: #68)
  * Handle tracking request timeouts and specify reasonable default (w/
    CLI parameter to override) [by @diosmosis] (Closes: #65)
  * In W3C logs, client IP can be - in some logs, but log importer fails
    to parse - for IP [by @diosmosis] (Closes: #63)
  * All fields in W3C log format can be quoted strings, but importer
    assumes all unknown fields cannot be quoted [by @diosmosis] (Closes:
    #62)
  * Add retry mechanism to import_logs.py [by @diosmosis, @mattab]
    (Closes: #60)
  * Cloudfront log values need to be urldecoded [by @diosmosis] (Closes:
    #59)
  * Handle extra whitespace in W3C extended logs, including in between
    comment lines and in Fields: line. [by @diosmosis] (Closes: #58)
  * Log importer should check success from tracking api http status code
    [by @tsteur, @diosmosis] (Closes: #57)
  * At end of 'Log Import summary', display the command to force archive
    all data [by @diosmosis] (Closes: #56)
  * Problem parsing W3C log files where cs(Cookie) field has spaces [by
    @diosmosis] (Closes: #55)
  * Special characters in website name not shown correctly, Fix double
    escaping [by @mnapoli, @diosmosis] (Closes: #7552)
  * Archiving of aggregated ecommerce metrics [by @tsteur] (Closes:
    #6986)
  * Bad encoding title in the list (Closes: #6325)
  * piwik.js: If cookies are disabled, no visitorId should be created /
    set [by @tsteur] (Closes: #7780)
  * Return a HTTP 400 response code if no tracking parameter is set [by
    @tsteur, @diosmosis] (Closes: #7668)
  * add -include-year-archives and -force-optimize-tables options to
    purge-old-archive-data command. [by @diosmosis] (Closes: #7594)
  * [RFC] allow plugins to create diagnostic tools that are available
    via CLI and the web [by @mnapoli] (Closes: #7235)
  * clicking on site selector below the currently selected site's text
    does not show the popup [by @mnapoli] (Closes: #6205)
  * Clicking on 'All Websites' top menu link should keep the same
    date/period [by @mnapoli] (Closes: #7735)
  * PHP Notice when running CronArchive in
    `loadCustomDateRangeToPreProcess` [by @mnapoli, @diosmosis] (Closes:
    #7647)
  * Default GeoLocation via language is not working. [by @diosmosis]
    (Closes: #7632)
  * No 'Access-Control-Allow-Origin' [by @mattab] (Closes: #7626)
  * Unable to log into Piwik after disabling ranges as period in UI [by
    @mnapoli] (Closes: #7615)
  * missing tmp folder in ZIP [by @mnapoli] (Closes: #7612)
  * Warning message output in some cases in core:archive [by @mnapoli]
    (Closes: #7581)
  * ArchivesToPurgeDistributedList.php(40): Notice - Array to string
    conversion [by @diosmosis, @mattab] (Closes: #7560)
  * Goal widget reloads Visits widget on dashboard [by @sgiehl, @tsteur]
    (Closes: #7495)
  * After preview of Widget live visitor profile, but not adding it to
    the dashboard, the calls keep on getting requested [by @sgiehl,
    @mnapoli] (Closes: #7404)
  * Plugin Overlay does not support squared brackets [] [by @mattab]
    (Closes: #3929)
  * Goals conversion : url encoding problem [by @mattab] (Closes: #3146)
  * Added possibility to profile any command by setting the option -
    xhprof [by @tsteur] (Closes: #7675)
  * Adding logging statements to SegmentArchivingRequestUrlProvider. [by
    @diosmosis] (Closes: #7485)
  * The menu shouldn't intercept middle mouse clicks [by @mnapoli]
    (Closes: #7466)
  * Extract INI file merging logic in Config class and move to new
    IniFileChain class. [by @diosmosis] (Closes: #7312)
  * Piwik.js added ibooks as download [by @RMastop, @mattab] (Closes:
    #7744)
  * Config::getFromLocalConfig + tests [by @ThaDafinser, @diosmosis]
    (Closes: #7639)
  * Do not allow to widgetize any API call [by @mattab] (Closes: #7638)
  * Visible subtableId in system tests [by @tsteur, @mattab] (Closes:
    #7593)
  * Auto update over HTTPS can fail [by @mnapoli] (Closes: #7576)
  * Inconsistent use of Taiwan country name [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #7479)
  * Skip to Content overlaps with top menu [by @mnapoli] (Closes: #7451)
  * Make titles black instead of brown [by @mnapoli] (Closes: #7449)
  * Explain that `misc/` folder must be writable for GeoIP geo location
    to update geoip dbs (Closes: #7421)
  * Typo: settings should be uppercase [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #7343)
  * Use the native JSON when available [by @shesek, @mattab] (Closes:
    #7231)
  * [automatic translation update] Updated 71 strings in 22 languages
    (bg, nb, nl, fi, cs, da, de, el, es, et, fa, fr, it, ja, pl, ro, ru,
    sl, sr, sv, tl, tr) [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #7628)
