 -- Aurélien Requiem <aurelien@requiem.fr>  Sat, 28 Mar 2015 20:51:18 +1100

piwik (2.11.1-1) stable; urgency=high

  * Releasing Piwik 2.11.1
  * Mysql process list is clogged with very inefficient updates on the
    archive blob tables [by @mattab] (Closes: #7195)
  * error in statistics graph, avg_time = 2 [by @diosmosis] (Closes:
    #7247)
  * Adding segment name in Scheduled email report title [by @ArnY,
    @mattab] (Closes: #7243)
  * Make widgets load faster on Piwik dashboard, and sparklines load
    faster on All Websites [by @ThaDafinser, @tsteur, @mattab] (Closes:
    #7104)
  * Move language report to location reports [by @sgiehl] (Closes:
    #7226)
  * Adding Toppreise.ch as search engine [by @sgiehl, @tsteur] (Closes:
    #7216)
  * Allow usernames with 2 letters [by @mattab] (Closes: #7121)
  * Move phpunit.xml.dist to phpunit.xml in PHPUnit bootstrap or when
    executing tests [by @tsteur] (Closes: #6635)
  * JavaScript Tracking Code: when a checkbox is clicked, make it clear
    the JS code was updated [by @mattab] (Closes: #7251)
  * Date Range Selector partially hidden in Dashboard (Closes: #7261)
  * DevicesDetection: Warning - array_key_exists() [by @sgiehl] (Closes:
    #7258)
  * The parameter 'period' isn't set in the Request, and a default value
    wasn't provided. when clicking on API link in menu [by @tsteur]
    (Closes: #7250)
  * When loading URL and not logged in, this should load the login form
    [by @tsteur] (Closes: #7193)
  * Forced French translation even with English setting [by @tsteur]
    (Closes: #7187)
  * System check not verifying permissions for LOAD DATA INFILE [by
    @mattab] (Closes: #7185)
  * Correctly process unique visitors across websites in MetaSite [by
    @mattab] (Closes: #7244)

 -- Aurélien Requiem <aurelien@requiem.fr>  Sat, 28 Mar 2015 20:46:51 +1100

piwik (2.11.0-1) stable; urgency=high

  * Releasing Piwik 2.11.0
  * Log Analytics: Monitor Bandwidth for each page, download, and
    measure overall traffic in bytes [by @tsteur, @diosmosis] (Closes:
    #5248)
  * Release a Android SDK for Piwik - Mobile App Analytics (Closes:
    #4733)
  * New icon in all reports: let me segment by visitors matching this
    row's criteria [by @tsteur] (Closes: #4633)
  * Review guides at developer.piwik.org for official launch (Closes:
    #4456)
  * Visitor log may be displayed with many columns [by @sgiehl] (Closes:
    #6928)
  * duplicate entries in piwik_log_action leading to pages not visible
    in segments + provide means to fix duplicates [by @diosmosis]
    (Closes: #6436)
  * New User menu now similar to admin menu [by @tsteur] (Closes: #6989)
  * Add new segment Operating System Version (Closes: #7206)
  * Splitted referrers overview into "Overview" and "All Referrers" [by
    @tsteur, @mattab] (Closes: #6945)
  * Split goals and ecommerce in two menus, and Manage Goals via User
    menu [by @tsteur, @mattab] (Closes: #6944)
  * When User ID is used, set the first party cookie UUID to this User
    ID [by @jantlwoomy, @mattab] (Closes: #7167)
  * Add option to map API tracking parameter to custom variable in log
    importer script. [by @diosmosis, @mattab] (Closes: #7151)
  * Provide a way to specify an alternate whois provider - SEO plugin
    [by @mnapoli] (Closes: #7107)
  * For new installs, do not use the Anonymized IP addresses when
    enriching visits [by @mattab] (Closes: #7229)
  * when main Menu is focused, display submenu [by @TheCrowsJoker,
    @mattab] (Closes: #7026)
  * Make email reports more beautiful [by @mattab, @munro98] (Closes:
    #6988)
  * Tweaks to improve accessibility (section around graph, better
    tooltip, set language in html) [by @itscutekk, @mattab] (Closes:
    #7024)
  * Improved accessibility by putting offscreen text in the widget title
    [by @munro98, @mattab] (Closes: #7022)
  * Added h3 tags to widget headers (accessibility) [by @TheCrowsJoker,
    @mattab] (Closes: #7015)
  * Changed colours for better accessibility for people with sight
    difficulties [by @flodrwho] (Closes: #7011)
  * Improved accessibility with off-screen text added on the menu [by
    @munro98, @mattab] (Closes: #7038)
  * Piwik Installation now fits with the current piwik style [by
    @TheCrowsJoker, @mattab] (Closes: #7037)
  * See the focus of menu items when tabbing through the page
    (accessibility) [by @TheCrowsJoker, @mattab] (Closes: #7035)
  * Add "Skip to content" feature when user presses tab key
    (accessibility) [by @flodrwho, @mattab] (Closes: #7025)
  * Improve Login Screen Layout - input width. [by @patagonic, @mnapoli]
    (Closes: #7102)
  * When development mode is enabled, add a new language that shows raw
    translation id [by @mnapoli] (Closes: #7094)
  * As a user I want to configure purging of processed custom ranges [by
    @mgazdzik] (Closes: #7079)
  * Improve Login Screen Layout [by @patagonic, @tsteur] (Closes: #7074)
  * Changes for usage of DeviceDetector 3.0 [by @sgiehl, @tsteur]
    (Closes: #7068)
  * Refactored Twig templates using a single base layout [by @mnapoli,
    @tsteur] (Closes: #7040)
  * Segment dropdown enhancements [by @Irrational86, @mattab] (Closes:
    #6958)
  * New Piwik Ini component [by @mnapoli, @mattab] (Closes: #6939)
  * Add Administrator link to top menu [by @tsteur] (Closes: #6937)
  * Move "Anonymous user settings" into a separate page and menu item
    [by @tsteur] (Closes: #6935)
  * Rename plugin management commands [by @mnapoli] (Closes: #6915)
  * include server time (as timestamp) in visitor actions (visitor live
    API) [by @FelixSchwarz, @mattab] (Closes: #6814)
  * Add a search field in Visitor settings Browsers [by @sgiehl]
    (Closes: #6490)
  * Force new visit after midnight [by @tsteur] (Closes: #6217)
  * Improve performance by caching all translations in a flat array
    (Closes: #6060)
  * Introduce Dependency Injection [by @sabl0r] (Closes: #4917)
  * add a plugin description to all core plugins [by @mattab] (Closes:
    #7184)
  * The SEO widget should be displayed even when a http service calls
    fail [by @mattab, @mnapoli] (Closes: #7153)
  * Allow Plugins to register parameters to exclude from the tracking
    URL [by @peterbo, @mattab] (Closes: #7146)
  * add Asian search engines [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #7111)
  * New label for issues: 'c: New plugin' (Closes: #7109)
  * Update FAQ 'how do I enable logging (and / or SQL profiling) in
    Piwik?' (Closes: #7099)
  * added possibibility to add more metrics to actions plugin [by
    @tsteur] (Closes: #7041)
  * Moved language reports to their own new plugin UserLanguage [by
    @sgiehl] (Closes: #7021)
  * import_logs.py and IIS/w3c date format [by @diosmosis, @flodrwho]
    (Closes: #6968)
  * Move UI tests into the Piwik repository, the screenshot testing lib
    into another repository [by @tsteur] (Closes: #6947)
  * Make Travis CI build status render faster by logging less output
    during builds [by @mattab] (Closes: #6942)
  * Allow plugins to test against minimum required Piwik version in
    travis build. [by @diosmosis] (Closes: #6940)
  * Document .travis.yml system's available environment variables
    (Closes: #6938)
  * Activate all CronArchive system tests [by @tsteur, @mattab] (Closes:
    #6753)
  * Scheduled reports: do not show "Users" metric when value is zero [by
    @tsteur] (Closes: #6705)
  * Ixquick not listed as search engine [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #6604)
  * Automatically refresh every week the last CI build for each of our
    repository (Closes: #6542)
  * No options for goal management on the Goal page [by @tsteur]
    (Closes: #6022)
  * Deprecate UserSettings plugin -> use DeviceDetection instead! [by
    @fhemberger, @sabl0r, @sgiehl, @mattab] (Closes: #3962)
  * piwik.js double encodes the url and referrer when they are detected
    automatically [by @tsteur] (Closes: #7220)
  * Segmentation for url-encoded page urls does not work [by @tsteur]
    (Closes: #7218)
  * Site Searches metric should include duplicate site searches requests
    [by @mattab] (Closes: #7189)
  * include_aggregate_rows export issue [by @mnapoli] (Closes: #7168)
  * Email reports not working when email SMTP server host contains a
    space [by @mattab] (Closes: #7157)
  * Date Picker: Year is not fully visible in Chrome [by @tsteur]
    (Closes: #7129)
  * Cannot upload BIG Bustom Logo [by @tsteur] (Closes: #7108)
  * whois.com rate limit [by @tsteur] (Closes: #7103)
  * Bad transport method used in certain restricted environments. [by
    @tsteur] (Closes: #7083)
  * Content type application/json breaks JSONP [by @tsteur] (Closes:
    #7075)
  * Problem with password recovery functionality when Piwik has no sites
    defined [by @tsteur] (Closes: #7073)
  * email reports: cannot edit anymore if a address-list contains empty
    line [by @tsteur] (Closes: #7069)
  * Some Admin/User menu items cannot be clicked when item is active [by
    @tsteur] (Closes: #7064)
  * Bug on ranges using "last" and "previous" [by @mnapoli] (Closes:
    #7057)
  * E-commerce bug: orders from registered users creates a new visit [by
    @tsteur] (Closes: #7056)
  * Issue with setUserId - setting to null creates error in Url building
    when tracking [by @tsteur] (Closes: #7043)
  * Login broken if accessing through "untrusted host" [by @mnapoli]
    (Closes: #7036)
  * Referrers Overview, distinct metrics sparklines are always set to
    one [by @diosmosis] (Closes: #7034)
  * Slow report website and dashboard in Piwik 2.10.0 [by @tsteur]
    (Closes: #7031)
  * Browser Widget Title not Found [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #7019)
  * Infinite loop when using the DatabaseHandler logger with DEBUG level
    [by @mnapoli] (Closes: #7017)
  * When the BulkTracking plugin is disabled, bulk imports succeed, but
    no data is imported [by @diosmosis] (Closes: #6982)
  * Array to string conversion in
    /var/www/piwik/libs/Zend/Session/Exception.php on line 58 [by
    @mnapoli, @flodrwho] (Closes: #6980)
  * Key "plugins" for array with keys does not exist in
    "@Live/getLastVisitsStart.twig" at line 12 [by @sgiehl] (Closes:
    #6979)
  * Empty output for archiving using the web cron [by @mnapoli] (Closes:
    #6978)
  * Date to load by default does not always work (regression) [by
    @tsteur] (Closes: #6960)
  * Segmentation by User ID (Closes: #6959)
  * All Websites Dashboard: Add new website link is broken [by @tsteur]
    (Closes: #6950)
  * Clicking on Evolution graph leads to "The parameter 'idGoal' isn't
    set in the Request," [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #6949)
  * concurrency problem w/ plugin activation [by @diosmosis, @mnapoli]
    (Closes: #6927)
  * Error message: array combine: Both parameters should have at least 1
    element [by @mnapoli] (Closes: #6926)
  * SEO Rankings Widget - Bad display format for Domain age [by @sgiehl]
    (Closes: #6925)
  * Warning - array_merge(): Argument #2 is not an array [by @mnapoli]
    (Closes: #6924)
  * Visits Over Time Graph - Bounce rate percentage mis-calculated [by
    @diosmosis] (Closes: #6923)
  * log-analytics & import_logs.py, hosts parameter failing [by
    @diosmosis] (Closes: #6919)
  * Click tracker piwik.php?redirect=[params] was not working [by
    @mnapoli] (Closes: #6918)
  * Return HTTP Status 500 for PHP errors and fatal errors (Closes:
    #6852)
  * Error in widgets when date range before website added. [by @tsteur,
    @mattab] (Closes: #6811)
  * Error: specify a value for 'reportUniqueId' when exporting Insights
    reports [by @tsteur] (Closes: #6790)
  * Minimization of a "Visitor log" widget will collapse a display. [by
    @sgiehl] (Closes: #6700)
  * Wrong dates returned when part of the date parameter is 'today' [by
    @tsteur, @mattab] (Closes: #6194)
  * When editing a SMS report, hide the row "(optional) Display options"
    [by @mattab, @tsteur] (Closes: #5904)
  * CustomEvent in Visitor Profil: Prevent linebreak after event symbol
    [by @tsteur] (Closes: #5233)
  * Display + and - icons in Campaign report [by @diosmosis] (Closes:
    #5209)
  * Browser versions in "Visitors in realtime" | Enhancement [by
    @sgiehl] (Closes: #7197)
  * Visual: Custom Alert overlap (Closes: #7188)
  * issues updating from 2.8.3 using Composer (Closes: #7179)
  * Some performance improvements for the all websites dashboard [by
    @tsteur, @mattab] (Closes: #7162)
  * added extensions svgz and otf to the STATIC_EXTENSIONS set [by
    @ledahulevogyre, @mattab] (Closes: #7141)
  * Move UI specs into Piwik repository and run UI tests in Piwik repo
    [by @tsteur] (Closes: #7127)
  * Removed PiwikRegistry and replaced its usage with the container [by
    @mnapoli, @mattab] (Closes: #7124)
  * Various performance improvements, especially for Range period and
    installations with many sites [by @tsteur, @mattab] (Closes: #7119)
  * Add parameter -title-category-delimiter to log importer [by @BeezyT]
    (Closes: #7045)
  * broken jquery path in geoipUpdateRows.php [by @sgiehl] (Closes:
    #7028)
  * Reuse the LESS variable for white color across all stylesheets [by
    @TheCrowsJoker, @mattab, @sgiehl] (Closes: #7002)
  * add link to changelog in email notification if update is a stable
    update [by @tsteur, @mattab] (Closes: #6999)
  * Moved scheduled tasks classes to Scheduler component [by @mnapoli,
    @mattab] (Closes: #6981)
  * Currently selected Segment should be displayed in bold (Closes:
    #6961)
  * Change the layout of the engagement page [by @tsteur, @mattab]
    (Closes: #6957)
  * .git/ files should not be part of integrity check (Closes: #6955)
  * Pre-merge Code Reviews [by @mattab] (Closes: #6916)
  * Data files: removed usage of $GLOBALS and manual inclusions [by
    @mnapoli, @mattab] (Closes: #6912)
  * Faster bootstrap for PHPUnit tests [by @mnapoli, @mattab] (Closes:
    #6910)
  * Refactoring translation handling into a Translation component [by
    @mnapoli, @mattab] (Closes: #6909)
  * Add a class uiTest to the html element in all uiTests. [by @tsteur]
    (Closes: #7123)
  * Monolog plugin [by @mnapoli] (Closes: #7118)
  * Plugins can provide their own config files [by @mnapoli, @mattab]
    (Closes: #7117)
  * [automatic translation update] Updated 9314 strings in 50 languages
    (cs, da, el, am, ar, be, bg, bn, bs, ca, cy, de, es, et, eu, fa, fi,
    fr, gl, he, hi, hr, hu, id, is, it, ja, ka, ko, lt, lv, nb, nl, nn,
