 -- Aurélien Requiem <aurelien@requiem.fr>  Sat, 28 Mar 2015 19:30:16 +1100

piwik (2.10.0-2) stable; urgency=high

  * install correctly /var/log/piwik folder
  * update /var/log/piwik permissions at the end of the installation

 -- Aurélien Requiem <aurelien@requiem.fr>  Sat, 17 Jan 2015 11:30:00 +1100

piwik (2.10.0-1) stable; urgency=high

  * Releasing Piwik 2.10.0
  * Cloudfront log importing support and W3CExtendedFormat refactor [by
    @diosmosis] (Closes: #6851)
  * IIS advanced log importing, netscaler log importing and cs-username
    handling [by @diosmosis] (Closes: #6825)
  * Support for importing AWS CloudFront log files [by @biroca] (Closes:
    #6554)
  * Query parameters imported incorrectly from IIS 8.5 logs [by @mattab]
    (Closes: #4936)
  * Log Analytics: add support for Netscaler w3c logs [by @diosmosis]
    (Closes: #4707)
  * IIS Advanced Logging Module log files support for Log Analytics [by
    @diosmosis] (Closes: #6795)
  * Support Page Speed tracking in IIS 8 log files (generation time) [by
    @diosmosis] (Closes: #6388)
  * Track the username (cs-username) as User ID in IIS and W3C extended
    logs [by @diosmosis] (Closes: #5980)
  * Importing w3c extended logs [by @diosmosis] (Closes: #5418)
  * PHP caching library based on Doctrine cache: new open source PHP
    project [by @tsteur] (Closes: #6866)
  * added support for different caching backends such as redis [by
    @tsteur] (Closes: #6861)
  * during core:archive console command, preprocess any custom date
    ranges that were selected in any User's Preferences [by @mattab]
    (Closes: #6856)
  * create new visit on different campaign info or different referrer
    website [by @diosmosis] (Closes: #6847)
  * When a campaign changes, creates a new "visit" by default [by
    @diosmosis] (Closes: #2624)
  * Aggregate data for multiple (groups) of websites (Closes: #2541)
  * User fingerprint hash should be different by default on separate
    websites [by @mattab] (Closes: #6824)
  * Write tracking requests into a queue and don't process them
    immediately [by @tsteur] (Closes: #6075)
  * Geo location support for IPv6 addresses [by @joostdekeijzer,
    @mattab] (Closes: #6690)
  * Live API can timeout on very large Piwik servers [by @mattab]
    (Closes: #6786)
  * Make Piwik compatible with sql_mode = STRICT_TRANS_TABLES (MySQL 5.6
    default and best practise) [by @diosmosis] (Closes: #5178)
  * Pre-process custom date ranges when users have selected them as
    their default date range [by @mattab] (Closes: #6672)
  * in multiple frontends setup, the cache file is not up to date on all
    frontends [by @tsteur] (Closes: #6637)
  * Do not request live information in case tab is not active [by
    @tsteur] (Closes: #6625)
  * Processed metrics metadata [by @mattab, @diosmosis] (Closes: #6589)
  * Remove duplicate reports from UserSettings plugin [by @sgiehl,
    @mattab] (Closes: #6565)
  * How to handle dependency injection? [by @mnapoli] (Closes: #6548)
  * live widget could benefit from sleep mode / shared hosting scenario
    [by @tsteur] (Closes: #6545)
  * New referrer spammer: 7makemoneyonline.com [by @mattab] (Closes:
    #6872)
  * New Referrer Spammer: buttons-for-website.com [by @mattab] (Closes:
    #6858)
  * Moved resolution reports to a new plugin [by @sgiehl] (Closes:
    #6827)
  * Module and action forwarding to prevent BC break does not work for
    Image Graphs [by @mattab] (Closes: #6865)
  * Error while trying to invalidate reports with raw data removal
    enabled [by @mattab] (Closes: #6859)
  * Plugin for Piwik that modifies the 'API.get' output to also list the
    website name and main website URL. (Closes: #6828)
  * Can't add site, The method 'isPluginActivated' does not exist or is
    not available in the module 'PiwikPluginsCoreAdminHomeAPI'. [by
    @mattab] (Closes: #6849)
  * Notice: ob_flush() [ref.outcontrol]: failed to flush buffer. No
    buffer to flush [by @mattab] (Closes: #6845)
  * Separated error and exception handling from logging [by @mnapoli]
    (Closes: #6842)
  * PHP Tracker client does not persist the time of the last ecommerce
    order [by @mattab] (Closes: #6835)
  * API error for web cron archive.php with: f"ur n"ahere
    Informationen): last-3776 [by @mattab] (Closes: #6830)
  * Fail when the codebase version is older than the Piwik database
    schema version [by @mattab] (Closes: #6829)
  * web cron (misc/cron/archive.php?token_auth=xyz) sometimes does not
    load [by @mattab] (Closes: #6823)
  * Live API SQL is refactored into Model, LogQueryBuilder [by @mattab]
    (Closes: #6817)
  * Multisites - confusing behaviour [by @tsteur] (Closes: #6807)
  * Tracker refactoring and added queued tracking plugin [by @tsteur]
    (Closes: #6802)
  * Notice: Undefined property: stdClass::$module in
    plugins/Dashboard/API.php on line 137 [by @mattab] (Closes: #6798)
  * New plugin to let a Super User create a custom, parameterised page
    in Piwik (Closes: #6796)
  * Provide better information regarding memory usage by each plugin [by
    @czolnowski, @mattab] (Closes: #6794)
  * json_encode(): Invalid UTF-8 sequence in argument [by @mattab]
    (Closes: #6792)
  * bug in ecommerce item reports + row evolution: abandonedCarts
    parameter which is required for abandoned carts report does not get
    sent to row evoluton API [by @diosmosis] (Closes: #6789)
  * Move the `proxy-hide-piwik-url` project into a separate repository
    [by @mnapoli] (Closes: #6788)
  * Provide better debug possibility using the Symfony VarDumper library
    [by @tsteur] (Closes: #6890)
  * Fix views and events that have the same timestamp get disordered [by
    @tsteur, @mattab] (Closes: #6889)
  * Create new DevicePlugins and move there the browser plugin reports
    [by @sgiehl, @mattab] (Closes: #6887)
  * Adds Hungarian translation [by @sagikazarmark] (Closes: #6886)
  * Cannot install, redirected to
    http://localhost/dev/piwik/&trackerStatus=0 [by @kylekatarnls,
    @mattab] (Closes: #6884)
  * Move PiwikTracker.php to own repository [by @tsteur] (Closes: #6870)
  * Environment and configs (Closes: #6843)
  * Show Exit Page > Exit Page Titles > Exit Page, then a error occurs.
    [by @mnapoli] (Closes: #6837)
  * Refactored the logger to use PSR-3 and Monolog (#6622) [by @mnapoli,
    @mattab] (Closes: #6813)
  * Content tracking - replay from logs (Closes: #6630)
  * Exclude all requests from all existing Google bot IP ranges [by
    @mattab] (Closes: #6503)
  * Create a SECURITY.md file to explain responsible disclosure
    procedure [by @mattab] (Closes: #6779)
  * Updater dry-run: do not show the SQL query to update core_version or
    $plugin_version [by @mattab] (Closes: #6760)
  * Ecommerce reports, row evolution issues [by @diosmosis] (Closes:
    #6756)
  * Removed screentype report [by @sgiehl, @mattab] (Closes: #6752)
  * Ecommerce log: also display non-ecommerce actions in Ecommerce log
    [by @mattab] (Closes: #6742)
  * In plugin settings it should be more clear which field caused an
    error [by @tsteur] (Closes: #6740)
  * automatically cache settings in tracker cache if used in tracker
    mode [by @tsteur] (Closes: #6733)
  * When a site ID was invalidated via API
    CoreAdminHome.invalidateArchivedReports, it should be reprocessed
    even when period archiving fails at first [by @mattab] (Closes:
    #6730)
  * In tracker mode plugin system settings should be automatically
    cached [by @tsteur] (Closes: #6728)
  * error message in form are html encoded [by @mattab] (Closes: #6722)
  * Do not use default value in case value is an integer or a float and
    a string is requested [by @tsteur] (Closes: #6720)
  * For maxthon browsers (Chinese Internet Explorer) then ignore
    DoNotTrack header as it is always enabled [by @mattab] (Closes:
    #6719)
  * Ecommerce Log shows error when there are abandoned carts and no
    conversion yet [by @mattab] (Closes: #6713)
  * Proxy script fails after piwik.php returns 204 response [by
    @mnapoli] (Closes: #6712)
  * Time bugfix [by @Uby501, @mattab] (Closes: #6689)
  * Fix for IE9 in compatibility mode [by @Fensterbank, @mnapoli]
    (Closes: #6687)
  * Moved the `tmp/` path into the config (was hardcoded everywhere) [by
    @mnapoli, @mattab] (Closes: #6658)
  * URLs without scheme eg. //example.com/home should be valid URLs in
    Piwik [by @av2k, @mattab, @piwik-auto-commit-bot] (Closes: #6652)
  * Red flag running Core unit tests, either on Jessie and Precise [by
    @mattab] (Closes: #6651)
  * Import INI config in DI config [by @mnapoli] (Closes: #6648)
  * strnatcasecmp() expects parameter 1 to be string, array given in
    /Piwik/core/DataTable/Filter/Sort.php on line 142 [by @mattab]
    (Closes: #6562)
  * Add badges to plugins repositories [by @mnapoli] (Closes: #6560)
  * Make sure core plugins are always loaded in same order [by @mattab]
    (Closes: #6529)
  * do not call exit/die in core/Tracker.php (Closes: #6489)
  * Add system check to enforce always_populate_raw_post_data is -1 on
    PHP 5.6 [by @mattab] (Closes: #6468)
  * Visitor log: overlapping provider name (Closes: #6301)
  * Processed metrics calculation refactor and removal of as much queued
    filter use as possible (Closes: #6261)
  * core:archive errors: shell_exec(): Unable to execute 'which 'ps' 2>
    /dev/null [by @mattab] (Closes: #6222)
  * Overriding Compatibility View in IE9 [by @Fensterbank] (Closes:
    #6163)
  * Make 'Time on page' column displayed in format MM:SS instead of '1
    min 46s' (Closes: #6104)
  * Introduce mechanism to hide API modules and/or actions from the API
    listing page (Closes: #6042)
  * No Multi Row Evolution graph data for "Android Browser" row (Closes:
    #5888)
  * Error message in server log: plugins/.htaccess: AddHandler not
    allowed here [by @mattab] (Closes: #5398)
  * Visitor Log - Modal doesn't always close [by @mattab] (Closes:
    #5304)
  * Visitor Log: symbol for abandoned cart is missing if ... [by
    @mattab] (Closes: #5241)
  * All websites dashboard: sparklines rendered 'flat' when sorting by
    website name (Closes: #5129)
  * Warn in System check that Piwik is not compatible with Apache
    modspeed and ngx_pagespeed [by @mattab] (Closes: #5081)
  * Web site selector dialog box too narrow ... [by @mattab] (Closes:
    #4512)
  * Visitor log: IPv6 Address, long Provider overlaps other layout
    elements [by @mattab] (Closes: #4391)
  * API message: This report has been reprocessed since your last click.
    [by @mattab] (Closes: #3414)
  * Obscure or prevent referer for outgoing links in piwik via
    rel=noreferrer (works in Firefox) [by @mattab] (Closes: #3147)
  * Faster bootstrap for PHPUnit tests [by @mnapoli, @mattab] (Closes:
    #6910)
  * Trivial fixes in tests README [by @FelixSchwarz, @mnapoli] (Closes:
    #6903)
  * Image graphs: show days within selected range [by @BeezyT] (Closes:
    #6895)
  * Simplified bootstrap files [by @mnapoli, @mattab] (Closes: #6891)
  * Use Mysql 5.6 on Continuous Integration [by @diosmosis] (Closes:
    #6882)
  * When DeviceDetection plugin is disabled, 'Settings' page should
    render without error [by @diosmosis] (Closes: #6876)
  * Cache file can be created with incorrect content [by @tsteur]
    (Closes: #6873)
  * when importing visits on a day different from the visit's day,
    invalidate the archived reports [by @tsteur] (Closes: #6850)
  * Row Evolution Metrics Bug [by @diosmosis] (Closes: #6751)
  * Move towards DI for the configuration system (Closes: #6656)
  * Automatically refresh every week the last CI build for each of our
    repository (Closes: #6542)
  * Bulk Request: Views and Events that have the same timestamp get
    disordered [by @tsteur] (Closes: #5808)
  * All Websites dashboard page title [by @mnapoli] (Closes: #4982)
  * [automatic translation update] Updated 424 strings in 47 languages
    (gl, cs, da, de, el, it, ar, be, bg, ca, es, et, eu, fa, fi, fr, he,
    hi, hu, id, is, ja, ka, ko, lt, lv, nb, nl, nn, pl, pt, ro, ru, sk,
    sl, sq, sr, sv, ta, th, tl, uk, vi, am, hr, te, tr) [by @sgiehl]
    (Closes: #6803)
  * [automatic translation update] Updated 31 strings in 5 languages
    (ar, da, de, el, es) [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #6914)

 -- Aurélien Requiem <aurelien@requiem.fr>  Wed, 14 Jan 2015 20:14:08 +1100

piwik (2.9.1-1) stable; urgency=high

  * Releasing Piwik 2.9.1
  * New Language for Piwik: Tagalog (Closes: #6682)
  * Code signing for Piwik releases, and explain to users how to verify
    PGP signatures (Closes: #1757)
  * Scheduled reports: All websites report should display all websites
    not just top 100 [by @mattab] (Closes: #6694)
  * Marketplace menu link should link to Marketplace directly [by
    @mattab] (Closes: #6692)
  * Fix installation when privacy form submitted [by @mnapoli, @mattab]
    (Closes: #6684)
  * Installation: add new screenshot test for the final step form submit
    [by @diosmosis] (Closes: #6685)
  * Tracker throws 500 errors when idsite is invalid causing false
    alerts [by @tsteur] (Closes: #6661)
  * Return HTTP 204 instead of GIF for JavaScript tracking. [by @tsteur]
    (Closes: #6659)
  * Humongous file in /tmp/climulti [by @tsteur] (Closes: #6617)
  * Notice: Undefined offset: 2 in piwik/core/DataArray.php on line 102
    [by @mattab] (Closes: #6599)
  * Fatal error on installation: Call to private method [by @mattab]
    (Closes: #6680)
  * Performance enhancement: Return HTTP 204 instead of GIF for
    JavaScript tracking [by @tsteur] (Closes: #6577)
  * Deprecate Google2Piwik (Closes: #6096)
  * Support Markdown in the Marketplace for plugin descriptions [by
    @tsteur] (Closes: #6675)
  * Detect pk_cpn as an alias to pk_campaign and utm_campaign [by
    @mattab] (Closes: #6674)
  * Throw HTTP 400 error when idsite is invalid [by @tsteur] (Closes:
    #6671)
  * Piwik 2.9.0: Missing language strings on Websites Management page
    [by @mnapoli] (Closes: #6670)
  * Upgrading Debian packaged Piwik 2.8.3->2.9 breakage.
    "config/global.php doesn't exist " (Closes: #6669)
  * CliMulti: If process or output size is unexpected large, declare it
    as finished [by @tsteur, @mattab] (Closes: #6667)
  * Piwik 2.9: untranslated string [by @tsteur, @mnapoli] (Closes:
    #6665)
  * when trust_visitors_cookies = 1 is used, replaying logs cause
    discrepencies [by @diosmosis] (Closes: #6664)
  * Console command to list activated plugins [by @mattab] (Closes:
    #6663)
  * bower install piwik [by @tsteur] (Closes: #6662)
  * Refactor out HtmlMessageException [by @tsteur] (Closes: #6587)
  * add namespaces to test files [by @diosmosis] (Closes: #5800)
  * Error in update script 2.9.0-b7 [by @mattab] (Closes: #6696)
  * show the console `git:pull` command whenever Piwik is deployed from
    git [by @mattab] (Closes: #6695)
  * OneVisitorNoKeywordSpecifiedTest fails since v2.9.0-b1 [by @sgiehl]
    (Closes: #6686)
  * [automatic translation update] Updated 35 strings in 4 languages
    (fr, tl, de, it) [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #6688)
  * [automatic translation update] Updated 2472 strings in 3 languages
    (tl, sl, fr) [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #6681)
  * [automatic translation update] Updated 179 strings in 7 languages
    (fr, nl, cs, el, da, de, it) [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #6668)

