piwik (2.8.1-1) stable; urgency=high

  * Releasing Piwik 2.8.1
  * Announce that Piwik will stop supporting PHP 5.3 soon [by @mattab]
    (Closes: #6470)
  * Content Tracking, Banner tracking: track impressions, Clicks on any
    piece of content [by @tsteur, @mattab] (Closes: #4996)
  * Allow admin users to customise the piwik.js code served by Piwik [by
    @mnapoli, @mattab] (Closes: #6372)
  * Uncaught TypeError: undefined is not a function [by @tsteur]
    (Closes: #6432)
  * Content-type set to text/plain when requesting &idSubtable [by
    @tsteur] (Closes: #6384)
  * The initSession method has not been changed [by @burakcakirel,
    @diosmosis] (Closes: #6455)
  * Warning: fread(): Length parameter must be greater than 0 in
    plugins/ScheduledReports/API.php on line 519 [by @diosmosis]
    (Closes: #6454)
  * Check if a file was actually copied when copying a file [by @tsteur,
    @mattab] (Closes: #6445)
  * Added events for Piwik update, enable/disable plugin and Plugin
    Settings update [by @mnapoli, @mattab] (Closes: #6440)
  * Console command generate:report not geting all available dimensions
    [by @tsteur] (Closes: #6481)
  * Events Pivot: reads only "from" from date range and fails. [by
    @diosmosis] (Closes: #6479)
  * PHP Fatal error: Call to undefined method
    PiwikDbAdapterMysqli::fetch() in core/Tracker/Model.php on line 353
    [by @mattab] (Closes: #6475)
  * Notice: Undefined offset: 39 core/DataArray.php on line 121 [by
    @mattab] (Closes: #6474)
  * Document how to enable Content Tracking by default using
    CustomTrackerJs (Closes: #6466)
  * redirect /index.php/.whatever?... URLs to /index.php?... to avoid
    Content-Type browser bugs [by @mnapoli] (Closes: #6156)
  * xss affecting IE6, IE7 and IE8 (Closes: #6053)
  * Pages Search Results: Error message + Graph with no Data [by
    @tsteur] (Closes: #6015)
  * Php 5.6 "Automatically populating $HTTP_RAW_POST_DATA is deprecated"
    [by @mattab, @mnapoli] (Closes: #6465)
  * CI icons: Use svg instead of png to get better image quality [by
    @PeterDaveHello, @mattab] (Closes: #6461)
  * Removed tests for PHP 5.4 and 5.5. We only test for 5.3.3 and 5.6.
    [by @mnapoli] (Closes: #6459)
  * Issues with Zend Mode message [by @tsteur, @diosmosis] (Closes:
    #6452)
  * Extracted `Piwik::getJavascriptCode()` into a separate, non static
    class [by @mnapoli] (Closes: #6446)
  * Reduce number of jobs in the Travis CI piwik/piwik build [by
    @tsteur] (Closes: #6413)
  * Add missing search engine hosts [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #6281)
  * Visitors in Real-time ecommerce order tooltip formatting [by
    @tsteur] (Closes: #6123)
  * Keep composer.json and composer.lock synchronised at all times [by
    @mnapoli, @mattab] (Closes: #6058)
  * [automatic translation update] Updated 209 strings in 3 languages
    (ja, tr, cs) [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #6482)

 -- Aurélien Requiem <aurelien@requiem.fr>  Wed, 22 Oct 2014 08:23:35 +1100

piwik (2.8.0-1) stable; urgency=high

  * Releasing Piwik 2.8.0
  * Piwik support for PHP 5.6 (Closes: #5062)
  * Display + and - icons in Campaign report (Closes: #5209)
  * Email Reports being sent out twice [by @mnapoli, @mattab] (Closes:
    #5300)
  * Piwik users do not need cookie consent in France: make Piwik privacy
    enabled.
  * Error in Archivejob: Adding a subtable to the row, but it already
    has a subtable associated [by @mattab] (Closes: #4528)
  * Admin UI: mitigate the display of token_auth on screen [by @mnapoli,
    @mattab] (Closes: #4616)
  * All links in admin pages should be underlined [by @mnapoli] (Closes:
    #6138)
  * Generate Code Coverage of Piwik test suite [by @sgiehl] (Closes:
    #4224)
  * Code Coverage for Piwik Plugins using coveralls.io (Closes: #6195)
  * Rename our test suites so the names make sense [by @tsteur,
    @mnapoli] (Closes: #5940)
  * Docs should not state Piwik requires GRANT OPTION (Closes: #335)
  * Improvements to Tracking API for easier Mobile Apps Tracking
    (Closes: #4994)
  * Make it clear how to force sending scheduled tasks for debugging [by
    @mnapoli, @mattab] (Closes: #6085)
  * IP in Providers widget is linking to FAQ page. [by @mattab] (Closes:
    #6101)
  * Tracker API: cdt parameter should not require token_auth when
    setting a recent datetime [by @mattab] (Closes: #6110)
  * Goal matching should match the raw URL including all query
    parameters [by @mattab] (Closes: #6191)
  * Remove dependency from Actions plugin to Contents (and maybe Events)
    [by @tsteur] (Closes: #6204)
  * 'Others' row in reports: explain to user how to see it less often
    [by @mnapoli, @mattab] (Closes: #6215)
  * archive.php compatibility with hhvm, next round [by @mattab]
    (Closes: #6224)
  * Make visitorId be equal by default for all Piwik.Trackers [by
    @a4tunado, @mattab] (Closes: #6257)
  * Fixed .gitignore [by @mnapoli, @halfdan] (Closes: #6264)
  * Unknown providers are now shown as "Unknown" instead of "IP" [by
    @mnapoli, @mattab] (Closes: #6400)
  * Added a "learn more" link on "Others" row in reports [by @mnapoli,
    @mattab] (Closes: #6401)
  * Update some AngularJS modules to match a new style guide [by
    @tsteur] (Closes: #5983)
  * AngularJS: Use controllerAs syntax [by @tsteur] (Closes: #6284)
  * New AngularJS directive for AJAX forms [by @diosmosis] (Closes:
    #6399)
  * AngularJS notifications: new directive [by @diosmosis] (Closes:
    #6366)
  * Provide a command to generate AngularJS components [by @tsteur]
    (Closes: #6285)
  * New component/decompress: extracted PiwikUnzip into a separate
    package (Closes: #6367)
  * Visitors having empty visits when using content tracking [by
    @tsteur, @mattab] (Closes: #6296)
  * Fix detection of a known visitor when there are multiple requests at
    same second for same visitor [by @tsteur] (Closes: #6298)
  * Proxy piwik.php script does not send http headers [by @KoffeinKaio,
    @mattab] (Closes: #6300)
  * Ignore any opcache_invalidate errors [by @stackcoder, @mattab]
    (Closes: #6303)
  * Remove "Website" word from scheduled email reports [by @mattab]
    (Closes: #6309)
  * aclocal and autoconf calls are necessary to build the xhprof php
    extension [by @sabl0r, @mattab] (Closes: #6311)
  * When a User Id is set, try to attach User ID to existing visit
    before user logged in [by @mattab] (Closes: #6313)
  * Warning: shell_exec() [function.shell-exec]: Unable to execute 'stat
    -f -c "%T" /proc 2>/dev/null' [by @mattab] (Closes: #6314)
  * Remove CacheFile cache from APC on write [by @brownoxford, @mattab]
    (Closes: #6315)
  * Refactor Auth logic to login's Auth class and new PasswordResetter
    class from login controller (Closes: #6318)
  * Move some menu logic from Twig to plugin's Menu [by @mgazdzik,
    @mattab] (Closes: #6322)
  * Mysql return rows count found in an UPDATE rather than rows modified
    [by @mattab] (Closes: #6323)
  * Optimize DatabaseTestCase so travis build will be faster [by
    @diosmosis] (Closes: #6331)
  * When pulling Piwik sourcode via Git we get: git fatal failed to stat
    File name too long (Closes: #6337)
  * Deprecate Piwik::setUserHasSuperUserAccess() and switch to using
    Access::doAsSuperUser() [by @diosmosis, @mattab] (Closes: #6342)
  * Improve readability of code [by @tsteur] (Closes: #6343)
  * When real time segments are disabled, still allow 'view' users to
    create pre-processed [by @mattab] (Closes: #6373)
  * The parameter 'period' isn't set in the Request, and a default value
    wasn't provided. [by @mattab] (Closes: #6374)
  * Only set error 500 headers when there is an internal server error
    (Database failure) [by @mattab] (Closes: #6375)
  * Let plugins further extend tracking code via Event
    'Piwik.getJavascriptCode' [by @czolnowski, @mattab] (Closes: #6380)
  * Update does not detect the newly available DB schema upgrades [by
    @mattab] (Closes: #6383)
  * Increase Piwik PHP requirement to PHP 5.3.3 [by @mattab] (Closes:
    #6390)
  * Show only the first characters of tokens in the admin [by @mnapoli,
    @mattab] (Closes: #6394)
  * Refactoring in ScheduledReports to remove useless indentation [by
    @mnapoli, @mattab] (Closes: #6396)
  * Tracker API: when 'cdt' tracker parameter is set in the recent past
    (last 4 hours) then do not require token_auth [by @mattab] (Closes:
    #6407)
  * Rename our test suites so the names make sense #5940 [by @tsteur]
    (Closes: #6411)
  * Moved test files into a subfolder framework [by @tsteur] (Closes:
    #6431)
  * [automatic translation update] Updated 278 strings in 10 languages
    (pt, cs, da, de, el, es, et, it, pl, ja) [by @sgiehl] (Closes:
    #6391)

 -- Aurélien Requiem <aurelien@requiem.fr>  Fri, 17 Oct 2014 16:13:08 +1100

piwik (2.7.0-1) stable; urgency=high

  * Releasing Piwik 2.7.0
  * User ID feature: Accurate User detection across devices [by @mattab,
    @tsteur] (Closes: #3490)
  * New metric 'nb_users' counting the number of Active Unique Users
    (the count of distinct User IDs set) [by @mattab] (Closes: #6162)
  * Cross websites reporting: Let me see the number of users who browsed
    two websites (new InterSites Piwik plugin!) (Closes: #6082)
  * Make it easier to discover and access reports footer options and
    icons [by @diosmosis] (Closes: #5976)
  * Content Tracking [by @tsteur] (Closes: #6201)
  * Show [+] icon in the reports rows when the row can be expanded [by
    @diosmosis] (Closes: #5355)
  * Event reporting: new report to view the second dimension as columns
    (Pivot by second dimension) [by @diosmosis, @mattab] (Closes: #6078)
  * Browser language reporting: Let me see the different language codes
    [by @vox3r, @mattab] (Closes: #6097)
  * Allow opt-out to be shown within an iframe on other domains [by
    @Guite, @mattab] (Closes: #6132)
  * As a Piwik admin, I want to disable ability for users to create
    segments for "All Websites" [by @diosmosis] (Closes: #5923)
  * invalidateArchivedReports should not delete the data but invalidate
    it until re-processed [by @mattab] (Closes: #5932)
  * New $period parameter to the API call
    CoreAdminHome.invalidateArchivedReports [by @mattab] (Closes: #5933)
  * Log Analytics: new parameter -download-extensions to override list
    of files tracked as downloads [by @postalservice14, @mattab]
    (Closes: #6231)
  * Wrong default date when adding annotations [by @tsteur] (Closes:
    #5972)
  * Setup Coveralls for Piwik Code coverage report [by @sgiehl] (Closes:
    #4302)
  * Display a warning in admin to super users in case PHP 5.3 is used
    [by @tsteur, @mattab] (Closes: #6275)
  * Changed JavaScript Tracking Code generation to use "//" [by
    @Irrational86, @mattab] (Closes: #344)
  * Add 'Disable all cookies' checkbox in the JavaScript Tracking code
    generator [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #6174)
  * Add an icon next to "Segments" box [by @diosmosis] (Closes: #6034)
  * display permanent notification to Super Users in admin screen for
    PHP 5.3 warning about EOL [by @tsteur, @mattab] (Closes: #6056)
  * Adding new PivotByDimension DataTable filter that can pivot a report
    by (almost) any dimension. [by @diosmosis, @mattab] (Closes: #6243)
  * Archiver: allow to process unique visitors across multiple websites
    [by @diosmosis] (Closes: #6079)
  * Tracker API: cid parameter no longer requires token_auth [by
    @mattab] (Closes: #6109)
  * Allow invalidated archive data to be used until they are re-
    processed [by @mkurzeja, @mattab] (Closes: #6116)
  * Log analytics : import_logs.py doesn't work any more (Closes: #6120)
  * insight select options: all option not working after you switch to
    another option [by @tsteur] (Closes: #6124)
  * problem with opt-out-iframe: when calling forwarded to log-in-screen
    with "idSite= is missing" [by @diosmosis] (Closes: #6128)
  * Log Analytics Update README add regex example for syslog format [by
    @ahattouti-canaltp, @halfdan] (Closes: #6131)
  * Upgrade from 2.5.0 to 2.6.1. breaks [by @diosmosis] (Closes: #6134)
  * PHP Arrays not Serialized by Default [by @claytondaley,
    @MichielDeMey, @mattab] (Closes: #6137)
  * Make it easier to define URLs for Menu and remove an unnessary
    parameter [by @tsteur] (Closes: #6140)
  * Menu Plugin API improvements [by @tsteur] (Closes: #6141)
  * Generate plugin should no longer ask whether it should also create
    an API and a controller [by @tsteur] (Closes: #6145)
  * When generating a plugin we should require at least the developer's
    Piwik version [by @tsteur] (Closes: #6149)
  * Menu: If development mode is enabled we should check whether action
    exists [by @tsteur] (Closes: #6153)
  * Php serializer was not serializing arrays by default. [by
    @claytondaley, @mattab] (Closes: #6155)
  * User ID implementation [by @mattab] (Closes: #6169)
  * Deprecate new_visit_api_requires_admin config setting [by @mattab]
    (Closes: #6175)
  * Bug: on hover of table rows incorrect jquery selector will result in
    size of value spans being same as largest label [by @diosmosis]
    (Closes: #6178)
  * Clean up arobases [by @kylekatarnls] (Closes: #6185)
  * fixes #6174 - added possibility to add 'disableCookies' option in
    trackinking code generator [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #6190)
  * Let Segments define a callback to use for suggested values in
    segment editor [by @czolnowski, @mattab] (Closes: #6192)
  * Add angularjs code to open and close dialogs. [by @diosmosis]
    (Closes: #6193)
  * Implementation of new Browser Reports by Language and Language code
    [by @vox3r, @mattab] (Closes: #6199)
  * Replace header() with Common::sendHeader() when possible [by
    @kylekatarnls, @mattab] (Closes: #6211)
  * Add option to disable menu title change after click position in top
    menu. [by @czolnowski, @mattab] (Closes: #6213)
  * Refs #6078, extract factory logic from Report::factory and move to
    ComponentFactory utility class. [by @diosmosis] (Closes: #6221)
  * #6232 getExpiresHeaderForFutureDay should be static [by
    @kylekatarnls, @mattab] (Closes: #6233)
  * Fix one unit test in PHP 5.6 allow charset complement in content-
    type [by @kylekatarnls, @mattab] (Closes: #6235)
  * use php_uname() instead of shell_exec('uname') [by @hdi-kw, @mattab]
    (Closes: #6237)
  * HTML scheduled report does not render in browser [by @mattab]
    (Closes: #6245)
  * german i18n mixed up after Update to 2.6(.1) (Closes: #6246)
  * More tests for content tracking [by @tsteur] (Closes: #6249)
  * User ID should be defined as dimension [by @tsteur] (Closes: #6273)
  * The import_logs.py script does not treat ".apk" files as downloads
    [by @andrejb, @mattab] (Closes: #6276)
  * Fix import_logs.py apk downloads (#6276). [by @andrejb, @mattab]
    (Closes: #6277)
  * Use PSR-4 for autoloader (Closes: #4074)
  * Argument 1 passed to
    PiwikAPIDataTableManipulatorReportTotalsCalculator::hasDataTableMetr
    ic() must be an instance of PiwikDataTable, instance of
    PiwikDataTableMap given [by @tsteur] (Closes: #5373)
  * Fixed typo in README [by @MichielDeMey, @halfdan] (Closes: #6136)
  * Improve detection of proc filesystem that works despite potential
    open_b... [by @snout1979, @mattab] (Closes: #5965)
  * [automatic translation update] Updated 62 strings in 1 languages
    (cs) [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #6143)
  * [automatic translation update] Updated 510 strings in 9 languages
    (pl, fr, de, it, ja, nb, tr, da, el) [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #6208)
