piwik (2.6.0-1) stable; urgency=high

  * Releasing Piwik 2.6.0
  * Reports for today will be processed every 150 seconds instead of
    previous default 10s (real time reports) (Closes: #6089)
  * When there are many goals, show them grouped in a selector [by
    @tsteur] (Closes: #5977)
  * PiwikDebugger: a new plugin to debug a Piwik instance without FTP
    access (troubleshooting toolkit). (Closes: #5982)
  * Let users define a Goal as "Goal is triggered when visitor send an
    Event" [by @tsteur] (Closes: #5989)
  * Add hooks to Live plugin and let other plugins extend it [by
    @tsteur] (Closes: #6045)
  * Use an event to collect visitor information and made sure UI works
    even when minimum plugins are enabled [by @tsteur] (Closes: #6071)
  * Entering Settings doesn't work after update to 2.4.0 [by @tsteur]
    (Closes: #5414)
  * Piwik.js JS tracker: allow developer to pass a 'callback' argument
    [by @Sija, @mattab] (Closes: #5850)
  * Split core language files into plugins where possible [by @tsteur]
    (Closes: #5863)
  * Fix xhprof integration, install xhprof through composer and build
    xhprof through composer. [by @diosmosis] (Closes: #6035)
  * Enables code coverage reports using coveralls.io [by @sgiehl]
    (Closes: #6036)
  * Let Piwik admins run the `core:archive` through the browser (Closes:
    #5924)
  * Error when switching 'report tables' view of DBStats plugin to pie
    chart [by @tsteur] (Closes: #5952)
  * Unexpected hijacking user after clicking on sparkline and chart [by
    @tsteur] (Closes: #5970)
  * Unclear indication of current state of Real-time widget [by @tsteur]
    (Closes: #5971)
  * Lack of "Cancel" option when editing users [by @tsteur] (Closes:
    #5973)
  * Add FAQ to explain how to configure CORS Cross-origin resource
    sharing hosts (Closes: #5993)
  * Duplicated "create new goal" text (Closes: #5990)
  * Fix XHProf implementation [by @diosmosis, @tsteur, @mattab] (Closes:
    #5995)
  * Lacking label in "Create new Goal" view [by @tsteur] (Closes: #5997)
  * Find only components and settings of activated plugins [by @tsteur]
    (Closes: #6011)
  * Make ./console core:archive work on CGI (use case 1&1
    hosting/managed server) [by @tsteur] (Closes: #6012)
  * /misc/cron/archive.php mistake web execution for command line [by
    @tsteur] (Closes: #6013)
  * "The string Goals_Ecommerce was not loaded in javascript" ...
    Massive Error message on "Websites Management" [by @tsteur] (Closes:
    #6014)
  * Switch to composer for autoloading. [by @diosmosis, @tsteur]
    (Closes: #6024)
  * On version 2.5.0 under the "Event Actions" report, the second-level
    aggregate table is now showing "Unique Visitors", it used to be
    "Total Events" [by @tsteur] (Closes: #6025)
  * Goals condition and examples do not update when creating/editing a
    goal [by @tsteur] (Closes: #6026)
  * Field 'location_browser_lang' doesn't have a default value In query
    [by @tsteur, @mattab] (Closes: #6028)
  * Object of class PiwikPluginsProxyController could not be converted
    to string in core/FrontController.php on line 173 [by @mattab]
    (Closes: #6030)
  * Theming - changing font variable does not work [by @tsteur] (Closes:
    #6038)
  * fixed composer.json to download the same set of vendors as with use
    of c... [by @mgazdzik, @mattab] (Closes: #6043)
  * Refactor piwikApi angularjs object to allow aborting individual
    requests and all requests. [by @diosmosis] (Closes: #6048)
  * 2.5.0 Upgrade - Breaks Visitor Log [by @tsteur] (Closes: #6049)
  * Bug in JSON renderer renders simple associative array as indexed
    array containing object. [by @diosmosis] (Closes: #6057)
  * Move translations from core to plugins and cache all plugin
    translations for better performance [by @tsteur] (Closes: #6059)
  * Cache list of Tracker plugins in tracker than config file [by
    @tsteur] (Closes: #6065)
  * Move JSON format bug fixes to new JSON2 format so existing clients
    will not fail. [by @diosmosis] (Closes: #6066)
  * at installation step 2, warning message: "GET request to piwik.php
    failed." [by @mattab] (Closes: #6067)
  * When a Goal is matching a pattern containing <, >, ', " goal will
    not match [by @mattab] (Closes: #6070)
  * dynamically detect tracker plugins and cache them instead of using
    config [by @tsteur, @mattab] (Closes: #6072)
  * Removing pre PHP 5.3 checks (SPL ArrayObject) [by @ThaDafinser,
    @mattab] (Closes: #6084)
  * 2.6b1: API returned an error: Date format.. [by @diosmosis] (Closes:
    #6086)
  * After updating to 2.5.0 the plugin page don't work [by @diosmosis]
    (Closes: #6092)
  * Processed report does not add all metrics to columns [by @tsteur]
    (Closes: #6102)
  * xhprof removed their composer.json file, adding it to our
    composer.json file so we can still use composer to manage xhprof [by
    @diosmosis] (Closes: #6107)
  * Fix getProcessedReport does not include all metrics in columns [by
    @tsteur] (Closes: #6112)
  * Norwegian Bokmal name is written wrong [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #6114)
  * [automatic translation update] Updated 129 strings in 6 languages
    (fa, tr, ru, cs, ja, nl) [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #6117)

