piwik (2.5.0-1) stable; urgency=high

  * Releasing Piwik 2.5.0
  * [New open source project] Github issues mirror for Data ownership
    and better searchability, on issues.piwik.org (Closes: #5299)
  * Create a CHANGELOG.md file that lists all changes and improvements
    to the core platform (Closes: #5953)
  * Create a CONTRIBUTING.md file to let users know how to contribute to
    Piwik [by @tsteur] (Closes: #5381)
  * Refactor reports and dimensions [by @tsteur] (Closes: #5820)
  * When there is an error in Piwik throw a http error code 500 [by
    @mattab] (Closes: #5958)
  * Don't store custom variables in cookies (better privacy) [by
    @mattab] (Closes: #5415)
  * When upgrading Piwik, -dry-run should show all SQL queries including
    Plugins install queries (Closes: #5806)
  * Cross-origin resource sharing [by @czolnowski, @halfdan, @mattab]
    (Closes: #5912)
  * Issues with changing segment name. [by @tsteur] (Closes: #5816)
  * "report to load by default" does not change to "All Websites" [by
    @tsteur] (Closes: #5817)
  * Fix HHVM support for CLI [by @Diftraku, @tsteur] (Closes: #5818)
  * New Search engines [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #5819)
  * In piwik.js when 'disableCookies' is pushed to the _paq array, apply
    it first [by @mattab] (Closes: #5957)
  * Show footer icons in the Ecommerce reports [by @tsteur] (Closes:
    #5385)
  * Notice: Undefined index: 2011-08-18 in plugins/API/API.php on line
    493 [by @mattab] (Closes: #5168)
  * Refactor core:archive command to use symfony console $input rather
    than getParameterFromCli() method [by @diosmosis] (Closes: #5807)
  * In processed report a segment parameter is not added to ImageGraph
    URL [by @tsteur, @mattab] (Closes: #5895)
  * filter, showColumns, hideColumns should work if API returns arrays
    [by @tsteur] (Closes: #5896)
  * Created unified system for running tests in travis for Piwik Core
    and any Piwik plugin. [by @diosmosis, @mattab] (Closes: #5962)
  * Movers and Shakers not compairing correctly when using Segmentation
    [by @tsteur] (Closes: #5964)
  * make the opt-out form work even if JavaScript is disabled [by
    @craue, @tsteur] (Closes: #5849)
  * refs #5950 add possibility to sort Live.getLastVisitsDetails [by
    @tsteur] (Closes: #5981)
  * refs #5936 remove gone files during update [by @tsteur] (Closes:
    #5984)
  * MultiSites.getAll returns wrong format under circumstances [by
    @tsteur] (Closes: #5987)
  * Add 'Marketplace' link to the top menu [by @tsteur] (Closes: #5994)
  * When Ajax request ends with error (5xx or 4xx), Piwik should display
    a friendly message notification [by @tsteur] (Closes: #5406)
  * Create FAQ to help troubleshoot the error "Failed to load HTML file"
    (Closes: #5404)
  * Widget error message "The report 'nb_pageviews' was requested but it
    is not available at this stage..." [by @diosmosis] (Closes: #4392)
  * Encountered unsupported archive type 'dat.gz.'. [by @mattab]
    (Closes: #4629)
  * Add icon for browser "Mobile Safari" [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #5151)
  * PHP Warning: parse_url(http://): Unable to parse URL in
    core/UrlHelper.php on line 494 [by @fhemberger, @tsteur] (Closes:
    #5180)
  * show visit time in visitor profile [by @mattab] (Closes: #5190)
  * huge whitespace in visitor profile [by @fhemberger] (Closes: #5191)
  * Visitor engagement: too wide [by @fhemberger] (Closes: #5242)
  * Change Visitor Profile log tooltip [by @tsteur] (Closes: #5313)
  * Piwik auf IIS im shared hosting erzeugt fehlerhafte CSS-Datei [by
    @tsteur] (Closes: #5399)
  * "zlib i missing" on 64bit Ubuntu systems [by @mattab] (Closes:
    #5407)
  * Real Time Visitor Count - wrong actions counter [by @tsteur]
    (Closes: #5416)
  * code cleanup [by @craue, @mattab] (Closes: #5813)
  * Fix parameter in deprecation message in /misc/cron/archive.php [by
    @fhemberger, @mattab] (Closes: #5825)
  * Adding the new variables to "UsersManager.addUser.end" and
    "UsersManager.updateUser.end" triggers [by @burakcakirel, @mattab]
    (Closes: #5833)
  * Uninitialized string offset: 1 in /srv/piwik/core/Piwik.php on line
    158 [by @tsteur] (Closes: #5841)
  * Piwik's asynchronous command line execution module does not properly
    detect currently running processes on some systems [by @diosmosis]
    (Closes: #5842)
  * code cleanup [by @craue, @tsteur] (Closes: #5847)
  * Search engine "Yandex" is defined as a website [by @sgiehl] (Closes:
    #5851)
  * [2.4.1] VisitorMap wrong visit summary? [by @tsteur] (Closes: #5854)
  * Add name parameter to MenuTop. [by @czolnowski, @tsteur] (Closes:
    #5858)
  * Treat response with any 2xx status code as successful POST track
    request [by @sslavic, @mattab] (Closes: #5859)
  * Show the image description also as title [by @ThaDafinser, @tsteur]
    (Closes: #5861)
