    #5866)
  * Unable to use new domain extensions as an email address [by @tsteur]
    (Closes: #5867)
  * remove dead code [by @craue, @tsteur] (Closes: #5871)
  * code cleanup [by @craue, @tsteur] (Closes: #5872)
  * On update, automatically delete from filesystem all Piwik files that
    are not in the latest release [by @tsteur] (Closes: #5936)
  * In the Visitor Profile, show also the time of the visit [by
    @ThaDafinser, @mattab] (Closes: #5883)
  * Integration Tests refactor (move API testing logic to separate
    classes) [by @diosmosis, @mattab] (Closes: #5884)
  * Calling MultiSites.getAll results in "Invalid parameter number" (in
    Piwik 2.5.0-b1) [by @tsteur] (Closes: #5887)
  * refs #5820 Report and dimension refactoring [by @tsteur] (Closes:
    #5821)
  * Plugin: Howto skip/adjust config filter? [by @tsteur] (Closes:
    #5890)
  * Visitors in real-time widget "Page views" metric should not counts
    other action types [by @mattab, @piwik-auto-commit-bot] (Closes:
    #5891)
  * fixed broken EventDispatcher mechanism for sorting callbacks order
    [by @mgazdzik, @halfdan] (Closes: #5893)
  * Missing word in FAQ (Closes: #5899)
  * r.search.yahoo.com tracked as external referrer [by @sgiehl]
    (Closes: #5910)
  * Display more useful message when error `Abort pclzip.lib.php :
    Missing zlib extensions` [by @mattab] (Closes: #5925)
  * Add example Dimensions and example Reports to the `ExamplePlugin`
    [by @tsteur] (Closes: #5926)
  * Delete unused column `log_conversion.referer_visit_server_date` [by
    @mattab] (Closes: #5927)
  * CORS refactoring [by @czolnowski, @mattab] (Closes: #5929)
  * Visitor profile image width to max-width [by @ThaDafinser, @mattab]
    (Closes: #5931)
  * Unit test fixes [by @mnapoli, @mattab] (Closes: #5934)
  * Run marketplace plugin tests with the defined PHP version in
    plugin.json [by @tsteur] (Closes: #5937)
  * Fixed a test to use the configured root URL [by @mnapoli, @mattab]
    (Closes: #5939)
  * When an admin removes a user's access to a website, sending
    scheduled reports may fail [by @tsteur] (Closes: #5943)
  * 5896 add showColumns/hideColumns filters to arrays [by @tsteur]
    (Closes: #5944)
  * Run tests on older version PHP 5.3.3 [by @mattab] (Closes: #5945)
  * Searching in datatable for `?param` results in error message [by
    @tsteur] (Closes: #5949)
  * Sorting Live.getLastVisitsDetails visits by a custom column [by
    @tsteur] (Closes: #5950)
  * Add search engine sputnik.ru [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #5969)
  * Notice: Undefined index: dimension in plugins/API/RowEvolution.php
    on line 334 [by @tsteur] (Closes: #5951)
  * When editing an existing goal, radio buttons are not checked [by
    @tsteur] (Closes: #5961)
  * shell_exec(): Cannot execute using backquotes in Safe Mode [by
    @mattab] (Closes: #5988)
  * Prevent ArchiveWeb test from failing [by @tsteur] (Closes: #6003)
  * [automatic translation update] Updated 90 strings in 8 languages
    (da, de, el, fr, it, ru, sv, tr) [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #5909)
  * [automatic translation update] Updated 65 strings in 2 languages
    (de, pl) [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #5857)
  * [automatic translation update] Updated 68 strings in 5 languages
    (da, de, el, sl, tr) [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #6004)
  * [automatic translation update] Updated 84 strings in 7 languages
    (el, it, ja, nb, nl, sv, tr) [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #5824)
  * [automatic translation update] Updated 131 strings in 8 languages
    (ru, fr, sv, cs, da, de, el, it) [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #5967)

 -- Aurelien Requiem <aurelien@requiem.fr>  Fri, 22 Aug 2014 13:54:41 +1000

piwik (2.4.1-1) stable; urgency=high

  * Releasing Piwik 2.4.1
  * SitesManager fully migrated to AngularJS [by @JulienMoumne, @mattab]
    (Closes: #324)
  * Row evolution data export fails when filter_limit is supplied [by
    @diosmosis] (Closes: #5397)
  * [automatic translation update] Updated 1133 strings in 9 languages
    (cs, da, el, fr, it, nb, nl, ro, tr) [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #340)
  * Update from 2.3 to 2.4 breaks db password [by @tsteur] (Closes:
    #341)
  * provide a more useful error message on exception [by @craue,
    @mattab] (Closes: #345)
  * included default value for concurent threads number [by @mgazdzik,
    @mattab] (Closes: #347)
  * remove defaults from PHPUnit configuration [by @craue] (Closes:
    #348)
  * Row Evolution shows wrong data when directory and file with
    identical names exist at same level [by @diosmosis] (Closes: #4363)
  * Change piwik URL to builds.piwik.org/piwik.zip [by @mattab] (Closes:
    #4455)
  * Migrate Piwik issues from Trac to Github issues! [by @mattab]
    (Closes: #5273)
  * Warning: syntax error, unexpected $end, expecting '}' in
    config.ini.php in libs/upgradephp/upgrade.php [by @tsteur] (Closes:
    #5349)
  * When database connection fails, display a useful page to user [by
    @diosmosis] (Closes: #5400)
  * When file uploads is disabled, display a meaningful error message
    [by @mattab] (Closes: #5403)
  * Bar graph loses correct yaxis in when report state is persisted
    (Closes: #5405)
  * Transitions on Page Titles regressed in 2.4.0 [by @diosmosis]
    (Closes: #5411)
  * SQL queries in upgrade files should always work when upgrade is
    executed several times [by @diosmosis] (Closes: #5809)
  * add XSD to PHPUnit configuration [by @craue, @mattab] (Closes: #346)
  * Decouple UI tests from fixtures by using SQL dump of OmniFixture [by
    @diosmosis] (Closes: #349)

 -- Aurelien Requiem <aurelien@requiem.fr>  Sat, 12 Jul 2014 10:51:53 +1000

piwik (2.4.0-1) stable; urgency=high

  * Releasing Piwik 2.4.0
  * Better Data Insights. Show me what's increased and decreased, movers
    and shakers (beta) (Closes: #57)
  * Remove Zeitgeist theme from Piwik and support only Morpheus (Closes:
    #5222)
  * Tracking API: major performance improvements with Transactions, when
    using Bulk Tracking (Closes: #5275)
  * Referrers overview: report labels should show more characters before
    truncation (Closes: #5394)
  * Log Analytics: several performance improvements (Closes: #5314)
  * New setting: enable Left Menu mode (Closes: #5212)
  * LibreJS compatibility for piwik.js: free/libre license notice
    (Closes: #3770)
  * Simplify / improve top menu (Closes: #5192)
  * Enable DevicesDetection plugin by default (Closes: #5329)
  * Developers: provide a simpler ScheduledTasks API (Closes: #5301)
  * Developers: new hooks in Login: 'Login.authenticate',
    'Login.authenticate.successful' (Closes: #5331)
  * Developers: new hook Live.makeNewVisitorObject for plugins to
    customise Visitor object (Closes: #5360)
  * Switching metrics in row evolution view doesn't work after changing
    report timespan (Closes: #5303)
  * New parameters for the core:archive console command for power users
    (Closes: #5396)
  * Change piwik URL to builds.piwik.org/piwik-latest.zip (Closes:
    #4455)
  * Row Evolution shows wrong data when directory and file with
    identical names exist at same level (Closes: #4363)
  * PiwikTracker PHP client: when bulk tracking, Custom variables are
    now reset after each request (Closes: #5291)
  * php console core:update -> issue using Piwik 2.3.0 (Closes: #5306)
  * Calculation All Websites dashboard wrong (Closes: #5320)
  * DataTable footer drawer does not expand when clicked (Closes: #5332)
  * When a custom date range is requested, the timezone of the requested
    website may be ignored (Closes: #5356)
  * When running piwik proxy php to hide footprint, IP address is not
    set correctly when the website being tracked is behind proxy
    (Closes: #2900)
  * When 10 widgets request the same site + date + segment at once,
    check it is archived only once (Closes: #4918)
  * make core:archive command compatibile with HHVM (Closes: #5263)
  * htaccess should help apache serve HTML files properly with:
    AddHandler text/html .html (Closes: #5266)
  * Include Meta tag IE=edge for best security practises (Closes: #5282)
  * Ensure all directories in plugins/ (Closes: #5311)
  * New system check to alert user when session.auto_start = 1 (Closes:
    #5344)
  * Limits ability of different Piwik instances to cross-match users
    (privacy) (Closes: #5366)
  * Detect requests from iTunes (Closes: #4017)
  * Support for user-agent string from AFNetworking library (iOS)
    (Closes: #5025)
  * Cron core:archive: make sure the PHP cli binary is at least 5.3.2
    (Closes: #5343)
  * Piwik should work as expected when PHP setting session.hash_function
    has non default value (Closes: #5371)
  * Make "Site Search" on "All Websites Dashboard" case-insensitive
    (Closes: #5382)
  * piwik.js: new function setCustomRequestProcessing() to let you edit
    the tracking request before it is sent (Closes: #5384)
  * Piwik.js: ability to register plugins to execute logic when a
    request is sent (Closes: #5393)
  * New config setting: set the Scheduled report emails Reply-to field
    to Email and Alias name of report creator (Closes: #5387)
  * Nightingale Media Player not detected correctly (Closes: #4870)
  * API: get PageUrl returns same results for several day (Closes:
    #4872)
  * Error when running cron:archive: Response was 'Console ToolUsage:
    [options] command.... (Closes: #5007)
  * Website dropdown no longer appears (Closes: #5213)
  * German translation incomplete in version 2.3.0 (Closes: #5240)
  * Visitor/locations: Map region selector to narrow (Closes: #5243)
  * Long Segment names break segment listing layout (Closes: #5247)
  * Error in "Database Usage" usage ... (Closes: #5253)
  * import_logs give a IOError: [Errno 29] Illegal seek when receiving
    log from pipe (Closes: #5254)
  * IIS: web.config should allow to server HTM, HTML and SVG files.
    (Closes: #5255)
  * Visitor Generator not working from console (Closes: #5256)
  * Not well testable php class method URL::redirectToUrl($url) (Closes:
    #5262)
  * 2.3.0: Visitors in Real-time widget, incorrect page title display
    (Closes: #5268)
  * invalidateArchivedReports $dates issue (Closes: #5281)
  * Remove plugins/Zeitgeist/ (Closes: #5297)
  * Incorrect domain age reported (Closes: #5322)
  * Warning: syntax error, unexpected $end, expecting '}' in
    config.ini.php in libs/upgradephp/upgrade.php (Closes: #5349)
  * Dropping outdated archives can timeout on huge Piwik instances
    (Closes: #5354)
  * Auto archiving: all websites should be archived at least once per
    day (Closes: #5358)
  * DBStats: Call to a member function getColumn() on a non-object in
    core/DataTable/Filter/ColumnCallbackAddColumnQuotient (Closes:
    #5370)
  * getVisitorProfilePopup: error on empty data (Closes: #5383)
  * FatalError - subDay() in API.php (Closes: #5388)
  * Support user agents of PIM clients (calendar, email) and feed
    readers (RSS, Atom) (Closes: #3651)
  * hardcoded user in permission error (Closes: #5339)

 -- Aurelien Requiem <aurelien@requiem.fr>  Fri, 04 Jul 2014 12:08:23 +1000

piwik (2.3.0-1) stable; urgency=high

  * Releasing Piwik 2.3.0
  * #4987 Introducing Zen Mode: Simplifying the Piwik user interface to
    let you focus
  * Custom Events analytics, event tracking (Closes: #472)
  * New plugin in Marketplace: Define Custom Alerts, and receive an
    email or SMS when they are triggered (Closes: #1486)
  * Tracking servers CPU saturation after upgrade from 2.1.0 to 2.2.0
    (Closes: #5019)
  * Let Piwik user upload custom Favicon (Closes: #5167)
  * Error 'Trying to add two strings values' in
    DataTableRow::sumRowArray (Closes: #4706)
  * 'Page Name not defined' in page title reports - Outlinks being
    tracked as pages (Closes: #5113)
  * New search field to find a Custom Segment (Closes: #5221)
  * branding: Logo breaks layout (size handling generally inconsistent)
    (Closes: #5051)
  * Pie chart should not be cropped on retina display (Closes: #4594)
  * Cleanup Morpheus + Zeitgeist stylesheets, generalize the use of
    "theme" variables (Closes: #5175)
  * Let Themes overwrite templates to allow customisation within Themes
    (Closes: #5122)
  * Improve error logging of core:archive cron script (Closes: #5111)
  * Let plugin developers customise the list of "Report date to load by
    default" (Closes: #5153)
  * Developers: SettingsPiwik::rewriteTmpPathWithHostname() is
    deprecated, use SettingsPiwik::rewriteTmpPathWithInstanceId()
    instead (Closes: #5181)
  * Add new system check whether the Piwik server supports managing
    processes in CLI (Closes: #5204)
  * Website List now populated early after loading (Closes: #5097)
  * Piwik.js: new getRequest() method returns the query string of
    Tracking API HTTP request (Closes: #5118)
  * Segment selector: display longer segment names (Closes: #5217)
  * As a user I want to allow only "admin" users or "superuser" to
    create new segment (default "view") (Closes: #5172)
  * New config setting to disable segment auto complete (Closes: #5121)
  * Segment Editor: request should timeout when it takes too long to
    generate auto suggested values (Closes: #4253)
  * "Custom segment" is displayed instead of real name (Closes: #5053)
  * PHP Tracker: new method setForceNewVisit() to force creation of a
    new visit (Closes: #5123)
  * Remember detailed visitor log 'Rows to display' (Closes: #5162)
  * Configurable "Rows to display" limit. (Closes: #5188)
  * Use consistent fonts and colors in new Morpheus theme CSS/less
    (Closes: #4457)
  * Widget selector sometimes not displayed in dashboard (firefox)
    (Closes: #5227)
  * Improvements for custom events in tables like visitor log (Closes:
    #5189)
  * Custom logo: transparency channel replaced with black color (Closes:
    #5207)
  * sum_daily_nb_uniq_visitors calculations incorrect for some ranges in
    many API methods (Closes: #4377)
  * Generated .htaccess in plugins folder breaks all plugins (Closes:
    #4499)
  * When adding new annotation calendar not visible (Closes: #4510)
  * Real time map: west coast visitors are not clickable (Closes: #4613)
  * Apostrophes (and maybe other special characters) are shown encoded
    in page tooltip (Closes: #4749)
  * Changes to Sessions to improve compatibility, Browser Session was
    lost on PHP 5.5 (Closes: #4806)
  * Tooltip is unreadable (Closes: #5000)
  * MultiSites: On first login,the currencies of the websites aren't
    recognized correctly (Closes: #5006)
  * showing ' HTML code of single quote character instead of ' symbol in
    page titles (Closes: #5026)
  * procfs needed by process component (Closes: #5041)
  * datatable footer of the map widget is displayed only when the widget
    is maximized (Closes: #5047)
  * Make tracking several site IDs easier to users implementing Piwik
    using Asynchronous javascript (Closes: #5049)
  * in Visitors - Overview, Action metrics not displayed when report
    purge is enabled (Closes: #5054)
  * Logo appears stretched and pixelated on IE10+ (Closes: #5100)
  * All Websites is a blank page (Closes: #5102)
  * Plugins may not be installed correctly in some cases (Closes: #5115)
  * Dashboard "Length of Visits" widget, Pie Chart incorrect %
    calculation (Closes: #5116)
  * Set Base URL used in the AJAX request to ? instead of index.php?
    (Closes: #5127)
  * Image tracker displays wrong code: idSite= instead but idsite=
    should be used (Closes: #5131)
  * Calling API with serialize=0, get: Array to string conversion in
    core/dispatch.php on line 37 (Closes: #5144)
  * Width of VisitorLog gets truncated once moving the cursor over any
    entry in IE10+ (Closes: #5152)
  * Websites drop-down list and All Websites Dashboard view not working
    (Closes: #5170)
  * huge whitespace in visitor profile (Closes: #5191)
  * Page snapshot in Bing Windows 8 app counted as visitor, not as bot
    (Closes: #5128)
  * Document how to log errors from archive.php cron, into a file
    (Closes: #4907)
  * Japanese Search Engine (Closes: #5114)

 -- Aurelien Requiem <aurelien@requiem.fr>  Wed, 28 May 2014 14:03:00 +1000

