piwik (2.2.1-1) stable; urgency=high

  * Releasing Piwik 2.2.1
  * Persist & Restore all settings from reports, like it is done for
    Dashboard widgets (Closes: #1915)
  * Bundle AngularJS with Piwik (Closes: #4691)
  * Tracking API: allow bulk tracking without token_auth (Closes: #5030)
  * Customise periods enabled in the API and in calendar, new config
    setting (Closes: #5037)
  * Archiving should trigger limited number of concurrent requests
    (Closes: #5035)
  * Adding widgets to the dashboard not possible on mobile devices
    (Closes: #3763)
  * import_logs.py fail to populate actions/page tables (Closes: #4946)
  * Database is sometimes not initialised correctly after a fresh
    install (Closes: #4989)
  * Error: it seems you tried to skip a step of the Installation process
    (Closes: #4990)
  * Install with errors, not tracking (Closes: #5005)
  * Installation: when there is already a Super User, skip the
    installation step (Closes: #5080)
  * core:archive doesn't produce hourly archives (Closes: #5043)
  * Implement a default Referrer spam blacklist (Closes: #2268)
  * Use autoloader in piwik.php requests (Closes: #4599)
  * Use Composer to require PHPUnit (Closes: #5031)
  * Deprecate archive.sh script -> use `./console core:archive` instead
    (Closes: #5039)
  * Deprecate Period::factory() -> use PeriodFactory::build() instead
    (Closes: #5065)
  * API: Column sort does not always work for processed metrics (Closes:
    #2838)
  * support for filter_sort_order in Live.getLastVisitsDetails API
    (Closes: #4992)
  * IE10/11: calendar date range shows days in white on white (Closes:
    #4972)
  * In UI "Metrics to plot" minor formatting errors (Closes: #4555)
  * Bug: Annotations API, "date=today" is not resolved to actual date
    (Closes: #4741)
  * Disable Insights plug-in on Database Usage Graph (Closes: #4884)
  * When new annotation created in PIWIK, it proposes wrong date
    (Closes: #4888)
  * All Websites dashboard page title (Closes: #4982)
  * API getLastVisitsDetails - sorting a range of data (Closes: #4992)
  * VisitorGenerator plugin: Token auth is required for bulk tracking
    (Closes: #5010)
  * All Websites Dashboard doesn't list websites if one has the group
    field filled (Piwik 2.2.0) (Closes: #5038)
  * procfs needed by process component as of Piwik 2.2 (Closes: #5041)
  * Incompatibility with PHP 5.5.11 due to bug in this php version
    (Closes: #5060)
  * Invalid FastCGI Check in ProxyHttp.php (Closes: #5064)
  * updated lintian rules for an extra licence file.

 -- Aurelien Requiem <aurelien@requiem.fr>  Thu, 08 May 2014 02:43:22 +1000

piwik (2.2.0-1) stable; urgency=high

  * Releasing Piwik 2.2.0
  * Make Dashboard widgets more readable and less busy-looking (Closes:
    #3093)
  * Use new device-detector library in Piwik to detect browsers,
    systems, devices, brands and model (Closes: #4965)
  * All reports: display as much text as possible before the label is
    truncated (Closes: #2834)
  * Create unlimited number of custom variables slots! (we often need
    more than five) (Closes: #3810)
  * Send Super Users an email when a new Piwik version is available
    (Closes: #4843)
  * Show Site Search reports in Scheduled email reports and Piwik Mobile
    (Closes: #4869)
  * Replace "Give us feedback" top menu link with "Help" (Closes: #4898)
  * Add possibility to run multiple archiver in parallel (Closes: #4903)
  * Make Datatables more readable and flatter, to let you focus on the
    data (Closes: #4985)
  * Plugin can hook on events 'before' and 'after' other plugins
    (Closes: #1169)
  * Write Installer/Updater screenshot tests (Closes: #2935)
  * Introduce AngularJS to Piwik, first step: Website Selector rewrite
    (Closes: #4690)
  * Introduce AngularJS to Piwik Platform: rewrite All Websites selector
    to use AngularJS (Closes: #4692)
  * move UI unit tests away from PHP code and run directly in phantomjs
    w/ jasmine testing framework (Closes: #4739)
  * Piwik will now use Semantic Versioning 2.0.0 (Closes: #4796)
  * VisitFrequency API: read pre 2.0 data (Closes: #4878)
  * Developer doc: script to auto generate list of available hooks in
    piwik (Closes: #264)
  * Loading Goal reports calls the API with segmentation which can be
    slow and should be pre-processed (Closes: #2981)
  * UI unit tests (Closes: #4189)
  * Add possibility to send feedback to the Piwik team in-context
    (Closes: #4877)
  * Move language selector for logged in users to user settings (Closes:
    #4899)
  * Date range show too many visitors when you include today (Closes:
    #4720)
  * Continuous Integration server improvements (Closes: #3606)
  * create & use API for coding UI controls that spans PHP/JavaScript
    (Closes: #4116)
  * Post Event only to activated plugins (Closes: #4357)
  * linking to #hash tag does not work after merging AngularJS (Closes:
    #4795)
  * Allow Plugin Settings to be loaded within Tracker flow (Closes:
    #4924)
  * Remove deprecated methods from code base (Closes: #4942)
  * Deprecate API CoreAdminHome.getKnownSegmentsToArchive (Closes:
    #4958)
  * Piwik Debian Package blog post (Closes: #4959)
  * New template hooks to inject content from themes:
    Template.beforeTopBar, Template.beforeContent, Template.footer
    (Closes: #4986)
  * API BREAKING: Deprecated the function Schema::dropTables() and
    DbHelper::dropTables, for the new Db::dropTables() (Closes: #4991)
  * Show Websites by Group in 'All websites' dashboard (Closes: #2174)
  * Calculate number of returning unique visitors (Closes: #3870)
  * When period=range, exporting data below an evolution graph should
    export data per day (Closes: #4777)
  * When API_datatable_default_limit=-1 in the config, 'Export as'
    should export all rows (Closes: #4966)
  * When a plugin requires a max Piwik core version, disable the plugin
    on update (Closes: #4967)
  * Custom Events should not trigger a conversion for Goal defined as
    matching an "Outlink" (Closes: #4659)
  * Notice: Undefined offset: Y in core/DataArray.php on line 109
    (Closes: #4687)
  * problem with puppet in vagrant (Closes: #4773)
  * Scheduled Tasks/Cron stopped working (Closes: #4780)
  * import_logs.py doesn't acknowledge azw3 as download (Closes: #4786)
  * Importing logs with -login and -password option doesn't work in
    2.1.0 (Closes: #4817)
  * Detect when shell_exec() has been disabled and use HTTP API instead
    (Closes: #4824)
  * Column not found: 1054 Unknown column 'log_conversion_item' in
    'field list' (Closes: #4828)
  * Class 'PiwikDbSchema' not found (Closes: #4830)
  * Add new segment button not working in FF-27.x (Closes: #4833)
  * Overlay: overwriting the API endpoint with setAPIUrl does not work
    in JS (Closes: #4856)
  * when browser_archiving_disabled_enforce=1 the Auto archiver will not
    process the VisitFrequency reports (Closes: #4857)
  * when Live plugin is disabled, do not show error in Segment value
    auto-suggest (Closes: #4873)
  * When Provider plugin not installed yet: Mysqli error: Unknown column
    'log_visit.location_provider' in 'field list (Closes: #4886)
  * Edge case: page view and ecommerce conversion tracked in the same
    second create wrong visitEcommerceStatus (Closes: #4909)
  * When Real time map is loaded over https, it does not always load the
    SVG files over ssl (Closes: #4926)
  * Notice: Trying to get property of non-object in
    ExampleRssWidget/RssRenderer.php (Closes: #4928)
  * Log Analytics: import_logs does not work on windows (updatetoken.php
    fail) (Closes: #4934)
  * piwik.js: setCustomVariable should not throw error when value is
    undefined (Closes: #4938)
  * Warning: substr_compare(): The start position cannot exceed initial
    string length (Closes: #4948)
  * Installation requirements incomplete (Closes: #4951)
  * Undefined index: argv in ..../core/CronArchive.php on line 894
    (Closes: #4955)
  * Archiving should work on Synology NAS devices (Closes: #4957)
  * not checked type of return value in
    PiwikPluginManager::deactivateThemeIfTheme (Closes: #4961)
  * Installer fails when php5-json isn't installed. (Closes: #4962)
  * Actions -> Pages export fail (Closes: #4963)
  * htmlspecialchars(): Invalid multibyte sequence in argument
    vendor/twig/twig/lib/Twig/Extension/Core.php on line 968 (Closes:
    #4974)
  * Call to undefined function twig_lower_filter() (Closes: #4999)
  * setSuperUserAccess overwrites login with any super user login
    (Closes: #5004)
  * Update JQuery & JQueryUI (Closes: #4723)
  * Piwik on Windows: SQL Server, Azure, Wincache (Closes: #1902)
  * Changing super username (Closes: #2747)
  * E-Commerce Reports should not aggregate data to -1 (Closes: #3116)
  * PHP API has an effect on Piwik option piwikUrl (Closes: #3220)
  * Actions plugin has to be enabled for Visitor overview to work
    (Closes: #3749)
  * Cannot create user with apostrophe in email address (Closes: #3873)
  * htaccess rule causing geoip file to be 403 unloadable (Closes:
    #4508)
  * Real time map animation for new visitors is not displayed anymore
    (Closes: #4513)
  * Same chart on reports for multiple domains (Closes: #4747)
  * Bad link for Segment Editor API (Closes: #4781)
  * Not using $PHP_BIN for running php Scripts inside archive.sh
    (Closes: #4820)
  * No "Add" button initially in Trusted Piwik Hostname settings
    (Closes: #4854)
  * added missing dep on php5-gd, closing issue #8, thanks to g-k-r for the
    report
  * added 3 new lintian rules
  * added 'checklintianlic' Makefile rule to check for any missing license
    file
  * call 'make checklintianlic' during package build
  * better handling of utf-8 alien characters when populating
    debian/changelog.
  * added php5-cli as a mandatory dep due to /usr/share/piwik/console

 -- Aurelien Requiem <aurelien@requiem.fr>  Fri, 18 Apr 2014 13:27:34 +1000

piwik (2.1.0-2) stable; urgency=high

  * updated dependencies for those who have php5-fpm installed
  * added php5-mysqlnd as possible dependency so it doesn't conflict with
    php5-mysql
  * added post install note about ads blocker and installer

 -- Aurelien Requiem <aurelien@requiem.fr>  Tue, 11 Mar 2014 12:49:32 +1100

piwik (2.1.0-1) stable; urgency=high

  * Releasing Piwik 2.1.0
  * Archive.php memory improvements (up to 10 times less memory
    required!) (Closes: #4604)
  * Make Innodb the new default type for all new Piwik installations (VS
    Myisam) (Closes: #4611)
  * New Plugin: Provide HTTP_AUTH Authentication for Piwik - Release in
    Marketplace (Closes: #514)
  * Add Support for Multiple Superusers (Closes: #2589)
  * Introduce new User permission: Super User Access (Closes: #4564)
  * Make Archive.php use PHP CLI instead of Web, more reliable and
    faster (Closes: #4610)
  * Various improvements to Devices Detection algorithm (Closes: #4617)
  * Implement a Smart App Banner to promote iPhone / iPad App (Closes:
    #3433)
  * Add Segment Editor to the Iframed embed dashboard (Closes: #4502)
  * Implement Smart App banner for Android devices (Closes: #4520)
  * Allow Super Users to change their alias (Closes: #4582)
  * Piwik will now use Semantic Versioning for Piwik core releases and
    all plugins (Closes: #4796)
  * New config setting to disable Creation of real time segments by non
    Super Users (Closes: #4675)
  * CSV format for Scheduled Email Reports (Closes: #4701)
  * Tracking API speed improvement: cache parsed yaml in tracker cache
    (DevicesDetection) (Closes: #4683)
  * Remove force_ssl_login setting -> only support force_ssl for
    security (Closes: #4001)
  * Automatically activate/deactivate the 'Login' plugin when activating
    another Login plugin (eg. LdapLogin) (Closes: #4529)
  * Custom date range not working if archiving triggered by report view
    from browser is disabled (Closes: #4532)
  * no option to "Reuse the tables" when reinstalling Piwik (Closes:
    #4562)
  * Users should not be able to delete custom segments created by Super
    User (Closes: #4580)
  * Different visitors with the same configuration visiting the site at
    same second, could be recorded as one visitor (Closes: #4598)
  * Regressed: Scheduled reports should be sent automatically by
    webcron, when cron is not setup (Closes: #4612)
  * If server is not using at least PHP 5.3, make sure Piwik displays a
    useful error message (Closes: #4653)
  * PrivacyManager settings + Custom logo should be stored using
    Option:: rather than in config file (Closes: #4563)
  * Overriding location, city, region, latitude, longitude should be
    work for all actions (Closes: #4565)
  * Kindly Ask plugins developers of plugins for Piwik 1.x to convert to
    Piwik 2 platform (Closes: #4607)
  * Remove comments still referencing old Piwik_ (before using PHP 5.3
    namespaces) (Closes: #4609)
  * Search Engine Detection: plugin hook (Closes: #1877)
  * Live: Returning visitor to open last visits for this visitor, in
    Visitor Log & Last visits widget (Closes: #3343)
  * Detect Firefox OS (Closes: #3865)
  * Show "Help us translate Piwik" after Installation (Closes: #4084)
  * New segment: support for 'visitConvertedGoalId' in all reports
    (visitors who converted a particular Goal) (Closes: #4503)
  * Create plugin to list all scheduled tasks (Closes: #4517)
  * Taks Timetable Plugin: Show actual Piwik ServerTime (Closes: #4539)
  * Add feedback message when a segment is used, and
    browser_archiving_disabled_enforce = 1 (Closes: #4569)
  * New console command to update core and/or plugins (Closes: #4711)
  * Misplaced icons when report spans on multiple pages (Closes: #3789)
  * Piwik detects Opera 15 as Chrome 28 (Closes: #3964)
  * Samsung Tab should be qualified as tablet (Closes: #3990)
  * Make campaign name and campaign keyword lowercase when tracking
    (Closes: #4260)
  * Metrics picker on Referrers: add "Total" record (Closes: #4375)
  * Notice:Array to string conversion in tmp/templates_c/42/f7/ (Closes:
    #4432)
  * Clockwork API returned the following error message : Error 7:
    'Content' Parameter Not Specified' (Closes: #4436)
  * invalid shutdown callback when eAccelerator is enabled (Closes:
    #4439)
  * Theming: some images not overridden by theme images (Closes: #4443)
  * "Load more visits" with "Visitor Profile" loads the same visits
    (Closes: #4451)
  * Annotations, unserialize() [function.unserialize]: Error at offset
    (Closes: #4496)
  * Incorrect url redirection from transitions modal window (Closes:
    #4525)
  * Auto Geoip Db update may fail, Tar library not loading in some
    server configs (Closes: #4533)
  * tasks timetable plugin: take year into account (Closes: #4540)
  * Visits per server time wrong sort key... (Closes: #4541)
  * Piwik detects Midori 0.5 as Chrome 18 (Closes: #4557)
  * GeoIPCity.dat error in UIAssetCacheBuster.php (Closes: #4559)
  * Fix Piwik API to be used with AngularJS JSONP callback (Closes:
    #4560)
  * typo in plugins/Login/templates/login.twig (Closes: #4561)
  * Invalidating reports may fail because of log delete settings
    (Closes: #4568)
  * Show author of plugin (Closes: #4578)
  * Untranslated text in referrers template (Closes: #4600)
  * Ensure Database is set in Tracker (Closes: #4603)
  * DisplayTopKeywords only shows a single character (Closes: #4618)
  * Log Analytics -enable-bots does not enable bots tracking (Closes:
    #4628)
  * Installation: when upgrading from 2.0.3 and reusing existing tables
    during install, sql error (Closes: #4631)
  * Update currencies (Closes: #4654)
  * Call to undefined method Twig_TokenStream::nextIf in
    core/View/RenderTokenParser.php line 43 (Closes: #4669)
  * Fatal error in VisitsSummaryController::getEvolutionGraph() (Closes:
    #4678)
  * SegmentEditor API throws NoAccessException (Closes: #4679)
  * The Tracker.getDatabaseConfig event is fired before the loading of
    the plugins (Closes: #4681)
  * Morpheus theme makes tables in security settings partly unreadable
    (Closes: #4682)
  * do not track pingdom bot (Closes: #4516)
  * Remove visualphpunit (Closes: #4614)
  * German Translation for Scheduled Task/ Task Timetable Plugin
    attached (Closes: #4538)
  * Styling: Missing indentions for level5 and deeper (Closes: #3800)
  * Wrong device detection (Closes: #3971)
  * UserSettings.getMobileVsDesktop error with period=month,
    date=previous1, idSite=all (Closes: #3972)
  * geoip DB automatic update doesn't respect update period (Closes:
    #4263)
  * UI bugs connected to subdatatables (Closes: #4536)
  * Social Network icon for Youtu.be is missing (Closes: #4545)
  * Small UI error in "Real time visitor count"... (Closes: #4556)
  * CacheBuster is suboptimal (Closes: #4567)
  * Useless code spotted. (Closes: #4572)
  * Warning: preg_match(): Unknown modifier '/' in Url.php (Closes:
    #4626)
  * Invalidate merged Noncore JS / CSS in case of any plugin
    update/downgrade/uninstall (Closes: #4655)

 -- Aurelien Requiem <aurelien@requiem.fr>  Thu, 06 Mar 2014 09:57:54 +1100

piwik (2.0.3-1) stable; urgency=high

  * Releasing Piwik 2.0.3
  * Plugins: support "require" particular Piwik version and/or a minimum
    PHP version (Closes: #4183)
  * Prevent Random error "This report has been reprocessed since your
    last click. " (Closes: #4491)
  * Tracking API reference missing parameters for Ecommerce analytics
    (Closes: #4180)
  * Add geolocation check to system check report (Closes: #4484)
  * Users report for All websites in scheduled report (Closes: #4471)
  * Remove DoNotTrack and Anonymize plugins and move them to
    PrivacyManager (Closes: #4493)
  * Can't open Plugins/Themes because my server and client are off the
    internet (Closes: #4431)
  * Exclude from traffic Baidu bot and Yandex bot (Closes: #4504)
  * Allow to define the time to look back to define a returning visitor
    (Closes: #3695)
  * Visitor Log: returning visitors: show number of visits (Closes:
    #4319)
  * Add setting to disable LOAD DATA INFILE, for easy Mysql replication
    in AWS (Closes: #4358)
  * Can't get goals by custom variable values (Closes: #4490)
  * Replace jsmin (Closes: #3874)
  * Broken sorting in Goals.getItems (Closes: #3944)
  * geoip DB automatic update doesn't respect update period (Closes:
    #4263)
  * Error in visitor Map for region Vaud, Switzerland (Closes: #4402)
  * Brazil SVG Map region fix (Closes: #4407)
  * Morpheus theme shouldn't force aspect ratio on custom branding logo
    (Closes: #4408)
  * Browser Detection Internet Explorer 11.0 (IE11) (Closes: #4414)
  * setting sites are very wide (Closes: #4423)
  * file .git/HEAD doesn't exist (Closes: #4425)
  * Log.php: Assigning the return value of new by reference is
    deprecated (Closes: #4427)
  * Bounce rate column sorts is not working (Closes: #4429)
  * Real time visitor count does not refresh automatically (Closes:
    #4435)
  * In Theme.php, file_exists() triggers open_basedir restrictions in
    Windows PHP if containing querystring (Closes: #4438)
  * "Ranking Query" for better archiving memory consumption (Closes:
    #3330)
  * visits from Google adwords bot should be excluded (Closes: #4441)
  * LOAD DATA INFILE in chroot environment (Closes: #4442)
  * Theming: some images not overridden by theme images (Closes: #4443)
  * Repeated visits reported in Visitor profile (Closes: #4448)
  * String data, right truncated: 1406 Data too long for column
    'location_browser_lang' at row 1 (Closes: #4450)
  * PHP Fatal error: Call to a member function
    rewriteAssetsPathToTheme() (Closes: #4453)
  * Wrong label for returning visitor in Visitors in Real-time. (Closes:
    #4479)
  * Ignore Do Not Track setting for IE 11 browsers (Closes: #4482)
  * Presence of "http://" in the parameters of the archive cron script
    may cause incompatibility with cPanel (Closes: #4483)
  * Goals> Ecommerce log listing, not listing all ecommerce orders and
    abandoned carts (Closes: #4505)
  * Error when downloading pdf-report (Closes: #4404)
  * Module ImageGraph.get API 'graphType=3dPie' error. (Closes: #4420)
  * Weird spacing in "Visits in Real-time" plugin (Closes: #4417)
  * Big extra spacing in annotations (Closes: #4419)

 -- Aurelien Requiem <aurelien@requiem.fr>  Wed, 15 Jan 2014 12:59:25 +1100

piwik (2.0.2-3) stable; urgency=high

  * entirely removed misc/translationTool.sh script from the package
  * cron is now installed in /etc/cron.d/piwik-archive as per documentation
  * now call archive.php to run the cron instead of archive.sh
  * added dependency on php5-curl
  * removed a directory from package that isn't necessary

